# <a name="sensitive-information-type-entity-definitions"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-104">敏感資訊類型實體定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-104">Sensitive information type entity definitions</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-105">規範中心的資料遺失防護（DLP）包含許多可供您在 DLP 原則中使用的機密資訊類型。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-105">Data loss prevention (DLP) in the Compliance Center includes many sensitive information types that are ready for you to use in your DLP policies.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="93909-106">本主題列出所有敏感資訊類型，並顯示 DLP 原則在偵測到每種類型時所尋找的功能。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-106">This topic lists all of these sensitive information types and shows what a DLP policy looks for when it detects each type.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="93909-107">敏感資訊類型是由正則運算式或函數所識別的模式所定義。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-107">A sensitive information type is defined by a pattern that can be identified by a regular expression or a function.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="93909-108">此外，您也可以使用確切證據（如關鍵字及校驗和）來識別敏感資訊類型。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-108">In addition, corroborative evidence such as keywords and checksums can be used to identify a sensitive information type.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="93909-109">評估程式中也會使用信賴等級和近程。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-109">Confidence level and proximity are also used in the evaluation process.</span></span>
  
## <a name="aba-routing-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-110">ABA 路由號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-110">ABA routing number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-111">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-111">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-112">格式或未格式化的模式中的9位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-112">9 digits which may be in a formatted or unformatted pattern</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-113">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-113">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-114">格式 化：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-114">Formatted:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-115">以0、1、2、3、6、7或8開頭的四位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-115">Four digits beginning with 0, 1, 2, 3, 6, 7, or 8</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-116">連字號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-116">A hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-117">四位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-117">Four digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-118">連字號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-118">A hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-119">一個數位</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-119">A digit</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-120">未格式化：9以0、1、2、3、6、7或8開頭的連續數位</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-120">Unformatted: 9 consecutive digits beginning with 0, 1, 2, 3, 6, 7, or 8</span></span> 

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-121">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-121">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-122">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-122">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-123">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-123">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-124">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-124">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-125">函數 Func_aba_routing 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-125">The function Func_aba_routing finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-126">會找到來自 Keyword_ABA_Routing 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-126">A keyword from Keyword_ABA_Routing is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- ABA Routing Number -->
<Entity id="cb353f78-2b72-4c3c-8827-92ebe4f69fdf" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_aba_routing" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_ABA_Routing" />
      </Pattern>
 </Entity>
```

## <a name="argentina-national-identity-dni-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-146">阿根廷國內身分識別（DNI）號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-146">Argentina national identity (DNI) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-147">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-147">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-148">以句點隔開的八位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-148">Eight digits separated by periods</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-149">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-149">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-150">八位數：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-150">Eight digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-151">兩位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-151">Two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-152">一個句點</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-152">A period</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-153">三位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-153">Three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-154">一個句點</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-154">A period</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-155">三位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-155">Three digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-156">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-156">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-157">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-157">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-158">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-158">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-159">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-159">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-160">正則運算式 Regex_argentina_national_id 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-160">The regular expression Regex_argentina_national_id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-161">會找到來自 Keyword_argentina_national_id 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-161">A keyword from Keyword_argentina_national_id is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Argentina National Identity (DNI) Number -->
<Entity id="eefbb00e-8282-433c-8620-8f1da3bffdb2" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
   <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
      <IdMatch idRef="Regex_argentina_national_id"/>
      <Match idRef="Keyword_argentina_national_id"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="australia-bank-account-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-173">澳大利亞銀行帳戶號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-173">Australia bank account number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-174">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-174">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-175">包含或不含銀行狀態分公司號碼的6-10 位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-175">6-10 digits with or without a bank state branch number</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-176">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-176">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-177">帳戶號碼是6-10 位數。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-177">Account number is 6-10 digits.</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="93909-178">澳大利亞銀行狀態分支編號：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-178">Australia bank state branch number:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-179">三位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-179">Three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-180">連字號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-180">A hyphen</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-181">三位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-181">Three digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-182">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-182">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-183">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-183">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-184">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-184">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-185">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是85%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-185">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-186">正則運算式 Regex_australia_bank_account_number 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-186">The regular expression Regex_australia_bank_account_number finds content that matches the pattern..</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-187">會找到來自 Keyword_australia_bank_account_number 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-187">A keyword from Keyword_australia_bank_account_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-188">正則運算式 Regex_australia_bank_account_number_bsb 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-188">The regular expression Regex_australia_bank_account_number_bsb finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-189">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-189">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-190">正則運算式 Regex_australia_bank_account_number 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-190">The regular expression Regex_australia_bank_account_number finds content that matches the pattern..</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-191">會找到來自 Keyword_australia_bank_account_number 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-191">A keyword from Keyword_australia_bank_account_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Australia Bank Account Number -->
<Entity id="74a54de9-2a30-4aa0-a8aa-3d9327fc07c7" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_australia_bank_account_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_australia_bank_account_number" />
        <Match idRef="Regex_australia_bank_account_number_bsb" />
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_australia_bank_account_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_australia_bank_account_number" />
  </Pattern>
 </Entity>
```

## <a name="australia-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-207">澳大利亞駕駛執照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-207">Australia driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-208">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-208">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-209">九個字母和數位</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-209">Nine letters and digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-210">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-210">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-211">九個字母和數位：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-211">Nine letters and digits:</span></span> 

- <span data-ttu-id="93909-212">兩位數或字母（不區分大小寫）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-212">Two digits or letters (not case sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-213">兩位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-213">Two digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-214">五個數字或字母（不區分大小寫）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-214">Five digits or letters (not case sensitive)</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-215">OR</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-215">OR</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="93909-216">1-2 選用的字母（不區分大小寫）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-216">1-2 optional letters (not case sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-217">4-9 位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-217">4-9 digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-218">OR</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-218">OR</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="93909-219">九個數字或字母（不區分大小寫）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-219">Nine digits or letters (not case sensitive)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-220">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-220">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-221">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-221">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-222">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-222">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-223">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-223">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-224">正則運算式 Regex_australia_drivers_license_number 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-224">The regular expression Regex_australia_drivers_license_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-225">會找到來自 Keyword_australia_drivers_license_number 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-225">A keyword from Keyword_australia_drivers_license_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-226">找不到 Keyword_australia_drivers_license_number_exclusions 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-226">No keyword from Keyword_australia_drivers_license_number_exclusions is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Australia Drivers License Number -->
<Entity id="1cbbc8f5-9216-4392-9eb5-5ac2298d1356" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
   <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_australia_drivers_license_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_australia_drivers_license_number" />
        <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_australia_drivers_license_number_exclusions" />
        </Any>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="australia-medical-account-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-326">澳大利亞醫療帳戶號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-326">Australia medical account number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-327">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-327">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-328">10-11 位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-328">10-11 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-329">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-329">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-330">10-11 位數：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-330">10-11 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-331">第一個數位是在2-6 範圍內</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-331">First digit is in the range 2-6</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-332">第九位數是檢查碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-332">Ninth digit is a check digit</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-333">第十個數字是問題的位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-333">Tenth digit is the issue digit</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-334">第十位數（選用）是個別數位</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-334">Eleventh digit (optional) is the individual number</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-335">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-335">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-336">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-336">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-337">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-337">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-338">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是95%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-338">A DLP policy is 95% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-339">函數 Func_australian_medical_account_number 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-339">The function Func_australian_medical_account_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-340">會找到來自 Keyword_Australia_Medical_Account_Number 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-340">A keyword from Keyword_Australia_Medical_Account_Number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-341">校驗和通過。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-341">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-342">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是85%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-342">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-343">函數 Func_australian_medical_account_number 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-343">The function Func_australian_medical_account_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-344">校驗和通過。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-344">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
  <!-- Australia Medical Account Number -->
<Entity id="104a99a0-3d3b-4542-a40d-ab0b9e1efe63" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="95">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_australian_medical_account_number"/>
     <Any minMatches="1">
     <Match idRef="Keyword_Australia_Medical_Account_Number"/>
     </Any>
  </Pattern>
<Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_australian_medical_account_number"/>
     <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
  <Match idRef="Keyword_Australia_Medical_Account_Number"/>
     </Any>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="australia-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-356">澳大利亞護照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-356">Australia passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-357">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-357">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-358">字母后接7位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-358">A letter followed by seven digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-359">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-359">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-360">字母（不區分大小寫）後接7位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-360">A letter (not case sensitive) followed by seven digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-361">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-361">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-362">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-362">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-363">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-363">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-364">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-364">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-365">正則運算式 Regex_australia_passport_number 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-365">The regular expression Regex_australia_passport_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-366">會找到 Keyword_passport 或 Keyword_australia_passport_number 中的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-366">A keyword from Keyword_passport or Keyword_australia_passport_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Australia Passport Number -->
<Entity id="29869db6-602d-4853-ab93-3484f905df50" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_australia_passport_number" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_passport" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_australia_passport_number" />
        </Any>
   </Pattern>
</Entity>   
```

## <a name="australia-tax-file-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-400">澳大利亞稅收檔編號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-400">Australia tax file number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-401">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-401">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-402">8-9 位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-402">8-9 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-403">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-403">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-404">通常會以空格呈現的8-9 位數，如下所示：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-404">8-9 digits typically presented with spaces as follows:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-405">三位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-405">Three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-406">選擇性的空格</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-406">An optional space</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-407">三位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-407">Three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-408">選擇性的空格</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-408">An optional space</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-409">最後一個數位是檢查碼的2-3 位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-409">2-3 digits where the last digit is a check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-410">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-410">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-411">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-411">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-412">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-412">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-413">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是85%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-413">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-414">函數 Func_australian_tax_file_number 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-414">The function Func_australian_tax_file_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-415">找不到 Keyword_Australia_Tax_File_Number 或 Keyword_number_exclusions 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-415">No keyword from Keyword_Australia_Tax_File_Number or Keyword_number_exclusions is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-416">校驗和通過。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-416">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
   <!-- Australia Tax File Number -->
    <Entity id="e29bc95f-ff70-4a37-aa01-04d17360a4c5" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_australian_tax_file_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_Australia_Tax_File_Number" />
        <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_number_exclusions" />
        </Any>
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

## <a name="austria-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-458">奧地利駕駛執照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-458">Austria driver's license number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="93909-459">這個敏感資訊類型實體只有歐盟駕駛執照號碼機密資訊類型提供。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-459">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-460">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-460">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-461">不含空格及分隔符號的八位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-461">Eight digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-462">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-462">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-463">八位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-463">Eight digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-464">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-464">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-465">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-465">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-466">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-466">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-467">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-467">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-468">正則運算式會 `Regex_austria_eu_driver's_license_number` 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-468">The regular expression  `Regex_austria_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-469">找到來自的關鍵字 `Keywords_austria_eu_driver's_license_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-469">A keyword from  `Keywords_austria_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
<!-- EU Driver's License Number -->
<Entity id="b8fe86d1-c056-453b-bfaa-9fe698699ecc" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_austria_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_austria_eu_driver's_license_number" />
        </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

## <a name="austria-national-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-486">奧地利國身分識別號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-486">Austria national identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="93909-487">這個敏感資訊類型實體僅可用於歐盟國身分識別號碼的敏感資訊類型。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-487">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU National Identification Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-488">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-488">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-489">字母、數位及特殊字元的24個字元的組合</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-489">A 24-character combination of letters, digits, and special characters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-490">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-490">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-491">24個字元：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-491">24 characters:</span></span>
  
-  <span data-ttu-id="93909-492">22個字母（不區分大小寫）、數位、反斜線、正斜線或正號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-492">22 letters (not case-sensitive), digits, backslashes, forward slashes, or plus signs</span></span> 
    
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-493">兩個字母（不區分大小寫）、數位、反斜線、正斜線、加號或等號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-493">Two letters (not case-sensitive), digits, backslashes, forward slashes, plus signs, or equal signs</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-494">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-494">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-495">不適用</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-495">Not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-496">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-496">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-497">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-497">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-498">正則運算式會 `Regex_austria_eu_national_id_card` 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-498">The regular expression  `Regex_austria_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-499">找到來自的關鍵字 `Keywords_austria_eu_national_id_card` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-499">A keyword from  `Keywords_austria_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 
   
```xml
<!-- EU austria_eu_national_id -->
<Entity id="419f449f-6d9d-4be1-a154-b531f7a91b41" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_austria_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_austria_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

#### <a name="keywords_austria_eu_national_id_card"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-501">Keywords_austria_eu_national_id_card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-501">Keywords_austria_eu_national_id_card</span></span>

## <a name="austria-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-505">奧地利護照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-505">Austria passport number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="93909-506">這個敏感資訊類型實體只適用于歐盟護照號碼 sensitiveinformation type。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-506">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Passport Number sensitiveinformation type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-507">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-507">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-508">一個字母后接一個選擇性的空格和七位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-508">One letter followed by an optional space and seven digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-509">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-509">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-510">一個字母、七位數和一個空格的組合：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-510">A combination of one letter, seven digits, and one space:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-511">一個字母（不區分大小寫）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-511">One letter (not case sensitive)</span></span>
    
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-512">一個空格（選用）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-512">One space (optional)</span></span>
    
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-513">七位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-513">Seven digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-514">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-514">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-515">不適用</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-515">Not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-516">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-516">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-517">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-517">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-518">正則運算式會 `Regex_austria_eu_passport_number` 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-518">The regular expression  `Regex_austria_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-519">找到來自的關鍵字 `Keywords_austria_eu_passport_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-519">A keyword from  `Keywords_austria_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Passport Number -->
<Entity id="21883626-6245-4f3d-9b61-5cbb43e625ee" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_austria_eu_passport_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_austria_eu_passport_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-520">關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-520">Keywords</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-521">**Keywords_austria_eu_passport_number**</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-521">**Keywords_austria_eu_passport_number**</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-522">護照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-522">passport number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-523">奧地利護照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-523">austrian passport number</span></span>

## <a name="austria-social-security-number-or-equivalent-identification"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-527">奧地利的社會安全號碼或同等身分識別</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-527">Austria social security number or equivalent identification</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="93909-528">這個敏感資訊類型實體只有歐盟社會保險號碼或同等識別碼的敏感資訊類型提供。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-528">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Social Security Number or Equivalent ID sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-529">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-529">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-530">指定之格式的10位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-530">10 digits in the specified format</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-531">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-531">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-532">10位數：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-532">10 digits:</span></span>
  
-  <span data-ttu-id="93909-533">對應至序列值的三位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-533">Three digits that correspond to a serial number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-534">一個檢查碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-534">One check digit</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-535">與出生日期對應的六位數（DDMMYY）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-535">Six digits that correspond to the birth date (DDMMYY)</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-536">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-536">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-537">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-537">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-538">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-538">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-539">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是85%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-539">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-540">函數 `Func_austria_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` 會找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-540">The function  `Func_austria_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-541">找到來自的關鍵字 `Keywords_austria_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-541">A keyword from  `Keywords_austria_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="93909-542">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-542">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-543">函數 `Func_austria_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` 會找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-543">The function  `Func_austria_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU SSN or Equivalent Number -->
<Entity id="d24e32a4-c0bb-4ba8-899d-6303b95742d9" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_austria_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_austria_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
        </Pattern>
<Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
            <IdMatch idRef="Func_austria_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
          </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-544">關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-544">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_austria_eu_ssn_or_equivalent"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-545">Keywords_austria_eu_ssn_or_equivalent</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-545">Keywords_austria_eu_ssn_or_equivalent</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="93909-546">社會安全性否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-546">social security no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-547">社會安全號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-547">social security number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-548">社會安全性碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-548">social security code</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-549">保險號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-549">insurance number</span></span>

## <a name="austria-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-559">奧地利納稅識別號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-559">Austria tax identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="93909-560">這個敏感資訊類型實體只適用于歐盟納稅識別碼的敏感資訊類型。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-560">This sensitive information type entity is only available the EU Tax ID number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-561">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-561">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-562">具有選擇性連字號及正斜線的九位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-562">Nine digits with optional hyphen and forward slash</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-563">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-563">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-564">具有選擇性連字號及正斜線的九位數：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-564">Nine digits with optional hyphen and forward slash:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-565">兩位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-565">Two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-566">連字號（選用）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-566">A hyphen (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-567">三位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-567">Three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-568">一個正斜線（選用）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-568">A forward slash (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-569">四位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-569">Four digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-570">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-570">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-571">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-571">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-572">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-572">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-573">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是85%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-573">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-574">函數 `Func_austria_eu_tax_file_number` 會找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-574">The function  `Func_austria_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-575">找到來自的關鍵字 `Keywords_austria_eu_tax_file_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-575">A keyword from  `Keywords_austria_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="93909-576">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-576">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-577">函數 `Func_austria_eu_tax_file_number` 會找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-577">The function  `Func_austria_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Tax File Number -->
<Entity id="e09c07d3-66e5-4783-989d-49ac62748f5f" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_austria_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_austria_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
<Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_austria_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="azure-documentdb-auth-key"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-600">Azure DocumentDB 驗證金鑰</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-600">Azure DocumentDB Auth key</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-601">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-601">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-602">字串 "DocumentDb"，後面加上下列模式中所述的字元及字串。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-602">The string "DocumentDb" followed by the characters and strings outlined in the pattern below.</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-603">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-603">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="93909-604">字串 "DocumentDb"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-604">The string "DocumentDb"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-605">介於3-200 小寫或大寫字母、數位、符號、特殊字元或空格之間的任何組合</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-605">Any combination of between 3-200 lower- or uppercase letters, digits, symbols, special characters, or spaces</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-606">大於符號（>）、等號（=）、引號（"）或撇號（'）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-606">A greater than symbol (>), an equal sign (=), a quotation mark ("), or an apostrophe (')</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-607">任何86的小寫字母或大寫字母、數位、正斜線（/）或加號（+）組合</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-607">Any combination of 86 lower- or uppercase letters, digits, forward slash (/), or plus sign (+)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-608">兩個等號（=）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-608">Two equal signs (=)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-609">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-609">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-610">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-610">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-611">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-611">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-612">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是85%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-612">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-613">正則運算式 CEP_Regex_AzureDocumentDBAuthKey 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-613">The regular expression CEP_Regex_AzureDocumentDBAuthKey finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-614">正則運算式**CEP_CommonExampleKeywords 不會找到符合**模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-614">The regular expression CEP_CommonExampleKeywords does **not** find content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Azure Document DB Auth Key -->
<Entity id="0f587d92-eb28-44a9-bd1c-90f2892b47aa" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="CEP_Regex_AzureDocumentDBAuthKey" />
        <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="CEP_CommonExampleKeywords" />
          </Any>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-615">關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-615">Keywords</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-617">（請注意，在技術上而言，這個敏感資訊類型是使用正則運算式來識別這些關鍵字，而不是關鍵字清單。）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-617">(Note that technically, this sensitive information type identifies these keywords by using a regular expression, not a keyword list.)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="93909-621">沙 箱</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-621">sandbox</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-622">onebox</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-622">onebox</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="93909-624">127.0.0.1</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-624">127.0.0.1</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-625">testacs.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-625">testacs.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="93909-626">Com</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-626">com</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-627">s-int。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-627">s-int.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="93909-628">網</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-628">net</span></span>

## <a name="azure-iaas-database-connection-string-and-azure-sql-connection-string"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-629">Azure IAAS 資料庫連接字串和 Azure SQL 連接字串</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-629">Azure IAAS database connection string and Azure SQL connection string</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-630">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-630">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-631">字串 "Server"、"server" 或 "data source"，後面加上模式中所述的字元及字串（包括字串 "cloudapp"）。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-631">The string "Server", "server", or "data source" followed by the characters and strings outlined in the pattern below, including the string "cloudapp.azure.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="93909-632">com "或" cloudapp。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-632">com" or "cloudapp.azure.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="93909-633">net "或" database。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-633">net" or "database.windows.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="93909-634">net "，及字串" Password "或" password "或" pwd "。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-634">net", and the string "Password" or "password" or "pwd".</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-635">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-635">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="93909-636">字串「伺服器」、「伺服器」或「資料來源」</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-636">The string "Server", "server", or "data source"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-637">0-2 空白字元</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-637">0-2 whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-638">等號（=）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-638">An equal sign (=)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-639">0-2 空白字元</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-639">0-2 whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-640">介於1-200 小寫或大寫字母、數位、符號、特殊字元或空格之間的任何組合</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-640">Any combination of between 1-200 lower- or uppercase letters, digits, symbols, special characters, or spaces</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-641">字串 "cloudapp"。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-641">The string "cloudapp.azure.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="93909-642">com "，" cloudapp。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-642">com", "cloudapp.azure.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="93909-643">net "或" database。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-643">net", or "database.windows.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="93909-644">真實</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-644">net"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-645">介於1-300 小寫或大寫字母、數位、符號、特殊字元或空格之間的任何組合</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-645">Any combination of between 1-300 lower- or uppercase letters, digits, symbols, special characters, or spaces</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-646">字串 "Password"、"password" 或 "pwd"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-646">The string "Password", "password", or "pwd"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-647">0-2 空白字元</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-647">0-2 whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-648">等號（=）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-648">An equal sign (=)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-649">0-2 空白字元</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-649">0-2 whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-650">一個或多個字元，不是分號（;)、引號（"）或單引號（'）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-650">One or more characters that is not a semicolon (;), quotation mark ("), or apostrophe (')</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-651">分號（;)、引號（"）或撇號（'）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-651">A semicolon (;), quotation mark ("), or apostrophe (')</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-652">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-652">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-653">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-653">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-654">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-654">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-655">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是85%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-655">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-656">正則運算式 CEP_Regex_AzureConnectionString 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-656">The regular expression CEP_Regex_AzureConnectionString finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-657">正則運算式**CEP_CommonExampleKeywords 不會找到符合**模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-657">The regular expression CEP_CommonExampleKeywords does **not** find content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
<!--Azure IAAS Database Connection String and Azure SQL Connection String-->
<Entity id="ce1a126d-186f-4700-8c0c-486157b953fd" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="CEP_Regex_AzureConnectionString" />
        <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="CEP_CommonExampleKeywords" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="azure-iot-connection-string"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-672">Azure IoT 連接字串</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-672">Azure IoT connection string</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-673">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-673">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-674">字串 "HostName"，後面加上下列模式中所述的字元及字串，包括字串 "azure 裝置。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-674">The string "HostName" followed by the characters and strings outlined in the pattern below, including the strings "azure-devices.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="93909-675">net "和" SharedAccessKey "。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-675">net" and "SharedAccessKey".</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-676">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-676">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="93909-677">字串 "HostName"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-677">The string "HostName"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-678">0-2 空白字元</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-678">0-2 whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-679">等號（=）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-679">An equal sign (=)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-680">0-2 空白字元</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-680">0-2 whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-681">介於1-200 小寫或大寫字母、數位、符號、特殊字元或空格之間的任何組合</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-681">Any combination of between 1-200 lower- or uppercase letters, digits, symbols, special characters, or spaces</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-682">"Azure 裝置" 字串。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-682">The string "azure-devices.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="93909-683">真實</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-683">net"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-684">介於1-200 小寫或大寫字母、數位、符號、特殊字元或空格之間的任何組合</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-684">Any combination of between 1-200 lower- or uppercase letters, digits, symbols, special characters, or spaces</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-685">字串 "SharedAccessKey"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-685">The string "SharedAccessKey"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-686">0-2 空白字元</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-686">0-2 whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-687">等號（=）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-687">An equal sign (=)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-688">0-2 空白字元</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-688">0-2 whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-689">任何43的小寫字母或大寫字母、數位、正斜線（/）或加號（+）組合</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-689">Any combination of 43 lower- or uppercase letters, digits, forward slash (/), or plus sign (+)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-690">等號（=）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-690">An equal sign (=)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-691">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-691">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-692">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-692">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-693">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-693">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-694">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是85%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-694">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-695">正則運算式 CEP_Regex_AzureIoTConnectionString 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-695">The regular expression CEP_Regex_AzureIoTConnectionString finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-696">正則運算式**CEP_CommonExampleKeywords 不會找到符合**模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-696">The regular expression CEP_CommonExampleKeywords does **not** find content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
<!--Azure IoT Connection String-->
<Entity id="0b34bec3-d5d6-4974-b7b0-dcdb5c90c29d" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="CEP_Regex_AzureIoTConnectionString" />
        <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="CEP_CommonExampleKeywords" />
        </Any>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

<Entity id="75f4cc8a-a68e-49e5-89ce-fa8f03d286a5" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
       <IdMatch idRef="CEP_Regex_AzurePublishSettingPasswords" />
       <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
           <Match idRef="CEP_CommonExampleKeywords" />
       </Any>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>

## <a name="azure-redis-cache-connection-string"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-738">Azure Redis cache connection string</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-738">Azure Redis cache connection string</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-739">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-739">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-740">字串 "redis。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-740">The string "redis.cache.windows.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="93909-741">net "後接下列模式中所述的字元和字串，包含字串" password "或" pwd "。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-741">net" followed by the characters and strings outlined in the pattern below, including the string "password" or "pwd".</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-742">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-742">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="93909-743">字串 "redis。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-743">The string "redis.cache.windows.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="93909-744">真實</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-744">net"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-745">介於1-200 小寫或大寫字母、數位、符號、特殊字元或空格之間的任何組合</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-745">Any combination of between 1-200 lower- or uppercase letters, digits, symbols, special characters, or spaces</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-746">字串 "password" 或 "pwd"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-746">The string "password" or "pwd"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-747">0-2 空白字元</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-747">0-2 whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-748">等號（=）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-748">An equal sign (=)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-749">0-2 空白字元</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-749">0-2 whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-750">43個字元的任何組合，其為小寫或大寫字母、數位、正斜線（/）或加號（+）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-750">Any combination of 43 characters that are lower- or uppercase letters, digits, forward slash (/), or plus sign (+)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-751">等號（=）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-751">An equal sign (=)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-752">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-752">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-753">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-753">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-754">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-754">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-755">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是85%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-755">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-756">正則運算式 CEP_Regex_AzureRedisCacheConnectionString 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-756">The regular expression CEP_Regex_AzureRedisCacheConnectionString finds content that matches the pattern..</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-757">正則運算式**CEP_CommonExampleKeywords 不會找到符合**模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-757">The regular expression CEP_CommonExampleKeywords does **not** find content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
<!--Azure Redis Cache Connection String-->
<Entity id="095a7e6c-efd8-46d5-af7b-5298d53a49fc" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="CEP_Regex_AzureRedisCacheConnectionString" />
        <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="CEP_CommonExampleKeywords" />
        </Any>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="azure-sas"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-772">Azure SAS</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-772">Azure SAS</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-773">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-773">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-774">字串 "sig"，後面加上下列模式中所述的字元及字串。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-774">The string "sig" followed by the characters and strings outlined in the pattern below.</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-775">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-775">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="93909-776">字串 "sig"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-776">The string "sig"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-777">0-2 空白字元</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-777">0-2 whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-778">等號（=）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-778">An equal sign (=)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-779">0-2 空白字元</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-779">0-2 whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-780">介於43-53 個字元、小寫字母、數位或百分比符號（%）之間的任何組合</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-780">Any combination of between 43-53 characters that are lower- or uppercase letters, digits, or the percent sign (%)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-781">字串 "% 三維"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-781">The string "%3d"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-782">非小寫或大寫字母、數位或百分號（%）以外的任何字元</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-782">Any character that is not a lower- or uppercase letter, digit, or percent sign (%)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-783">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-783">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-784">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-784">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-785">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-785">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-786">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是85%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-786">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-787">正則運算式 CEP_Regex_AzureSAS 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-787">The regular expression CEP_Regex_AzureSAS finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
<!--Azure SAS-->
<Entity id="4d235014-e564-47f4-a6fb-6ebb4a826834" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="CEP_Regex_AzureSAS" />
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="azure-service-bus-connection-string"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-788">Azure 服務匯流排連接字串</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-788">Azure Service Bus Connection String</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-789">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-789">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-790">字串 "EndPoint" 後接下列模式中所述的字元及字串，包含字串 "</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-790">The string "EndPoint" followed by the characters and strings outlined in the pattern below, including the strings "servicebus.windows.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="93909-791">net "和" SharedAccesKey "。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-791">net" and "SharedAccesKey".</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-792">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-792">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="93909-793">字串 "EndPoint"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-793">The string "EndPoint"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-794">0-2 空白字元</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-794">0-2 whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-795">等號（=）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-795">An equal sign (=)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-796">0-2 空白字元</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-796">0-2 whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-797">介於1-200 小寫或大寫字母、數位、符號、特殊字元或空格之間的任何組合</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-797">Any combination of between 1-200 lower- or uppercase letters, digits, symbols, special characters, or spaces</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-798">字串 "</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-798">The string "servicebus.windows.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="93909-799">真實</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-799">net"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-800">介於1-200 小寫或大寫字母、數位、符號、特殊字元或空格之間的任何組合</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-800">Any combination of between 1-200 lower- or uppercase letters, digits, symbols, special characters, or spaces</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-801">字串 "SharedAccessKey"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-801">The string "SharedAccessKey"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-802">0-2 空白字元</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-802">0-2 whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-803">等號（=）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-803">An equal sign (=)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-804">0-2 空白字元</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-804">0-2 whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-805">43個字元的任何組合，其為小寫或大寫字母、數位、正斜線（/）或加號（+）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-805">Any combination of 43 characters that are lower- or uppercase letters, digits, forward slash (/), or plus sign (+)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-806">等號（=）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-806">An equal sign (=)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-807">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-807">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-808">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-808">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-809">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-809">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-810">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是85%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-810">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-811">正則運算式 CEP_Regex_AzureServiceBusConnectionString 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-811">The regular expression CEP_Regex_AzureServiceBusConnectionString finds content that matches the pattern..</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-812">正則運算式**CEP_CommonExampleKeywords 不會找到符合**模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-812">The regular expression CEP_CommonExampleKeywords does **not** find content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
<!--Azure Service Bus Connection String-->
<Entity id="b9a6578f-a83f-4fcd-bf44-2130bae49a6f" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="CEP_Regex_AzureServiceBusConnectionString" />
        <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="CEP_CommonExampleKeywords" />
        </Any>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="azure-storage-account-key"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-827">Azure 儲存體帳戶金鑰</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-827">Azure Storage Account Key</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-830">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-830">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="93909-831">字串 "DefaultEndpointsProtocol"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-831">The string "DefaultEndpointsProtocol"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-832">0-2 空白字元</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-832">0-2 whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-833">等號（=）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-833">An equal sign (=)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-834">0-2 空白字元</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-834">0-2 whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-835">介於1-200 小寫或大寫字母、數位、符號、特殊字元或空格之間的任何組合</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-835">Any combination of between 1-200 lower- or uppercase letters, digits, symbols, special characters, or spaces</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-836">字串 "AccountKey"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-836">The string "AccountKey"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-837">0-2 空白字元</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-837">0-2 whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-838">等號（=）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-838">An equal sign (=)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-839">0-2 空白字元</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-839">0-2 whitespace characters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-840">86個字元的任何組合，其為小寫或大寫字母、數位、正斜線（/）或加號（+）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-840">Any combination of 86 characters that are lower- or uppercase letters, digits, forward slash (/), or plus sign (+)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-841">兩個等號（=）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-841">Two equal signs (=)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-842">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-842">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-843">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-843">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-844">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-844">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-845">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是85%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-845">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-846">正則運算式 CEP_Regex_AzureStorageAccountKey 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-846">The regular expression CEP_Regex_AzureStorageAccountKey finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-847">正則運算式**CEP_AzureEmulatorStorageAccountFilter 不會找到符合**模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-847">The regular expression CEP_AzureEmulatorStorageAccountFilter does **not** find content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-848">正則運算式**CEP_CommonExampleKeywords 不會找到符合**模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-848">The regular expression CEP_CommonExampleKeywords does **not** find content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
<!--Azure Storage Account Key-->
<Entity id="c7bc98e8-551a-4c35-a92d-d2c8cda714a7" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="CEP_Regex_AzureStorageAccountKey" />
        <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="CEP_AzureEmulatorStorageAccountFilter" />
            <Match idRef="CEP_CommonExampleKeywords" />
        </Any>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="azure-storage-account-key-generic"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-866">Azure 儲存體帳戶金鑰（一般）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-866">Azure Storage account key (generic)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-867">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-867">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-868">任何86的小寫字母或大寫字母、數位、正斜線（/）或加號（+）的組合，前置或後接下列模式中所述的字元。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-868">Any combination of 86 lower- or uppercase letters, digits, the forward slash (/), or plus sign (+), preceded or followed by the characters outlined in the pattern below.</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-869">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-869">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="93909-870">大於符號（>）、撇號（'）、等號（=）、引號（"）或數位記號（#）的0-1</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-870">0-1 of the greater than symbol (>), apostrophe ('), equal sign (=), quotation mark ("), or number sign (#)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-871">86個字元的任何組合（低或大寫字母、數位、正斜線（/）或加號（+））</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-871">Any combination of 86 characters that are lower- or uppercase letters, digits, the forward slash (/), or plus sign (+)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-872">兩個等號（=）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-872">Two equal signs (=)</span></span>


### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-873">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-873">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-874">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-874">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-875">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-875">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-876">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是85%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-876">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-877">正則運算式 CEP_Regex_AzureStorageAccountKeyGeneric 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-877">The regular expression CEP_Regex_AzureStorageAccountKeyGeneric finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
<!--Azure Storage Account Key (Generic)-->
<Entity id="7ff41bd0-5419-4523-91d6-383b3a37f084" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="CEP_Regex_AzureStorageAccountKeyGeneric" />
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```
## <a name="belgium-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-878">比利時駕駛執照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-878">Belgium driver's license number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="93909-879">這個敏感資訊類型實體只有歐盟駕駛執照號碼機密資訊類型提供。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-879">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-880">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-880">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-881">10位數，不含空格及分隔符號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-881">10 digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-882">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-882">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-883">10位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-883">10 digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-884">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-884">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-885">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-885">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-886">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-886">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-887">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-887">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-888">正則運算式會 `Regex_belgium_eu_driver's_license_number` 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-888">The regular expression  `Regex_belgium_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-889">找到來自的關鍵字 `Keywords_belgium_eu_driver's_license_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-889">A keyword from  `Keywords_belgium_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span>
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Driver's License Number -->
<Entity id="b8fe86d1-c056-453b-bfaa-9fe698699ecc" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_belgium_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_belgium_eu_driver's_license_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```
