## <a name="belgium-national-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-911">比利時國號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-911">Belgium national number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="93909-912">這種敏感資訊類型的實體包含在歐盟國身分識別號碼機密資訊類型中，並可作為獨立的機密資訊類型實體。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-912">This sensitive information type entity is included in the EU National Identification Number sensitive information type and is available as a stand alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-913">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-913">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-914">11位數加上分隔符號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-914">11 digits plus delimiters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-915">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-915">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-916">11位數加上分隔符號：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-916">11 digits plus delimiters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-917">以 YY 格式表示的六位數和兩個句點。毫米。出生日期的 DD</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-917">Six digits and two periods in the format YY.MM.DD for date of birth</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-918">連字號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-918">A hyphen</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-919">三個連續數位（奇數用於男生，即便是女生）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-919">Three sequential digits (odd for males, even for females)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-920">一個句點</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-920">A period</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-921">兩位數的檢查碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-921">Two digits that are a check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-922">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-922">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-923">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-923">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-924">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-924">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-925">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-925">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-926">函數 Func_belgium_national_number 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-926">The function Func_belgium_national_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-927">會找到來自 Keyword_belgium_national_number 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-927">A keyword from Keyword_belgium_national_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-928">校驗和通過。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-928">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Belgium National Number -->
  <Entity id="fb969c9e-0fd1-4b18-8091-a2123c5e6a54" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
   <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_belgium_national_number"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_belgium_national_number"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="belgium-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-987">比利時護照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-987">Belgium passport number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="93909-988">這個敏感資訊類型實體只適用于歐盟護照號碼機密資訊類型。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-988">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-989">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-989">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-990">兩個字母后接六位數，不含空格或分隔符號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-990">Two letters followed by six digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-991">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-991">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-992">兩個字母后接六位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-992">Two letters and followed by six digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-993">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-993">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-994">不適用</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-994">Not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-995">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-995">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-996">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-996">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-997">正則運算式會 `Regex_belgium_eu_passport_number` 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-997">The regular expression  `Regex_belgium_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-998">找到來自的關鍵字 `Keywords_belgium_eu_passport_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-998">A keyword from  `Keywords_belgium_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span>

```xml
 <!-- EU Passport Number -->
<Entity id="21883626-6245-4f3d-9b61-5cbb43e625ee" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_belgium__eu_passport_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_belgium_eu_passport_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="belgium-social-security-number-or-equivalent-identification"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-1008">比利時社會安全號碼或對等身分識別</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1008">Belgium social security number or equivalent identification</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="93909-1009">這個敏感資訊類型實體只有歐盟社會保險號碼或同等識別碼的敏感資訊類型提供。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1009">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Social Security Number or Equivalent ID sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-1010">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1010">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-1011">11位數，不含空格或分隔符號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1011">11 digits without spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-1012">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1012">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-1013">11位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1013">11 digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-1014">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1014">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-1015">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1015">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-1016">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1016">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-1017">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是85%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1017">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-1018">函數 `Func_belgium_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` 會找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1018">The function  `Func_belgium_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-1019">找到來自的關鍵字 `Keywords_belgium_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1019">A keyword from  `Keywords_belgium_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="93909-1020">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1020">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-1021">函數 `Func_belgium_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` 會找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1021">The function  `Func_belgium_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU SSN or Equivalent Number -->
<Entity id="d24e32a4-c0bb-4ba8-899d-6303b95742d9" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_belgium_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_belgium_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
        </Pattern> 
       <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_belgium_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
        </Pattern>      
</Entity>
```

## <a name="belgium-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-1041">比利時納稅識別號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1041">Belgium tax identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="93909-1042">這個敏感資訊類型實體只適用于歐盟稅收 Identificaiton 號碼機密資訊類型。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1042">This sensitive information type entity is only available the EU Tax Identificaiton Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-1043">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1043">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-1044">11位數，不含空格及分隔符號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1044">11 digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-1045">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1045">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-1046">11位數：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1046">11 digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-1047">兩位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1047">Two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-1048">"0" 或 "1"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1048">A "0" or "1"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-1049">一個數位</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1049">One digit</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-1050">"0" 或 "1" 或 "2" 或 "3"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1050">A "0" or "1" or "2" or "3"</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-1051">六位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1051">Six digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-1052">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1052">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-1053">不適用</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1053">Not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-1054">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1054">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-1055">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1055">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-1056">正則運算式會 `Regex_belgium_eu_tax_file_number` 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1056">The regular expression  `Regex_belgium_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-1057">找到來自的關鍵字 `Keywords_belgium_eu_tax_file_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1057">A keyword from  `Keywords_belgium_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Tax File Number -->
<Entity id="e09c07d3-66e5-4783-989d-49ac62748f5f" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_belgium_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_belgium_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="brazil-cpf-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-1116">巴西 CPF 號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1116">Brazil CPF number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-1117">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1117">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-1118">11位數包含檢查碼，可格式化或未格式化</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1118">11 digits that include a check digit and can be formatted or unformatted</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-1119">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1119">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-1120">格式 化：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1120">Formatted:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-1121">三位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1121">Three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-1122">一個句點</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1122">A period</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-1123">三位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1123">Three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-1124">一個句點</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1124">A period</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-1125">三位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1125">Three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-1126">連字號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1126">A hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-1127">兩位數的檢查碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1127">Two digits which are check digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-1128">非</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1128">Unformatted:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-1129">11位數的最後兩位數的檢查碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1129">11 digits where the last two digits are check digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-1130">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1130">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-1131">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1131">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-1132">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1132">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-1133">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是85%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1133">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-1134">函數 Func_brazil_cpf 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1134">The function Func_brazil_cpf finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-1135">會找到來自 Keyword_brazil_cpf 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1135">A keyword from Keyword_brazil_cpf is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-1136">校驗和通過。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1136">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-1137">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1137">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-1138">函數 Func_brazil_cpf 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1138">The function Func_brazil_cpf finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-1139">校驗和通過。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1139">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Brazil CPF Number -->
<Entity id="78e09124-f2c3-4656-b32a-c1a132cd2711" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_brazil_cpf"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_brazil_cpf"/>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_brazil_cpf"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="brazil-legal-entity-number-cnpj"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-1151">巴西法律實體編號（CNPJ）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1151">Brazil legal entity number (CNPJ)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-1152">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1152">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-1153">14位數包含登記編號、分支編號及檢查數位，加上分隔符號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1153">14 digits that include a registration number, branch number, and check digits, plus delimiters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-1154">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1154">Pattern</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="93909-1155">14位數，加上分隔符號：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1155">14 digits, plus delimiters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-1156">兩位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1156">Two digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-1157">一個句點</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1157">A period</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-1158">三位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1158">Three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-1159">一個句點</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1159">A period</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-1160">三位數（前八位數為註冊碼）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1160">Three digits (these first eight digits are the registration number)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-1161">一個正斜線</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1161">A forward slash</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-1162">四位數的分支編號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1162">Four-digit branch number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-1163">連字號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1163">A hyphen</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-1164">兩位數的檢查碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1164">Two digits which are check digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-1165">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1165">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-1166">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1166">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-1167">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1167">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-1168">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是85%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1168">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-1169">函數 Func_brazil_cnpj 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1169">The function Func_brazil_cnpj finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-1170">會找到來自 Keyword_brazil_cnpj 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1170">A keyword from Keyword_brazil_cnpj is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-1171">校驗和通過。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1171">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-1172">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1172">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-1173">函數 Func_brazil_cnpj 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1173">The function Func_brazil_cnpj finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-1174">校驗和通過。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1174">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Brazil Legal Entity Number (CNPJ) -->
<Entity id="9b58b5cd-5e90-4df6-b34f-1ebcc88ceae4" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
   <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_brazil_cnpj"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_brazil_cnpj"/>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_brazil_cnpj"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="brazil-national-identification-card-rg"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-1196">巴西國身分識別卡（RG）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1196">Brazil national identification card (RG)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-1197">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1197">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-1198">Registro Geral （舊格式）：九位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1198">Registro Geral (old format): Nine digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-1199">Registro de Identidade （RIC）（新格式）：11位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1199">Registro de Identidade (RIC) (new format): 11 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-1200">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1200">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-1201">Registro Geral （舊格式）：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1201">Registro Geral (old format):</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-1202">兩位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1202">Two digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-1203">一個句點</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1203">A period</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-1204">三位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1204">Three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-1205">一個句點</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1205">A period</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-1206">三位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1206">Three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-1207">連字號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1207">A hyphen</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-1208">一位數的檢查碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1208">One digit which is a check digit</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-1209">Registro de Identidade （RIC）（新格式）：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1209">Registro de Identidade (RIC) (new format):</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-1210">10位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1210">10 digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-1211">連字號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1211">A hyphen</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-1212">一位數的檢查碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1212">One digit which is a check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-1213">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1213">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-1214">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1214">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-1215">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1215">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-1216">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是85%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1216">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-1217">函數 Func_brazil_rg 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1217">The function Func_brazil_rg finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-1218">會找到來自 Keyword_brazil_rg 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1218">A keyword from Keyword_brazil_rg is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-1219">校驗和通過。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1219">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-1220">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1220">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-1221">函數 Func_brazil_rg 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1221">The function Func_brazil_rg finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-1222">校驗和通過。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1222">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Brazil National ID Card (RG) -->
<Entity id="486de900-db70-41b3-a886-abdf25af119c" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_brazil_rg"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_brazil_rg"/>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_brazil_rg"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="bulgaria-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-1233">保加利亞駕駛執照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1233">Bulgaria driver's license number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="93909-1234">這個敏感資訊類型實體只有歐盟駕駛執照號碼機密資訊類型提供。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1234">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-1235">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1235">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-1236">九位數，不含空格及分隔符號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1236">Nine digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-1237">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1237">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-1238">九位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1238">Nine digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-1239">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1239">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-1240">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1240">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-1241">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1241">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-1242">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1242">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-1243">正則運算式會 `Regex_bulgaria_eu_driver's_license_number` 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1243">The regular expression  `Regex_bulgaria_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-1244">找到來自的關鍵字 `Keywords_bulgaria_eu_driver's_license_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1244">A keyword from  `Keywords_bulgaria_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Driver's License Number -->
<Entity id="b8fe86d1-c056-453b-bfaa-9fe698699ecc" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
             <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_bulgaria_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_bulgaria_eu_driver's_license_number" />
        </Pattern> 
</Entity>    
```

## <a name="bulgaria-national-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-1263">保加利亞國身分識別號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1263">Bulgaria national identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="93909-1264">這個敏感資訊類型實體僅可用於歐盟國身分識別號碼的敏感資訊類型。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1264">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU National Identification Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-1265">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1265">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-1266">10位數，不含空格及分隔符號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1266">Ten digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-1267">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1267">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-1268">10位數，不含空格及分隔符號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1268">Ten digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-1269">與出生日期對應的六位數（YYMMDD）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1269">Six digits that correspond to the birth date (YYMMDD)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-1270">對應至出生順序的兩位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1270">Two digits that correspond to the birth order</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-1271">對應于性別的一個數位：用於男的偶數位數和用於女的奇數數位</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1271">One digit that corresponds to gender: An even digit for male and an odd digit for female</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-1272">一個檢查碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1272">One check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-1273">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1273">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-1274">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1274">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-1275">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1275">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-1276">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是85%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1276">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-1277">函數 `Func_bulgaria_eu_national_id_card` 會找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1277">The function  `Func_bulgaria_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-1278">找到來自的關鍵字 `Keywords_bulgaria_national_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1278">A keyword from  `Keywords_bulgaria_national_number` is found.</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="93909-1279">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1279">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-1280">函數 `Func_bulgaria_eu_national_id_card` 會找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1280">The function  `Func_bulgaria_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
<Entity id="419f449f-6d9d-4be1-a154-b531f7a91b41" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_bulgaria_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_bulgaria_national_number" />
        </Pattern>
<Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_bulgaria_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="bulgaria-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-1325">保加利亞護照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1325">Bulgaria passport number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="93909-1326">這個敏感資訊類型實體只適用于歐盟護照號碼機密資訊類型。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1326">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-1327">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1327">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-1328">九位數，不含空格及分隔符號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1328">Nine digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-1329">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1329">Pattern</span></span>

 <span data-ttu-id="93909-1330">九位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1330">Nine digits</span></span> 
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-1331">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1331">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-1332">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1332">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-1333">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1333">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-1334">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1334">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-1335">正則運算式會 `Regex_bulgaria_eu_passport_number` 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1335">The regular expression  `Regex_bulgaria_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-1336">找到來自的關鍵字 `Keywords_bulgaria_eu_passport_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1336">A keyword from  `Keywords_bulgaria_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 

```xml
 <!-- EU Passport Number -->
<Entity id="21883626-6245-4f3d-9b61-5cbb43e625ee" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_bulgaria_eu_passport_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_bulgaria_eu_passport_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```
### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-1337">關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1337">Keywords</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-1338">**Keywords_bulgaria_eu_passport_number**</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1338">**Keywords_bulgaria_eu_passport_number**</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-1339">護照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1339">passport number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-1340">保加利亞文護照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1340">bulgarian passport number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-1341">護照否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1341">passport no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-1342">номер на паспорта</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1342">номер на паспорта</span></span>

## <a name="bulgaria-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-1343">保加利亞納稅識別號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1343">Bulgaria tax identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="93909-1344">此機密資訊類型實體僅可用於歐盟納稅識別碼的敏感資訊類型。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1344">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Tax Identification Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-1345">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1345">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-1346">10位數，不含空格及分隔符號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1346">Ten digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-1347">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1347">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-1348">10位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1348">10 digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-1349">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1349">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-1350">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1350">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-1351">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1351">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-1352">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是85%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1352">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-1353">函數 `Func_bulgaria_eu_tax_file_number` 會找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1353">The function  `Func_bulgaria_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-1354">找到來自的關鍵字 `Keywords_bulgaria_eu_tax_file_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1354">A keyword from  `Keywords_bulgaria_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="93909-1355">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1355">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-1356">函數 `Func_bulgaria_eu_tax_file_number` 會找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1356">The function  `Func_bulgaria_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 

```xml
 <!-- EU Tax File Number -->
<Entity id="e09c07d3-66e5-4783-989d-49ac62748f5f" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_bulgaria_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_bulgaria_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
 <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_bulgaria_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="canada-bank-account-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-1401">加拿大銀行帳戶號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1401">Canada bank account number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-1402">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1402">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-1403">七位數或十二位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1403">Seven or twelve digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-1404">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1404">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-1405">加拿大銀行帳戶號碼為七位數或十二位數。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1405">A Canada Bank Account Number is seven or twelve digits.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-1406">加拿大銀行帳戶中轉號碼為：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1406">A Canada bank account transit number is:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-1407">五位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1407">Five digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-1408">連字號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1408">A hyphen</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-1409">三位數或</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1409">Three digits OR</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-1410">零 "0"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1410">A zero "0"</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-1411">八位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1411">Eight digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-1412">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1412">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-1413">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1413">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-1414">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1414">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-1415">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是85%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1415">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-1416">正則運算式 Regex_canada_bank_account_number 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1416">The regular expression Regex_canada_bank_account_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-1417">會找到來自 Keyword_canada_bank_account_number 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1417">A keyword from Keyword_canada_bank_account_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-1418">正則運算式 Regex_canada_bank_account_transit_number 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1418">The regular expression Regex_canada_bank_account_transit_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-1419">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是85%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1419">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-1420">正則運算式 Regex_canada_bank_account_number 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1420">The regular expression Regex_canada_bank_account_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-1421">會找到來自 Keyword_canada_bank_account_number 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1421">A keyword from Keyword_canada_bank_account_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Canada Bank Account Number -->
<Entity id="552e814c-cb50-4d94-bbaa-bb1d1ffb34de" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_canada_bank_account_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_bank_account_number" />
        <Match idRef="Regex_canada_bank_account_transit_number" />
   </Pattern>
   <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_canada_bank_account_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_bank_account_number" />
   </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="canada-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-1445">加拿大駕駛執照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1445">Canada driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-1446">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1446">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-1447">依省份</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1447">Varies by province</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-1448">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1448">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-1449">涵蓋 Alberta、英屬哥倫比亞、Manitoba、新的 Brunswick、Newfoundland/Labrador、Nova Scotia、安大略、Prince Edward 孤島、魁北克和薩斯的各種模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1449">Various patterns covering Alberta, British Columbia, Manitoba, New Brunswick, Newfoundland/Labrador, Nova Scotia, Ontario, Prince Edward Island, Quebec, and Saskatchewan</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-1450">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1450">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-1451">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1451">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-1452">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1452">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-1453">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1453">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-1454">函數 Func_ [province_name] _drivers_license_number 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1454">The function Func_[province_name]_drivers_license_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-1455">找到來自 Keyword_ [province_name] _drivers_license_name 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1455">A keyword from Keyword_[province_name]_drivers_license_name is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-1456">會找到來自 Keyword_canada_drivers_license 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1456">A keyword from Keyword_canada_drivers_license is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Canada Driver's License Number -->
    <Entity id="37186abb-8e48-4800-ad3c-e3d1610b3db0" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_alberta_drivers_license_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_alberta_drivers_license_name" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_drivers_license" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_british_columbia_drivers_license_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_british_columbia_drivers_license_name" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_drivers_license" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_manitoba_drivers_license_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_manitoba_drivers_license_name" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_drivers_license" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_new_brunswick_drivers_license_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_new_brunswick_drivers_license_name" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_drivers_license" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_newfoundland_labrador_drivers_license_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_newfoundland_labrador_drivers_license_name" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_drivers_license" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_nova_scotia_drivers_license_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_nova_scotia_drivers_license_name" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_drivers_license" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_ontario_drivers_license_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_ontario_drivers_license_name" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_drivers_license" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_prince_edward_island_drivers_license_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_prince_edward_island_drivers_license_name" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_drivers_license" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_quebec_drivers_license_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_quebec_drivers_license_name" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_drivers_license" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_saskatchewan_drivers_license_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_saskatchewan_drivers_license_name" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_drivers_license" />
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

## <a name="canada-health-service-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-1592">加拿大健康情況服務號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1592">Canada health service number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-1593">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1593">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-1594">10位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1594">10 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-1595">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1595">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-1596">10位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1596">10 digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-1597">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1597">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-1598">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1598">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-1599">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1599">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-1600">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1600">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-1601">正則運算式 Regex_canada_health_service_number 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1601">The regular expression Regex_canada_health_service_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-1602">會找到來自 Keyword_canada_health_service_number 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1602">A keyword from Keyword_canada_health_service_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Canada Health Service Number -->
<Entity id="59c0bf39-7fab-482c-af25-00faa4384c94" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_canada_health_service_number" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_health_service_number" />
        </Any>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-1603">關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1603">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_canada_health_service_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-1604">Keyword_canada_health_service_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1604">Keyword_canada_health_service_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="93909-1605">個人健康號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1605">personal health number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-1606">患者資訊</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1606">patient information</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-1607">健康情況服務</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1607">health services</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-1608">speciality 服務</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1608">speciality services</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-1609">汽車意外</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1609">automobile accident</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-1610">病人醫院</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1610">patient hospital</span></span>

## <a name="canada-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-1614">加拿大護照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1614">Canada passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-1615">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1615">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-1616">兩個大寫字母後接六位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1616">Two uppercase letters followed by six digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-1617">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1617">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-1618">兩個大寫字母後接六位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1618">Two uppercase letters followed by six digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-1619">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1619">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-1620">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1620">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-1621">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1621">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-1622">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1622">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-1623">正則運算式 Regex_canada_passport_number 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1623">The regular expression Regex_canada_passport_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-1624">會找到 Keyword_canada_passport_number 或 Keyword_passport 中的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1624">A keyword from Keyword_canada_passport_number or Keyword_passport is found.</span></span>

```xml 
<!-- Canada Passport Number -->
<Entity id="14d0db8b-498a-43ed-9fca-f6097ae687eb" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_canada_passport_number" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_passport_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_passport" />
        </Any>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="canada-personal-health-identification-number-phin"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-1654">加拿大個人健康身分識別號碼（PHIN）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1654">Canada personal health identification number (PHIN)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-1655">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1655">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-1656">九位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1656">Nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-1657">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1657">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-1658">九位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1658">Nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-1659">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1659">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-1660">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1660">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-1661">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1661">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-1662">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：正則運算式 Regex_canada_phin 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1662">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters: The regular expression Regex_canada_phin finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="93909-1663">至少會找到兩個 Keyword_canada_phin 或 Keyword_canada_provinces 中的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1663">At least two keywords from Keyword_canada_phin or Keyword_canada_provinces are found..</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Canada PHIN -->
<Entity id="722e12ac-c89a-4ec8-a1b7-fea3469f89db" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_canada_phin" />
        <Any minMatches="2">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_phin" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_canada_provinces" />
        </Any>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="canada-social-insurance-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-1696">加拿大社交保險號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1696">Canada social insurance number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-1697">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1697">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-1698">具有選擇性連字號或空格的九位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1698">Nine digits with optional hyphens or spaces</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-1699">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1699">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-1700">格式 化：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1700">Formatted:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-1701">三位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1701">Three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-1702">連字號或空格</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1702">A hyphen or space</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-1703">三位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1703">Three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-1704">連字號或空格</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1704">A hyphen or space</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-1705">三位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1705">Three digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-1706">未格式化：九位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1706">Unformatted: Nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-1707">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1707">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-1708">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1708">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-1709">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1709">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-1710">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是85%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1710">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-1711">函數 Func_canadian_sin 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1711">The function Func_canadian_sin finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-1712">下列其中一種組合，至少有兩種：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1712">At least two of any combination of the following:</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="93909-1713">會找到來自 Keyword_sin 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1713">A keyword from Keyword_sin is found.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="93909-1714">會找到來自 Keyword_sin_collaborative 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1714">A keyword from Keyword_sin_collaborative is found.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="93909-1715">函數 Func_eu_date 會找到正確日期格式的日期。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1715">The function Func_eu_date finds a date in the right date format.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-1716">校驗和通過。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1716">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-1717">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1717">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-1718">函數 Func_unformatted_canadian_sin 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1718">The function Func_unformatted_canadian_sin finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-1719">會找到來自 Keyword_sin 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1719">A keyword from Keyword_sin is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-1720">校驗和通過。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1720">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Canada Social Insurance Number -->
<Entity id="a2f29c85-ecb8-4514-a610-364790c0773e" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_canadian_sin" />
        <Any minMatches="2">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_sin" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_sin_collaborative" />
          <Match idRef="Func_eu_date" />
        </Any>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_unformatted_canadian_sin" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_sin" />
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="93909-1731">國家識別號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1731">national identification number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-1732">國家識別碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1732">national id</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="93909-1737">駕駛執照</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1737">driver's license</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-1738">驅動程式授權</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1738">drivers license</span></span>

## <a name="chile-identity-card-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-1745">智利身分識別卡號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1745">Chile identity card number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-1746">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1746">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-1747">7-8 位數加上分隔符號 a check digits 或字母</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1747">7-8 digits plus delimiters a check digit or letter</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-1748">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1748">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-1749">7-8 位數加上分隔符號：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1749">7-8 digits plus delimiters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-1750">1-2 位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1750">1-2 digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-1751">一個句點</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1751">A period</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-1752">三位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1752">Three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-1753">一個句點</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1753">A period</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-1754">三位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1754">Three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-1755">虛線</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1755">A dash</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-1756">一個數位或字母（不區分大小寫），這是一種檢查碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1756">One digit or letter (not case sensitive) which is a check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-1757">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1757">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-1758">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1758">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-1759">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1759">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-1760">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是85%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1760">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-1761">函數 Func_chile_id_card 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1761">The function Func_chile_id_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-1762">會找到來自 Keyword_chile_id_card 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1762">A keyword from Keyword_chile_id_card is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-1763">校驗和通過。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1763">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-1764">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1764">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-1765">函數 Func_chile_id_card 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1765">The function Func_chile_id_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-1766">校驗和通過。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1766">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Chile Identity Card Number -->
<Entity id="4e979794-49a0-407e-a0b9-2c536937b925" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_chile_id_card"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_chile_id_card"/>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_chile_id_card"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="china-resident-identity-card-prc-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-1781">中國居民身分識別卡片（中國）號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1781">China resident identity card (PRC) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-1782">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1782">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-1783">18位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1783">18 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-1784">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1784">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-1785">18位數：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1785">18 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-1786">六位數的位址碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1786">Six digits which are an address code</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-1787">在 YYYYMMDD 中的八位數（出生日期）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1787">Eight digits in the form YYYYMMDD which are the date of birth</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-1788">三位數的訂單碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1788">Three digits which are an order code</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-1789">一位數的檢查碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1789">One digit which is a check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-1790">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1790">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-1791">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1791">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-1792">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1792">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-1793">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是85%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1793">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-1794">函數 Func_china_resident_id 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1794">The function Func_china_resident_id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-1795">會找到來自 Keyword_china_resident_id 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1795">A keyword from Keyword_china_resident_id is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-1796">校驗和通過。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1796">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-1797">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1797">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-1798">函數 Func_china_resident_id 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1798">The function Func_china_resident_id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-1799">校驗和通過。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1799">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- China Resident Identity Card (PRC) Number -->
<Entity id="c92daa86-2d16-4871-901f-816b3f554fc1" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_china_resident_id"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_china_resident_id"/>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_china_resident_id"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="93909-1802">常駐身分識別卡</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1802">Resident Identity Card</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-1803">中國</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1803">PRC</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-1804">全國身分識別卡</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1804">National Identification Card</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-1805">身份證</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1805">身份证</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="93909-1807">居民身份證</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1807">居民身份证</span></span>

## <a name="credit-card-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-1812">信用卡號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1812">Credit card number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-1813">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1813">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-1814">14至16位數，可格式化或未格式化（dddddddddddddddd），且必須透過 Luhn 測試。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1814">14 to 16 digits which can be formatted or unformatted (dddddddddddddddd) and which must pass the Luhn test.</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-1815">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1815">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-1816">非常複雜且健全的模式，可偵測全球所有主要品牌的卡，包括簽證、MasterCard、探索卡、JCB、美洲 Express、禮品卡和 diner 卡。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1816">Very complex and robust pattern that detects cards from all major brands worldwide, including Visa, MasterCard, Discover Card, JCB, American Express, gift cards, and diner cards.</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-1817">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1817">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-1818">是，Luhn 檢查碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1818">Yes, the Luhn checksum</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-1819">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1819">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-1820">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是85%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1820">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-1821">函數 Func_credit_card 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1821">The function Func_credit_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-1822">下列其中一項為真：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1822">One of the following is true:</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="93909-1823">會找到來自 Keyword_cc_verification 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1823">A keyword from Keyword_cc_verification is found.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="93909-1824">會找到來自 Keyword_cc_name 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1824">A keyword from Keyword_cc_name is found.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="93909-1825">函數 Func_expiration_date 會找到正確日期格式的日期。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1825">The function Func_expiration_date finds a date in the right date format.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-1826">校驗和通過。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1826">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-1827">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是65%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1827">A DLP policy is 65% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-1828">函數 Func_credit_card 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1828">The function Func_credit_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-1829">校驗和通過。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-1829">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Credit Card Number -->
<Entity id="50842eb7-edc8-4019-85dd-5a5c1f2bb085" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_credit_card" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_cc_verification" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_cc_name" />
          <Match idRef="Func_expiration_date" />
        </Any>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_credit_card" />
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="croatia-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-2035">克羅地亞駕駛執照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2035">Croatia driver's license number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="93909-2036">這個敏感資訊類型實體只有歐盟駕駛執照號碼機密資訊類型提供。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2036">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-2037">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2037">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-2038">不含空格及分隔符號的八位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2038">Eight digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-2039">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2039">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-2040">八位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2040">Eight digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-2041">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2041">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-2042">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2042">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-2043">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2043">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-2044">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2044">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-2045">正則運算式會 `Regex_croatia_eu_driver's_license_number` 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2045">The regular expression  `Regex_croatia_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-2046">找到來自的關鍵字 `Keywords_croatia_eu_driver's_license_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2046">A keyword from  `Keywords_croatia_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 

```xml
 <!-- EU Driver's License Number -->
<Entity id="b8fe86d1-c056-453b-bfaa-9fe698699ecc" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_croatia_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_croatia_eu_driver's_license_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="croatia-identity-card-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-2062">克羅地亞身分識別卡號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2062">Croatia identity card number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="93909-2063">這種敏感資訊類型的實體包含在歐盟國身分識別號碼機密資訊類型中，並可作為獨立的機密資訊類型實體。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2063">This sensitive information type entity is included in the EU National Identification Number sensitive information type and is available as a stand alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>


### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-2064">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2064">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-2065">九位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2065">Nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-2066">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2066">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-2067">九個連續數位</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2067">Nine consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-2068">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2068">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-2069">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2069">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-2070">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2070">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-2071">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2071">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-2072">函數 Func_croatia_id_card 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2072">The function Func_croatia_id_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-2073">會找到來自 Keyword_croatia_id_card 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2073">A keyword from Keyword_croatia_id_card is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!--Croatia Identity Card Number-->
<Entity id="ff12f884-c20a-4189-b185-34c8e7258d47" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_croatia_id_card"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_croatia_id_card"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```
