## <a name="croatia-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-2104">克羅地亞護照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2104">Croatia passport number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="93909-2105">這個敏感資訊類型實體只適用于歐盟護照號碼機密資訊類型。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2105">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-2106">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2106">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-2107">九位數，不含空格及分隔符號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2107">Nine digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-2108">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2108">Pattern</span></span>

 <span data-ttu-id="93909-2109">九位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2109">Nine digits</span></span> 
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-2110">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2110">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-2111">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2111">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-2112">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2112">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-2113">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2113">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-2114">正則運算式會 `Regex_croatia_eu_passport_number` 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2114">The regular expression  `Regex_croatia_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-2115">找到來自的關鍵字 `Keywords_croatia_eu_passport_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2115">A keyword from  `Keywords_croatia_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Passport Number -->
<Entity id="21883626-6245-4f3d-9b61-5cbb43e625ee" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_croatia_eu_passport_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_croatia_eu_passport_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```
### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-2116">關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2116">Keywords</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-2117">**Keywords_croatia_eu_passport_number**</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2117">**Keywords_croatia_eu_passport_number**</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="93909-2118">護照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2118">passport number</span></span>

## <a name="croatia-personal-identification-oib-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-2122">克羅地亞個人身分識別（OIB）號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2122">Croatia personal identification (OIB) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-2123">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2123">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-2124">11位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2124">11 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-2125">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2125">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-2126">11位數：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2126">11 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-2127">10位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2127">10 digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-2128">最後一個數位是檢查碼用於國際資料交換的目的，在11位數之前新增字母「HR」。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2128">Final digit is a check digit For the purposes of international data exchange, the letters HR are added preceding the eleven digits.</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-2129">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2129">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-2130">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2130">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-2131">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2131">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-2132">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是85%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2132">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-2133">函數 Func_croatia_oib_number 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2133">The function Func_croatia_oib_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-2134">會找到來自 Keyword_croatia_oib_number 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2134">A keyword from Keyword_croatia_oib_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-2135">校驗和通過。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2135">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-2136">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2136">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-2137">函數 Func_croatia_oib_number 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2137">The function Func_croatia_oib_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-2138">校驗和通過。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2138">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Croatia Personal Identification (OIB) Number -->
<Entity id="31983b6d-db95-4eb2-a630-b44bd091968d" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_croatia_oib_number"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_croatia_oib_number"/>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_croatia_oib_number"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="croatia-social-security-number-or-equivalent-identification"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-2144">克羅地亞社會安全號碼或同等身分識別</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2144">Croatia social security number or equivalent identification</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="93909-2145">這個敏感資訊類型實體只有歐盟社會保險號碼或同等識別碼的敏感資訊類型提供。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2145">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Social Security Number or Equivalent ID sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-2146">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2146">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-2147">11位數，不含空格及分隔符號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2147">11 digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-2148">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2148">Pattern</span></span>

 <span data-ttu-id="93909-2149">11位數：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2149">11 digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-2150">10位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2150">Ten digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-2151">一個檢查碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2151">One check digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-2152">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2152">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-2153">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2153">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-2154">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2154">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-2155">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是85%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2155">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-2156">函數 `Func_croatia_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` 會找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2156">The function  `Func_croatia_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-2157">找到來自的關鍵字 `Keywords_croatia_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2157">A keyword from  `Keywords_croatia_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="93909-2158">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2158">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-2159">函數 `Func_croatia_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` 會找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2159">The function  `Func_croatia_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU SSN or Equivalent Number -->
<Entity id="d24e32a4-c0bb-4ba8-899d-6303b95742d9" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_croatia_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_croatia_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
        </Pattern> 
       <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_croatia_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
        </Pattern>      
</Entity>
```

## <a name="croatia-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-2176">克羅地亞納稅識別號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2176">Croatia tax identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="93909-2177">這個敏感資訊類型實體只適用于歐盟稅收 Identificaiton 號碼機密資訊類型。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2177">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Tax Identificaiton Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-2179">11位數，不含空格或分隔符號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2179">11 digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-2180">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2180">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-2181">11位數：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2181">11 digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-2182">10位數（隨機播放）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2182">Ten digits, randomly chosen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-2183">一個檢查碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2183">One check digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-2184">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2184">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-2185">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2185">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-2186">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2186">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-2187">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是85%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2187">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-2188">函數 `Func_croatia_eu_tax_file_number` 會找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2188">The function  `Func_croatia_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-2189">找到來自的關鍵字 `Keywords_croatia_eu_tax_file_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2189">A keyword from  `Keywords_croatia_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="93909-2190">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2190">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-2191">函數 `Func_croatia_eu_tax_file_number` 會找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2191">The function  `Func_croatia_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Tax File Number -->
<Entity id="e09c07d3-66e5-4783-989d-49ac62748f5f" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_croatia_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_croatia_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
<Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_croatia_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="cyprus-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-2222">賽普勒斯驅動程式授權號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2222">Cyprus drivers license number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="93909-2223">這個敏感資訊類型實體只有歐盟駕駛執照號碼機密資訊類型提供。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2223">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-2224">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2224">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-2225">12位數，不含空格及分隔符號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2225">12 digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-2226">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2226">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-2227">12位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2227">12 digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-2228">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2228">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-2229">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2229">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-2230">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2230">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-2231">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2231">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-2232">正則運算式會 `Regex_cyprus_eu_driver's_license_number` 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2232">The regular expression  `Regex_cyprus_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_cyprus_eu_driver's_license_number" />

        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="cyprus-national-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-2248">賽普勒斯國身分識別號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2248">Cyprus national identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="93909-2249">這個敏感資訊類型實體僅可用於歐盟國身分識別號碼的敏感資訊類型。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2249">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU National Identification Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-2250">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2250">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-2251">10位數，不含空格及分隔符號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2251">Ten digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-2252">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2252">Pattern</span></span>

 <span data-ttu-id="93909-2253">10位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2253">Ten digits</span></span> 
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-2254">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2254">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-2255">不適用</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2255">Not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-2256">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2256">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-2257">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2257">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-2258">正則運算式會 `Regex_cyprus_eu_national_id_card` 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2258">The regular expression  `Regex_cyprus_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-2259">找到來自的關鍵字 `Keywords_cyprus_eu_national_id_card` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2259">A keyword from  `Keywords_cyprus_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml 
<Entity id="419f449f-6d9d-4be1-a154-b531f7a91b41" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_cyprus_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_cyprus_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="cyprus-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-2268">賽普勒斯護照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2268">Cyprus passport number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="93909-2269">這個敏感資訊類型實體只適用于歐盟護照號碼機密資訊類型。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2269">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-2270">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2270">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-2271">一個字母后接6-8 位數，沒有空格或分隔符號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2271">One letter followed by 6-8 digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-2272">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2272">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-2273">一個字母后接六個到八位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2273">One letter followed by six to eight digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-2274">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2274">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-2275">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2275">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-2276">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2276">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-2277">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2277">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-2278">正則運算式會 `Regex_cyprus_eu_passport_number` 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2278">The regular expression  `Regex_cyprus_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-2279">找到來自的關鍵字 `Keywords_cyprus_eu_passport_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2279">A keyword from  `Keywords_cyprus_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Passport Number -->
<Entity id="21883626-6245-4f3d-9b61-5cbb43e625ee" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_cyprus_eu_passport_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_cyprus_eu_passport_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-2280">關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2280">Keywords</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-2281">**Keywords_cyprus_eu_passport_number**</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2281">**Keywords_cyprus_eu_passport_number**</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="93909-2282">護照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2282">passport number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="93909-2284">護照否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2284">passport no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-2285">αριθμό διαβατηρίου</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2285">αριθμό διαβατηρίου</span></span>

## <a name="cyprus-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-2286">賽普勒斯納稅識別號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2286">Cyprus tax identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="93909-2287">此機密資訊類型實體僅可用於歐盟納稅識別碼的敏感資訊類型。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2287">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Tax Identification Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-2288">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2288">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-2289">指定的模式中的八位數和一個字母</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2289">Eight digits and one letter in the specified pattern</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-2290">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2290">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-2291">八位數和一個字母：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2291">Eight digits and one letter:</span></span>
  
-  <span data-ttu-id="93909-2292">為 "0"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2292">A "0"</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-2293">七位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2293">Seven digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-2294">一個字母（不區分大小寫）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2294">One letter (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-2295">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2295">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-2296">不適用</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2296">Not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-2297">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2297">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-2298">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是85%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2298">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-2299">函數 `Func_cyprus_eu_tax_file_number` 會找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2299">The function  `Func_cyprus_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-2300">找到來自的關鍵字 `Keywords_cyprus_eu_tax_file_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2300">A keyword from  `Keywords_cyprus_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="93909-2301">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2301">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-2302">函數 `Func_cyprus_eu_tax_file_number` 會找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2302">The function  `Func_cyprus_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Tax File Number -->
<Entity id="e09c07d3-66e5-4783-989d-49ac62748f5f" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_cyprus_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_cyprus_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_cyprus_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="czech-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-2331">捷克文駕駛執照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2331">Czech driver's license number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="93909-2332">這個敏感資訊類型實體只有歐盟駕駛執照號碼機密資訊類型提供。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2332">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-2333">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2333">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-2334">兩個字母后接六位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2334">Two letters followed by six digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-2335">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2335">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-2336">8個字母和數位：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2336">Eight letters and digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-2337">兩個字母（不區分大小寫）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2337">Two letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-2338">一個空格（選用）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2338">A space (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-2339">六位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2339">Six digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-2340">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2340">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-2341">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2341">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-2342">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2342">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-2343">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2343">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-2344">正則運算式會 `Regex_czech_republic_eu_driver's_license_number` 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2344">The regular expression  `Regex_czech_republic_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-2345">找到來自的關鍵字 `Keywords_czech_republic_eu_driver's_license_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2345">A keyword from  `Keywords_czech_republic_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 

```xml
 <!-- EU Driver's License Number -->
<Entity id="b8fe86d1-c056-453b-bfaa-9fe698699ecc" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_czech_republic_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_czech_republic_eu_driver's_license_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>

```

## <a name="czech-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-2362">捷克護照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2362">Czech passport number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="93909-2363">這個敏感資訊類型實體只適用于歐盟護照號碼機密資訊類型。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2363">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-2364">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2364">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-2365">不含空格或分隔符號的八位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2365">Eight digits without spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-2366">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2366">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-2367">不含空格或分隔符號的八位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2367">Eight digits without spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-2368">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2368">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-2369">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2369">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-2370">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2370">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-2371">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2371">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-2372">正則運算式會 `Regex_czech_republic_eu_passport_number` 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2372">The regular expression  `Regex_czech_republic_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-2373">找到來自的關鍵字 `Keywords_czech_republic_eu_passport_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2373">A keyword from  `Keywords_czech_republic_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Passport Number -->
<Entity id="21883626-6245-4f3d-9b61-5cbb43e625ee" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_czech_republic_eu_passport_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_czech_republic_eu_passport_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-2374">關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2374">Keywords</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-2375">**Keywords_czech_republic_eu_passport_number**</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2375">**Keywords_czech_republic_eu_passport_number**</span></span>

## <a name="czech-personal-identity-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-2381">捷克個人身分識別號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2381">Czech personal identity number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="93909-2382">這種機密資訊類型的實體包含在歐盟的身分識別號碼束中，並可作為獨立的敏感資訊類型實體。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2382">This sensitive information type entity is included in the EU National identification number bundle and is available as a stand alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-2383">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2383">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-2384">具有選用正斜線的九位數（舊格式）10位數（選用反斜線（新格式））</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2384">Nine digits with optional forward slash (old format) 10 digits with optional forward slash (new format)</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-2385">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2385">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-2386">九位數（舊格式）：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2386">Nine digits (old format):</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-2387">九位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2387">Nine digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-2388">OR</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2388">OR</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="93909-2389">六位數代表出生日期</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2389">Six digits that represent date of birth</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-2390">一個正斜線</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2390">A forward slash</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-2391">三位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2391">Three digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-2392">10位數（新格式）：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2392">10 digits (new format):</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-2393">10位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2393">10 digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-2394">OR</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2394">OR</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="93909-2395">六位數代表出生日期</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2395">Six digits that represent date of birth</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-2396">一個正斜線</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2396">A forward slash</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-2397">最後一個數位是檢查碼的四位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2397">Four digits where last digit is a check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-2398">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2398">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-2399">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2399">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-2400">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2400">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-2401">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是85%：函數 Func_czech_id_card 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2401">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters: The function Func_czech_id_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="93909-2402">會找到來自 Keyword_czech_id_card 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2402">A keyword from Keyword_czech_id_card is found.</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="93909-2403">校驗和通過。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2403">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Czech Personal Identity Number -->
<Entity id="60c0725a-4eb6-455b-9dda-05d8a7396497"      patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
   <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
      <IdMatch idRef="Func_czech_id_card" />
      <Match idRef="Keyword_czech_id_card" />
   </Pattern>
</Entity>
```
### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-2404">關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2404">Keywords</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="93909-2405">捷克個人身分識別號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2405">czech personal identity number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-2406">Rodné číslo</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2406">Rodné číslo</span></span>



## <a name="czech-social-security-number-or-equivalent-identification"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-2407">捷克社會安全號碼或同等身分識別</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2407">Czech social security number or equivalent identification</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="93909-2408">這個敏感資訊類型實體只有歐盟社會保險號碼或同等識別碼的敏感資訊類型提供。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2408">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Social Security Number or Equivalent ID sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-2409">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2409">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-2410">指定之模式中的10位數和反斜線</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2410">Ten digits and a backslash in the specified pattern</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-2411">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2411">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-2412">10位數和反斜線：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2412">Ten digits and a backslash:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-2413">對應至出生日期的六位數（YYMMDD）：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2413">Six digits that correspond to the birth date (YYMMDD):</span></span> 
    
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-2414">反斜線</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2414">A backslash</span></span>
    
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-2415">三位數的數位，對應至在相同日期出生的人員</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2415">Three digits that correspond to a serial number that separates persons born on the same date</span></span>
    
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-2416">一個檢查碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2416">One check digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-2417">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2417">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-2418">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2418">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-2419">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2419">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-2420">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是85%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2420">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-2421">函數 `Func_czech_republic_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` 會找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2421">The function  `Func_czech_republic_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-2422">找到來自的關鍵字 `Keywords_czech_republic_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2422">A keyword from  `Keywords_czech_republic_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="93909-2423">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2423">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-2424">函數 `Func_czech_republic_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` 會找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2424">The function  `Func_czech_republic_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 

```xml
 <!-- EU SSN or Equivalent Number -->
<Entity id="d24e32a4-c0bb-4ba8-899d-6303b95742d9" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_czech_republic_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_czech_republic_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
        </Pattern> 
       <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_czech_republic_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
        </Pattern>      
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-2425">關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2425">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_czech_republic_eu_ssn_or_equivalent"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-2426">Keywords_czech_republic_eu_ssn_or_equivalent</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2426">Keywords_czech_republic_eu_ssn_or_equivalent</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="93909-2429">個人身分識別號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2429">personal identification number</span></span>

## <a name="czech-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-2440">捷克納稅識別號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2440">Czech tax identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="93909-2441">此機密資訊類型實體僅可用於歐盟納稅識別碼的敏感資訊類型。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2441">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Tax Identification Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-2442">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2442">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-2443">九位數和10位數（選用反斜線）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2443">Nine or ten digits with an optional backslash</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-2444">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2444">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-2445">九位數或十位數，具有選用的 backslashl：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2445">Nine or ten digits with an optional backslashl:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-2446">六位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2446">Six digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-2447">反斜線（選用）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2447">A backslash (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-2448">三位數或四位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2448">Three or four digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-2449">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2449">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-2450">不適用</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2450">Not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-2451">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2451">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-2452">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2452">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-2453">正則運算式會 `Regex_czech_republic_eu_tax_file_number` 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2453">The regular expression  `Regex_czech_republic_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-2454">找到來自的關鍵字 `Keywords_czech_republic_eu_tax_file_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2454">A keyword from  `Keywords_czech_republic_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Tax File Number -->
<Entity id="e09c07d3-66e5-4783-989d-49ac62748f5f" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_czech_republic_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_czech_republic_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="denmark-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-2493">丹麥駕照編號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2493">Denmark driver's license number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="93909-2494">這個敏感資訊類型實體只有歐盟駕駛執照號碼機密資訊類型提供。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2494">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-2495">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2495">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-2496">不含空格及分隔符號的八位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2496">Eight digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-2497">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2497">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-2498">八位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2498">Eight digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-2499">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2499">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-2500">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2500">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-2501">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2501">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-2502">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2502">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-2503">正則運算式會 `Regex_denmark_eu_driver's_license_number` 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2503">The regular expression  `Regex_denmark_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-2504">找到來自的關鍵字 `Keywords_denmark_eu_driver's_license_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2504">A keyword from  `Keywords_denmark_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Driver's License Number -->
<Entity id="b8fe86d1-c056-453b-bfaa-9fe698699ecc" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_denmark_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_denmark_eu_driver's_license_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="denmark-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-2521">丹麥護照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2521">Denmark passport number</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-2528">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2528">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-2529">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2529">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-2530">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2530">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-2531">正則運算式會 `Regex_denmark_eu_passport_number` 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2531">The regular expression  `Regex_denmark_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-2532">找到來自的關鍵字 `Keywords_denmark_eu_passport_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2532">A keyword from  `Keywords_denmark_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Passport Number -->
<Entity id="21883626-6245-4f3d-9b61-5cbb43e625ee" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_denmark_eu_passport_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_denmark_eu_passport_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="denmark-personal-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-2540">丹麥個人身分識別號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2540">Denmark personal identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="93909-2541">這種敏感資訊類型的實體包含在歐盟國身分識別號碼機密資訊類型中，並可作為獨立的機密資訊類型實體。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2541">This sensitive information type entity is included in the EU National Identification Number sensitive information type and is available as a stand alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-2542">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2542">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-2543">10位數包含連字號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2543">10 digits containing a hyphen</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-2544">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2544">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-2545">10位數：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2545">10 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-2546">DDMMYY 之日期格式的六位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2546">Six digits in the format DDMMYY which are the date of birth</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-2547">連字號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2547">A hyphen</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-2548">四位數的最後一個數位是檢查碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2548">Four digits where the final digit is a check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-2549">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2549">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-2550">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2550">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-2551">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2551">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-2552">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：正則運算式 Regex_denmark_id 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2552">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters: The regular expression Regex_denmark_id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="93909-2553">會找到來自 Keyword_denmark_id 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2553">A keyword from Keyword_denmark_id is found.</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="93909-2554">校驗和通過。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2554">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Denmark Personal Identification Number -->
<Entity id="6c4f2fef-56e1-4c00-8093-88d7a01cf460" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Regex_denmark_id"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_denmark_id"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="denmark-social-security-number-or-equivalent-identification"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-2606">丹麥社會安全號碼或對等身分識別</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2606">Denmark social security number or equivalent identification</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="93909-2607">這個敏感資訊類型實體只有歐盟社會保險號碼或同等識別碼的敏感資訊類型。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2607">This sensitive information type entity is only available the EU Social Security Number or Equivalent ID sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-2608">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2608">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-2609">在指定的模式中，10位數和連字號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2609">Ten digits and a hyphen in the specified pattern</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-2610">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2610">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-2611">10位數和連字號：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2611">Ten digits and a hyphen:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-2612">與出生日期對應的六位數（DDMMYY）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2612">Six digits that correspond to the birth date (DDMMYY)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-2613">連字號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2613">A hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-2614">對應至序號的四位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2614">Four digits that correspond to a sequence number</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-2615">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2615">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-2616">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2616">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-2617">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2617">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-2618">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是85%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2618">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-2619">函數 `Func_denmark_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` 會找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2619">The function  `Func_denmark_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-2620">找到來自的關鍵字 `Keywords_denmark_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2620">A keyword from  `Keywords_denmark_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="93909-2621">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2621">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-2622">函數 `Func_denmark_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` 會找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2622">The function  `Func_denmark_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU SSN or Equivalent Number -->
<Entity id="d24e32a4-c0bb-4ba8-899d-6303b95742d9" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_denmark_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_denmark_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
        </Pattern> 
       <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_denmark_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
        </Pattern>      
</Entity>
```

## <a name="denmark-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-2636">丹麥納稅識別號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2636">Denmark tax identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="93909-2637">此機密資訊類型實體僅可用於歐盟納稅識別碼的敏感資訊類型。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2637">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Tax Identification Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-2638">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2638">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-2639">10位數包含連字號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2639">Ten digits containing a hyphen</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-2640">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2640">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-2641">10位數包含 hyphenl：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2641">Ten digits containing a hyphenl:</span></span>
  
-  <span data-ttu-id="93909-2642">與出生日期對應的六位數（DDMMYY）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2642">Six digits that correspond to the birth date (DDMMYY)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-2643">連字號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2643">A hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-2644">四位數的數位，其中第一個數位對應到出生的世紀，最後一個數位對應于個人的性別（對男為奇數，甚至是女）。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2644">Four digits that correspond to a sequence number where the first digit corresponds to the century of birth and the last digit corresponds to the individual's gender (odd for male and even for female)</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-2645">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2645">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-2646">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2646">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-2647">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2647">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-2648">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是85%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2648">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-2649">函數 `Func_denmark_eu_tax_file_number` 會找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2649">The function  `Func_denmark_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-2650">找到來自的關鍵字 `Keywords_denmark_eu_tax_file_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2650">A keyword from  `Keywords_denmark_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="93909-2651">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2651">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-2652">函數 `Func_denmark_eu_tax_file_number` 會找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2652">The function  `Func_denmark_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Tax File Number -->
<Entity id="e09c07d3-66e5-4783-989d-49ac62748f5f" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_denmark_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_denmark_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern> 
<Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_denmark_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="drug-enforcement-agency-dea-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-2704">藥品強制代理人（DEA）號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2704">Drug Enforcement Agency (DEA) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-2705">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2705">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-2706">兩個字母后接7位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2706">Two letters followed by seven digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-2707">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2707">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-2708">模式必須包含下列各項：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2708">Pattern must include all of the following:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-2709">這組可能字母的一個字母（不區分大小寫）： abcdefghjklmnprstux，也就是報名者程式碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2709">One letter (not case sensitive) from this set of possible letters: abcdefghjklmnprstux, which is a registrant code</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-2710">一個字母（不區分大小寫），這是報名者姓氏的第一個字母</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2710">One letter (not case sensitive), which is the first letter of the registrant's last name</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-2711">七位數，最後一個是檢查碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2711">Seven digits, the last of which is the check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-2712">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2712">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-2713">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2713">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-2714">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2714">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-2715">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是85%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2715">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-2716">函數 Func_dea_number 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2716">The function Func_dea_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-2717">校驗和通過。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2717">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- DEA Number -->
<Entity id="9a5445ad-406e-43eb-8bd7-cac17ab6d0e4" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_dea_number"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-2718">關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2718">Keywords</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-2719">無</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2719">None</span></span>

## <a name="estonia-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-2720">愛沙尼亞駕照編號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2720">Estonia driver's license number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="93909-2721">這個敏感資訊類型實體只有歐盟駕駛執照號碼機密資訊類型提供。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2721">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-2722">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2722">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-2723">兩個字母后接六位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2723">Two letters followed by six digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-2724">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2724">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-2725">兩個字母和六位數：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2725">Two letters and six digits:</span></span>
  
-  <span data-ttu-id="93909-2726">字母 "ET" （不區分大小寫）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2726">The letters "ET" (not case-sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-2727">六位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2727">Six digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-2728">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2728">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-2729">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2729">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-2730">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2730">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-2731">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2731">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-2732">正則運算式會 `Regex_estonia_eu_driver's_license_number` 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2732">The regular expression  `Regex_estonia_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-2733">找到來自的關鍵字 `Keywords_estonia_eu_driver's_license_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2733">A keyword from  `Keywords_estonia_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Driver's License Number -->
<Entity id="b8fe86d1-c056-453b-bfaa-9fe698699ecc" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_estonia_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_estonia_eu_driver's_license_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-2734">關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2734">Keywords</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-2735">**Keywords_estonia_eu_driver ' s_license_number**</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2735">**Keywords_estonia_eu_driver's_license_number**</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="93909-2736">Dl#</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2736">dl#</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="93909-2738">駕駛執照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2738">driver license number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-2739">駕駛執照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2739">driver license number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-2740">驅動程式許可證</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2740">driver licence</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-2741">驅動程式 .lic。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2741">drivers lic.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-2742">驅動程式授權</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2742">drivers license</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-2743">驅動程式許可證</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2743">drivers licence</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-2744">駕駛執照</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2744">driver's license</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-2745">駕駛執照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2745">driver's license number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-2746">駕駛執照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2746">driving license number</span></span>

## <a name="estonia-national-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-2749">愛沙尼亞國身分識別號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2749">Estonia national identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="93909-2750">這個敏感資訊類型實體僅可用於歐盟國身分識別號碼的敏感資訊類型。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2750">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU National Identification Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-2751">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2751">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-2752">11位數，不含空格及分隔符號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2752">11 digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-2753">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2753">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-2754">11位數：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2754">11 digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-2755">對應于性別和世紀的一位數（奇數號男，甚至是數位女; 1-2：19世紀; 3-4：20世紀; 5-6：21世紀）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2755">One digit that corresponds to sex and century of birth (odd number male, even number female; 1-2: 19th century; 3-4: 20th century; 5-6: 21st century)</span></span>
    
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-2756">對應至出生日期的六位數（YYMMDD）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2756">Six digits that correspond to date of birth (YYMMDD)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-2757">三位數，對應至在相同日期出生的人員的序號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2757">Three digits that correspond to a serial number separating persons born on the same date</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-2758">一個檢查碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2758">One check digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-2759">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2759">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-2760">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2760">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-2761">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2761">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-2762">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是85%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2762">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-2763">函數 `Func_estonia_eu_national_id_card` 會找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2763">The function  `Func_estonia_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-2764">找到來自的關鍵字 `Keywords_estonia_eu_national_id_card` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2764">A keyword from  `Keywords_estonia_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="93909-2765">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2765">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-2766">函數 `Func_estonia_eu_national_id_card` 會找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2766">The function  `Func_estonia_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 
<Entity id="419f449f-6d9d-4be1-a154-b531f7a91b41" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_estonia_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_estonia_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
<Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_estonia_eu_national_id_card" />
</Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="estonia-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-2799">愛沙尼亞護照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2799">Estonia passport number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="93909-2800">這個敏感資訊類型實體只適用于歐盟護照號碼機密資訊類型。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2800">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-2801">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2801">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-2802">一個字母后接7位數，不含空格或分隔符號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2802">One letter followed by seven digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-2803">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2803">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-2804">一個字母后接7位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2804">One letter followed by seven digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-2805">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2805">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-2806">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2806">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-2807">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2807">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-2808">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2808">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-2809">正則運算式會 `Regex_estonia_eu_passport_number` 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2809">The regular expression  `Regex_estonia_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-2810">找到來自的關鍵字 `Keywords_estonia_eu_passport_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2810">A keyword from  `Keywords_estonia_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Passport Number -->
<Entity id="21883626-6245-4f3d-9b61-5cbb43e625ee" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_estonia_eu_passport_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_estonia_eu_passport_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-2811">關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2811">Keywords</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-2812">**Keywords_estonia_eu_passport_number**</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2812">**Keywords_estonia_eu_passport_number**</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="93909-2813">護照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2813">passport number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-2814">愛沙尼亞文護照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2814">estonian passport number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-2815">護照否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2815">passport no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-2816">eesti kodaniku 傳遞</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2816">eesti kodaniku pass</span></span>

## <a name="estonia-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-2817">愛沙尼亞納稅識別號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2817">Estonia tax identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="93909-2818">此機密資訊類型實體僅可用於歐盟納稅識別碼的敏感資訊類型。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2818">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Tax Identification Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-2819">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2819">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-2820">11位數，不含空格或分隔符號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2820">11 digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-2821">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2821">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-2822">11位數：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2822">11 digits:</span></span>
  
-  <span data-ttu-id="93909-2823">一種對應到性別和世紀的數位，其奇數表示男和偶數表示女，如下所示：1，2代表19世紀;3，4代表20世紀;21世紀的5，6</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2823">One digit that corresponds to gender and century of birth where an odd number indicates male and the even number indicates female as follows: 1, 2 for the 19th century; 3, 4 for the 20th century; and 5, 6 for the 21st century</span></span> 
    
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-2824">對應至出生日期的六位數（YYMMDD）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2824">Six digits that correspond to birth date (YYMMDD)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-2825">三位數，對應至在相同日期出生的人員的序號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2825">Three digits that correspond to a serial number separating persons born on the same date</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-2826">一個檢查碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2826">One check digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-2827">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2827">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-2828">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2828">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-2829">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2829">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-2830">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是85%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2830">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-2831">函數 `Func_estonia_eu_tax_file_number` 會找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2831">The function  `Func_estonia_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-2832">找到來自的關鍵字 `Keywords_estonia_eu_tax_file_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2832">A keyword from  `Keywords_estonia_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="93909-2833">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2833">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-2834">函數 `Func_estonia_eu_tax_file_number` 會找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2834">The function  `Func_estonia_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Tax File Number -->
<Entity id="e09c07d3-66e5-4783-989d-49ac62748f5f" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_estonia_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_estonia_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
<Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_estonia_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```
