## <a name="eu-debit-card-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-2867">歐盟借方卡號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2867">EU debit card number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-2868">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2868">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-2869">16位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2869">16 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-2870">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2870">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-2871">非常複雜且健全的模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2871">Very complex and robust pattern</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-2872">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2872">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-2873">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2873">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-2874">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2874">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-2875">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是85%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2875">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-2876">函數 Func_eu_debit_card 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2876">The function Func_eu_debit_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-2877">下列專案中至少有一個為真：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2877">At least one of the following is true:</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="93909-2878">會找到來自 Keyword_eu_debit_card 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2878">A keyword from Keyword_eu_debit_card is found.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="93909-2879">會找到來自 Keyword_card_terms_dict 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2879">A keyword from Keyword_card_terms_dict is found.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="93909-2880">會找到來自 Keyword_card_security_terms_dict 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2880">A keyword from Keyword_card_security_terms_dict is found.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="93909-2881">會找到來自 Keyword_card_expiration_terms_dict 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2881">A keyword from Keyword_card_expiration_terms_dict is found.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="93909-2882">函數 Func_expiration_date 會找到正確日期格式的日期。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2882">The function Func_expiration_date finds a date in the right date format.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-2883">校驗和通過。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-2883">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- EU Debit Card Number -->
    <Entity id="0e9b3178-9678-47dd-a509-37222ca96b42" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_eu_debit_card" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_eu_debit_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_card_terms_dict" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_card_security_terms_dict" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_card_expiration_terms_dict" />
          <Match idRef="Func_expiration_date" />
        </Any>
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

## <a name="finland-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-3329">芬蘭駕照編號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3329">Finland driver's license number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="93909-3330">這個敏感資訊類型實體只有歐盟駕駛執照號碼機密資訊類型提供。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3330">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-3331">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3331">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-3332">10位數包含連字號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3332">10 digits containing a hyphen</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-3333">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3333">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-3334">10位數包含連字號：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3334">10 digits containing a hyphen:</span></span>
  
-  <span data-ttu-id="93909-3335">六位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3335">Six digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-3336">連字號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3336">A hyphen</span></span>
-  <span data-ttu-id="93909-3337">四位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3337">Four digits</span></span> 
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-3338">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3338">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-3339">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3339">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-3340">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3340">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-3341">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3341">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-3342">正則運算式會 `Regex_finland_eu_driver's_license_number` 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3342">The regular expression  `Regex_finland_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-3343">找到來自的關鍵字 `Keywords_finland_eu_driver's_license_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3343">A keyword from  `Keywords_finland_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Driver's License Number -->
<Entity id="b8fe86d1-c056-453b-bfaa-9fe698699ecc" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_finland_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_finland_eu_driver's_license_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-3344">關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3344">Keywords</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-3345">**Keywords_finland_eu_driver ' s_license_number**</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3345">**Keywords_finland_eu_driver's_license_number**</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="93909-3346">Dl#</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3346">dl#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-3347">駕照</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3347">driver license</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-3348">駕駛執照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3348">driver license number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-3349">驅動程式許可證</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3349">driver licence</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-3350">驅動程式 .lic。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3350">drivers lic.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-3351">驅動程式授權</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3351">drivers license</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-3352">驅動程式許可證</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3352">drivers licence</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-3353">駕駛執照</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3353">driver's license</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-3354">駕駛執照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3354">driver's license number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-3355">駕駛執照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3355">driver's licence number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-3356">駕駛執照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3356">driving license number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-3357">dlno#</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3357">dlno#</span></span>

## <a name="finland-national-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-3359">芬蘭國身分識別號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3359">Finland national identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="93909-3360">這種敏感資訊類型的實體包含在歐盟國身分識別號碼機密資訊類型中，並可作為獨立的機密資訊類型實體。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3360">This sensitive information type entity is included in the EU National Identification Number sensitive information type and is available as a stand alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-3361">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3361">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-3362">六位數加上一個表示世紀的字元加上三個數字加上檢查碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3362">Six digits plus a character indicating a century plus three digits plus a check digit</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-3363">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3363">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-3364">模式必須包含下列各項：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3364">Pattern must include all of the following:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-3365">DDMMYY 出生日期格式格式的六位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3365">Six digits in the format format DDMMYY which are a date of birth</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-3366">世紀標記（'-'、' + ' 或 ' a '）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3366">Century marker (either '-', '+' or 'a')</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-3367">三位數的個人身分識別號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3367">Three-digit personal identification number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-3368">一種檢查碼的數位或字母（不區分大小寫）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3368">A digit or letter (case insensitive) which is a check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-3369">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3369">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-3370">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3370">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-3371">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3371">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-3372">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是85%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3372">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-3373">函數 Func_finnish_national_id 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3373">The function Func_finnish_national_id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-3374">會找到來自 Keyword_finnish_national_id 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3374">A keyword from Keyword_finnish_national_id is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-3375">校驗和通過。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3375">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Finnish National ID-->
<Entity id="338FD995-4CB5-4F87-AD35-79BD1DD926C1" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_finnish_national_id" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_finnish_national_id" />
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="finland-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-3424">芬蘭護照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3424">Finland passport number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="93909-3425">您可以在歐盟護照號碼機密資訊類型中使用此機密資訊類型實體，也可以做為獨立機密資訊類型實體。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3425">This sensitive information type entity is available in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type and is available as a stand alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-3426">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3426">Format</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="93909-3427">九個字母和數位的組合</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3427">Combination of nine letters and digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-3428">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3428">Pattern</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="93909-3429">九個字母和數位的組合：兩個字母（不區分大小寫）七位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3429">Combination of nine letters and digits: Two letters (not case sensitive) Seven digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-3430">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3430">Checksum</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="93909-3431">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3431">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-3432">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3432">Definition</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="93909-3433">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3433">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-3434">正則運算式 Regex_finland_passport_number 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3434">The regular expression Regex_finland_passport_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-3435">會找到來自 Keyword_finland_passport_number 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3435">A keyword from Keyword_finland_passport_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Finland Passport Number -->
<Entity id="d1685ac3-1d3a-40f8-8198-32ef5669c7a5" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Regex_finland_passport_number"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_finland_passport_number"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```
### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-3436">關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3436">Keywords</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-3437">Keyword_finland_passport_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3437">Keyword_finland_passport_number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-3438">護照</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3438">Passport</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-3439">Passi</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3439">Passi</span></span>

## <a name="finland-social-security-number-or-equivalent-identification"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-3440">芬蘭社會安全號碼或對等身分識別</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3440">Finland social security number or equivalent identification</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="93909-3441">這個敏感資訊類型實體只有歐盟社會保險號碼或同等識別碼的敏感資訊類型提供。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3441">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Social Security Number or Equivalent ID sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-3442">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3442">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-3443">以指定格式為11個字元的組合</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3443">An 11-character combination in the specified format</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-3444">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3444">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-3445">以指定格式為11個字元的組合：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3445">An 11-character combination in the specified format:</span></span>
  
-  <span data-ttu-id="93909-3446">六位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3446">Six digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-3447">下列其中一個範例：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3447">One instance of one of the following:</span></span>
  - <span data-ttu-id="93909-3448">加號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3448">Plus symbol</span></span>
  - <span data-ttu-id="93909-3449">負號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3449">Minus symbol</span></span>
  - <span data-ttu-id="93909-3450">字母 "A" （不區分大小寫）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3450">The letter "A" (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-3451">三位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3451">Three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-3452">一個字母或一個數位</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3452">One letter or one digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-3453">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3453">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-3454">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3454">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-3455">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3455">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-3456">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是85%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3456">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-3457">函數 `Func_finland_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` 會找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3457">The function  `Func_finland_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-3458">找到來自的關鍵字 `Keywords_finland_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3458">A keyword from  `Keywords_finland_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="93909-3459">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3459">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-3460">函數 `Func_finland_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` 會找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3460">The function  `Func_finland_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU SSN or Equivalent Number -->
<Entity id="d24e32a4-c0bb-4ba8-899d-6303b95742d9" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_finland_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_finland_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
        </Pattern> 
       <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_finland_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
        </Pattern>      
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-3461">關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3461">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_finland_eu_ssn_or_equivalent"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-3462">Keywords_finland_eu_ssn_or_equivalent</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3462">Keywords_finland_eu_ssn_or_equivalent</span></span>

## <a name="finland-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-3484">芬蘭納稅識別號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3484">Finland tax identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="93909-3485">此機密資訊類型實體僅可用於歐盟納稅識別碼的敏感資訊類型。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3485">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Tax Identification Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-3486">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3486">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-3487">一個11個字元的位數、字母和正負號組合</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3487">An 11-character combination of digits, letters, and plus and minus sign</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-3488">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3488">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-3489">一個11個字元的位數、字母和正負號組合：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3489">An 11-character combination of digits, letters, and plus and minus sign:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-3490">六位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3490">Six digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-3491">下列其中一項：加號、減號或字母 "A" （不區分大小寫），其中加號表示介於1800-1899 之間，減號表示出生于1900-1999，而 "A" 表示出生2000和之後</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3491">One of the following: a plus sign, a minus sign, or the letter "A" (not case sensitive) where the plus sign means born between 1800-1899, the minus sign means born between 1900-1999, and "A" means born 2000 and after</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-3492">三位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3492">Three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-3493">一個字母或一個數位</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3493">One letter or one number</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-3494">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3494">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-3495">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3495">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-3496">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3496">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-3497">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是85%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3497">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-3498">函數 `Func_finland_eu_tax_file_number` 會找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3498">The function  `Func_finland_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-3499">找到來自的關鍵字 `Keywords_finland_eu_tax_file_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3499">A keyword from  `Keywords_finland_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="93909-3500">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3500">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-3501">函數 `Func_finland_eu_tax_file_number` 會找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3501">The function  `Func_finland_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Tax File Number -->
<Entity id="e09c07d3-66e5-4783-989d-49ac62748f5f" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_finland_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_finland_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
<Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_finland_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="france-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-3552">法國駕駛執照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3552">France driver's license number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="93909-3553">您可以在歐盟駕駛執照號碼的敏感資訊類型中取得此機密資訊類型實體，也可以作為獨立的機密資訊類型實體使用。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3553">This sensitive information type entity is available in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type and is available as a stand alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-3554">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3554">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-3555">12位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3555">12 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-3556">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3556">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-3557">12位數與折扣類似的模式，例如法國電話號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3557">12 digits with validation to discount similar patterns such as French telephone numbers</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-3558">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3558">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-3559">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3559">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-3560">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3560">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-3561">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3561">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-3562">函數 Func_french_drivers_license 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3562">The function Func_french_drivers_license finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-3563">下列專案中至少有一個為真：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3563">At least one of the following is true:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-3564">會找到來自 Keyword_french_drivers_license 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3564">A keyword from Keyword_french_drivers_license is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-3565">函數 Func_eu_date 會找到正確日期格式的日期。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3565">The function Func_eu_date finds a date in the right date format.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- France Driver's License Number -->
<Entity id="18e55a36-a01b-4b0f-943d-dc10282a1824" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_french_drivers_license" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_french_drivers_license" />
          <Match idRef="Func_eu_date" />
        </Any>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-3566">關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3566">Keywords</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="93909-3568">驅動程式許可證</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3568">drivers licence</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-3569">驅動程式授權</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3569">drivers license</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-3570">駕駛許可證</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3570">driving licence</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-3571">駕照</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3571">driving license</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-3572">permis de conduire</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3572">permis de conduire</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="93909-3575">許可證號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3575">licence numbers</span></span>

## <a name="france-national-identification-card-cni"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-3577">法國國身分識別卡片（CNI）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3577">France national identification card (CNI)</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="93909-3578">這種敏感資訊類型的實體包含在歐盟國身分識別號碼機密資訊類型中，並可作為獨立的機密資訊類型實體。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3578">This sensitive information type entity is included in the EU National Identification Number sensitive information type and is available as a stand alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-3579">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3579">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-3580">12位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3580">12 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-3581">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3581">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-3582">12位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3582">12 digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-3583">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3583">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-3584">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3584">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-3585">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3585">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-3586">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是65%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3586">A DLP policy is 65% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-3587">正則運算式 Regex_france_cni 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3587">The regular expression Regex_france_cni finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- France CNI -->
<Entity id="f741ac74-1bc0-4665-b69b-f0c7f927c0c4" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="65">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_france_cni" />
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="93909-3592">Cni#</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3592">cni#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-3593">Cni</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3593">cni</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="93909-3595">國家識別號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3595">national identification number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="93909-3598">numéro d'assurance maladie</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3598">numéro d'assurance maladie</span></span>

## <a name="france-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-3600">法國護照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3600">France passport number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="93909-3601">您可以在歐盟護照號碼機密資訊類型中使用此機密資訊類型實體，也可以做為獨立機密資訊類型實體。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3601">This sensitive information type entity is available in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type and is available as a stand alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-3602">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3602">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-3603">九個數字和字母</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3603">Nine digits and letters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-3604">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3604">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-3605">九個數字和字母：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3605">Nine digits and letters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-3606">兩位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3606">Two digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-3607">兩個字母（不區分大小寫）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3607">Two letters (not case sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-3608">五位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3608">Five digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-3609">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3609">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-3610">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3610">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-3611">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3611">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-3612">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3612">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-3613">函數 Func_fr_passport 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3613">The function Func_fr_passport finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-3614">會找到來自 Keyword_passport 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3614">A keyword from Keyword_passport is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- France Passport Number -->
<Entity id="3008b884-8c8c-4cd8-a289-99f34fc7ff5d" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_fr_passport" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_passport" />
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="france-social-security-number-insee-or-equivalent-identification"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-3635">法國社會安全號碼（INSEE）或對等身分識別</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3635">France social security number (INSEE) or equivalent identification</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="93909-3636">此機密資訊類型的實體包含在歐盟社會保險號碼和對等識別碼的敏感資訊類型中，並可作為獨立機密資訊類型實體。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3636">This sensitive information type entity is included in the EU Social Security Number and Equivalent ID sensitive information type and is available as a stand alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-3637">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3637">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-3638">15位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3638">15 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-3639">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3639">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-3640">必須符合下列其中一種模式：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3640">Must match one of two patterns:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-3641">13位數後接一個空格後接兩位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3641">13 digits followed by a space followed by two digits</span></span><br/>
<span data-ttu-id="93909-3642">或</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3642">or</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-3643">15個連續數位</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3643">15 consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-3644">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3644">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-3645">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3645">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-3646">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3646">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-3647">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是95%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3647">A DLP policy is 95% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-3648">函數 Func_french_insee 或 Func_fr_insee 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3648">The function Func_french_insee or Func_fr_insee finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-3649">會找到來自 Keyword_fr_insee 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3649">A keyword from Keyword_fr_insee is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-3650">校驗和通過。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3650">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-3651">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是85%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3651">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-3652">函數 Func_french_insee 或 Func_fr_insee 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3652">The function Func_french_insee or Func_fr_insee finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-3653">找不到 Keyword_fr_insee 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3653">No keyword from Keyword_fr_insee is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-3654">校驗和通過。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3654">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- France INSEE -->
<Entity id="71f62b97-efe0-4aa1-aa49-e14de253619d" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="95">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_french_insee" />
        <Match idRef="Func_fr_insee" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_fr_insee" />
        </Any>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_french_insee" />
        <Match idRef="Func_fr_insee" />
        <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_fr_insee" />
        </Any>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="france-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-3680">法國納稅識別號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3680">France tax identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="93909-3681">此機密資訊類型實體僅可用於歐盟納稅識別碼的敏感資訊類型。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3681">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Tax Identification Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-3682">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3682">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-3683">每個人13位數，實體的九位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3683">13 digits for individuals and nine digits for entities</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-3684">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3684">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-3685">個人13位數：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3685">13 digits for individuals:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-3686">一個位數必須是0、1、2或3</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3686">One digit that must be 0, 1, 2, or 3</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-3687">12位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3687">12 digits</span></span>
    
<span data-ttu-id="93909-3688">實體的九位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3688">Nine digits for entities</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-3689">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3689">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-3690">不適用</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3690">Not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-3691">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3691">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-3692">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是85%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3692">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-3693">函數 `Func_france_eu_tax_file_number` 會找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3693">The function  `Func_france_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-3694">找到來自的關鍵字 `Keywords_france_eu_tax_file_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3694">A keyword from  `Keywords_france_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="93909-3695">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3695">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-3696">函數 `Func_france_eu_tax_file_number` 會找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3696">The function  `Func_france_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Tax File Number -->
<Entity id="e09c07d3-66e5-4783-989d-49ac62748f5f" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_france_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_france_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
 <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_france_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="germany-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-3716">德國駕駛執照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3716">Germany driver's license number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="93909-3717">這種敏感資訊類型的實體包含在歐盟駕駛執照號碼的敏感資訊類型中，可作為獨立的敏感資訊類型實體。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3717">This sensitive information type entity is included in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type and is available as a stand alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-3718">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3718">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-3719">11位數和字母的組合</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3719">Combination of 11 digits and letters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-3720">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3720">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-3721">11個數字和字母（不區分大小寫）：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3721">11 digits and letters (not case sensitive):</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-3722">一個數位或字母</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3722">A digit or letter</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-3723">兩位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3723">Two digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-3724">六個數字或字母</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3724">Six digits or letters</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-3725">一個數位</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3725">A digit</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-3726">一個數位或字母</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3726">A digit or letter</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-3727">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3727">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-3728">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3728">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-3729">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3729">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-3730">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3730">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-3731">函數 Func_german_drivers_license 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3731">The function Func_german_drivers_license finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-3732">下列專案中至少有一個為真：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3732">At least one of the following is true:</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="93909-3733">會找到來自 Keyword_german_drivers_license_number 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3733">A keyword from Keyword_german_drivers_license_number is found.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="93909-3734">會找到來自 Keyword_german_drivers_license_collaborative 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3734">A keyword from Keyword_german_drivers_license_collaborative is found.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="93909-3735">會找到來自 Keyword_german_drivers_license 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3735">A keyword from Keyword_german_drivers_license is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-3736">校驗和通過。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3736">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Germany Driver's License Number -->
<Entity id="91da9335-1edb-45b7-a95f-5fe41a16c63c" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_german_drivers_license" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_german_drivers_license_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_german_drivers_license_collaborative" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_german_drivers_license" />
        </Any>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="germany-identity-card-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-3829">德國身分識別卡號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3829">Germany identity card number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-3830">這種敏感資訊類型的實體包含在歐盟國身分識別號碼機密資訊類型中，並可作為獨立的機密資訊類型實體。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3830">This sensitive information type entity is included in the EU National Identification Number sensitive information type and is available as a stand alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-3831">這種敏感資訊類型實體包含在歐盟社會保險號碼或同等識別碼的敏感資訊類型中。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3831">This sensitive information type entity is included in the EU Social Security Number or Equivalent ID sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-3832">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3832">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-3833">自11月2010：9個字母和數位</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3833">Since 1 November 2010: Nine letters and digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-3834">從1年4月1987至31年10月2010：10位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3834">From 1 April 1987 until 31 October 2010: 10 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-3835">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3835">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-3836">自11月1日2010：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3836">Since 1 November 2010:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-3837">一個字母（不區分大小寫）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3837">One letter (not case sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-3838">八位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3838">Eight digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-3839">從1年4月1987至31年10月2010：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3839">From 1 April 1987 until 31 October 2010:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-3840">10位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3840">10 digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-3841">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3841">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-3842">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3842">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-3843">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3843">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-3844">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是65%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3844">A DLP policy is 65% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-3845">正則運算式 Regex_germany_id_card 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3845">The regular expression Regex_germany_id_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-3846">會找到來自 Keyword_germany_id_card 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3846">A keyword from Keyword_germany_id_card is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Germany Identity Card Number -->
<Entity id="e577372f-c42e-47a0-9d85-bebed1c237d4" recommendedConfidence="65" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
     <IdMatch idRef="Regex_germany_id_card"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_germany_id_card"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="germany-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-3862">德國護照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3862">Germany passport number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="93909-3863">這個敏感資訊類型實體包含在歐盟護照號碼機密資訊類型中，並可作為獨立的敏感資訊類型實體。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3863">This sensitive information type entity is included in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type and is available as a stand alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-3864">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3864">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-3865">10位數或字母</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3865">10 digits or letters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-3866">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3866">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-3867">模式必須包含下列各項：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3867">Pattern must include all of the following:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-3868">第一個字元是來自此集合的數位或字母（C、F、G、H、J、K）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3868">First character is a digit or a letter from this set (C, F, G, H, J, K)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-3869">三位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3869">Three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-3870">來自此集合的五個數字或字母（C、-H、J-N、P、R、T、V-Z）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3870">Five digits or letters from this set (C, -H, J-N, P, R, T, V-Z)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-3871">一個數位</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3871">A digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-3872">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3872">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-3873">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3873">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-3874">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3874">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-3875">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是85%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3875">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-3876">函數 Func_german_passport 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3876">The function Func_german_passport finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-3877">找到任何五個關鍵字清單中的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3877">A keyword from any of the five keyword lists is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-3878">校驗和通過。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3878">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-3879">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3879">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-3880">函數 Func_german_passport_data 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3880">The function Func_german_passport_data finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-3881">找到任何五個關鍵字清單中的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3881">A keyword from any of the five keyword lists is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-3882">校驗和通過。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3882">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Germany Passport Number -->
<Entity id="2e3da144-d42b-47ed-b123-fbf78604e52c" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_german_passport" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_german_passport" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_german_passport_collaborative" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_german_passport_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_german_passport1" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_german_passport2" />
        </Any>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_german_passport_data" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_german_passport" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_german_passport_collaborative" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_german_passport_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_german_passport1" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_german_passport2" />
        </Any>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="germany-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-3900">德國納稅識別號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3900">Germany tax identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="93909-3901">此機密資訊類型實體僅可用於歐盟納稅識別碼的敏感資訊類型。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3901">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Tax Identification Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-3902">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3902">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-3903">11位數，不含空格及分隔符號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3903">11 digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-3904">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3904">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-3905">11位數：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3905">11 digits :</span></span>
  
-  <span data-ttu-id="93909-3906">10位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3906">Ten digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-3907">一個檢查碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3907">One check digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-3908">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3908">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-3909">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3909">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-3910">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3910">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-3911">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是85%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3911">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-3912">函數 `Func_germany_eu_tax_file_number` 會找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3912">The function  `Func_germany_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-3913">找到來自的關鍵字 `Keywords_germany_eu_tax_file_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3913">A keyword from  `Keywords_germany_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="93909-3914">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3914">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-3915">函數 `Func_germany_eu_tax_file_number` 會找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3915">The function  `Func_germany_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Tax File Number -->
<Entity id="e09c07d3-66e5-4783-989d-49ac62748f5f" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_germany_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_germany_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
<Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_germany_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="greece-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-3941">希臘駕駛執照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3941">Greece driver's license number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="93909-3942">這種敏感資訊類型的實體包含在歐盟駕駛執照號碼的敏感資訊類型中，可作為獨立的敏感資訊類型實體。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3942">This sensitive information type entity is included in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type and is available as a stand alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-3943">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3943">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-3944">九位數，不含空格及分隔符號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3944">Nine digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-3945">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3945">Pattern</span></span>

 <span data-ttu-id="93909-3946">九位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3946">Nine digits</span></span> 
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-3947">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3947">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-3948">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3948">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-3949">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3949">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-3950">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3950">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-3951">正則運算式會 `Regex_greece_eu_driver's_license_number` 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3951">The regular expression  `Regex_greece_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-3952">找到來自的關鍵字 `Keywords_greece_eu_driver's_license_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3952">A keyword from  `Keywords_greece_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Driver's License Number -->
<Entity id="b8fe86d1-c056-453b-bfaa-9fe698699ecc" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_greece_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_greece_eu_driver's_license_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="greece-national-id-card"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-3969">希臘國民身分證</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3969">Greece National ID Card</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="93909-3970">這種敏感資訊類型的實體包含在歐盟國身分識別號碼機密資訊類型中，並可作為獨立的機密資訊類型實體。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3970">This sensitive information type entity is included in the EU National Identification Number sensitive information type and is available as a stand alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-3971">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3971">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-3972">7-8 字母和數位的組合，加上破折號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3972">Combination of 7-8 letters and numbers plus a dash</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-3973">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3973">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-3974">七個字母和數位（舊格式）：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3974">Seven letters and numbers (old format):</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-3975">一個字母（希臘文字母表的任何字母）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3975">One letter (any letter of the Greek alphabet)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-3976">虛線</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3976">A dash</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-3977">六位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3977">Six digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-3978">八個字母和數位（新格式）：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3978">Eight letters and numbers (new format):</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-3979">兩個字母大寫字元會同時出現于希臘字母和拉丁字母表中（ABEZHIKMNOPTYX）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3979">Two letters whose uppercase character occurs in both the Greek and Latin alphabets (ABEZHIKMNOPTYX)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-3980">虛線</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3980">A dash</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-3981">六位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3981">Six digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-3982">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3982">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-3983">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3983">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-3984">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3984">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-3985">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是85%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3985">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-3986">正則運算式 Regex_greece_id_card 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3986">The regular expression Regex_greece_id_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-3987">會找到來自 Keyword_greece_id_card 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3987">A keyword from Keyword_greece_id_card is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Greece National ID Card -->
<Entity id="82568215-1da1-46d3-874a-d2294d81b5ac" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Regex_greece_id_card"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_greece_id_card"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="greece-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-3998">希臘護照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3998">Greece passport number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="93909-3999">這個敏感資訊類型實體只適用于歐盟護照號碼機密資訊類型。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-3999">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4000">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4000">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-4001">兩個字母后接7位數，不含空格或分隔符號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4001">Two letters followed by seven digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4002">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4002">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-4003">兩個字母后接7位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4003">Two letters followed by seven digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4004">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4004">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-4005">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4005">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4006">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4006">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-4007">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4007">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4008">正則運算式會 `Regex_greece_eu_passport_number` 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4008">The regular expression  `Regex_greece_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4009">找到來自的關鍵字 `Keywords_greece_eu_passport_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4009">A keyword from  `Keywords_greece_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Passport Number -->
<Entity id="21883626-6245-4f3d-9b61-5cbb43e625ee" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_greece_eu_passport_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_greece_eu_passport_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4010">關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4010">Keywords</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-4011">**Keywords_greece_eu_passport_number**</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4011">**Keywords_greece_eu_passport_number**</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4012">護照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4012">passport number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4013">希臘文護照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4013">greek passport number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4014">護照否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4014">passport no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4015">διαβατηριο</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4015">διαβατηριο</span></span>

## <a name="greece-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4016">希臘納稅識別號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4016">Greece tax identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="93909-4017">此機密資訊類型實體僅可用於歐盟納稅識別碼的敏感資訊類型。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4017">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Tax Identification Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4018">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4018">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-4019">九位數，不含空格及分隔符號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4019">Nine digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4020">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4020">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-4021">九位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4021">Nine digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4022">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4022">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-4023">不適用</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4023">Not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4024">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4024">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-4025">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4025">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4026">正則運算式會 `Regex_greece_eu_tax_file_number` 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4026">The regular expression  `Regex_greece_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4027">找到來自的關鍵字 `Keywords_greece_eu_tax_file_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4027">A keyword from  `Keywords_greece_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```
 <!-- EU Tax File Number -->
<Entity id="e09c07d3-66e5-4783-989d-49ac62748f5f" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_greece_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_greece_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="hong-kong-identity-card-hkid-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4056">中國香港身分識別卡（HKID）號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4056">Hong Kong identity card (HKID) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4057">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4057">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-4058">8-9 字母和數位的組合，以及最後一個字元兩邊的 optional 括弧</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4058">Combination of 8-9 letters and numbers plus optional parentheses around the final character</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4059">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4059">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-4060">8-9 個字母的組合：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4060">Combination of 8-9 letters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4061">1-2 個字母（不區分大小寫）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4061">1-2 letters (not case sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4062">六位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4062">Six digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4063">最後一個字元（任何數位或字母 A），也就是檢查碼，也可以以括弧括住。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4063">The final character (any digit or the letter A), which is the check digit and is optionally enclosed in parentheses.</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4064">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4064">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-4065">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4065">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4066">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4066">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-4067">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4067">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4068">函數 Func_hong_kong_id_card 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4068">The function Func_hong_kong_id_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4069">會找到來自 Keyword_hong_kong_id_card 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4069">A keyword from Keyword_hong_kong_id_card is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4070">校驗和通過。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4070">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-4071">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是65%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4071">A DLP policy is 65% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4072">函數 Func_hong_kong_id_card 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4072">The function Func_hong_kong_id_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4073">校驗和通過。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4073">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Hong Kong Identity Card (HKID) number -->
<Entity id="e63c28a7-ad29-4c17-a41a-3d2a0b70fd9c" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_hong_kong_id_card"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_hong_kong_id_card"/>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_hong_kong_id_card"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="hungary-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4112">匈牙利駕照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4112">Hungary driver's license number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="93909-4113">這個敏感資訊類型實體只有歐盟駕駛執照號碼機密資訊類型提供。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4113">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4114">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4114">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-4115">兩個字母后接六位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4115">Two letters followed by six digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4116">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4116">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-4117">兩個字母和六位數：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4117">Two letters and six digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4118">兩個字母（不區分大小寫）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4118">Two letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4119">六位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4119">Six digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4120">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4120">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-4121">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4121">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4122">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4122">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-4123">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4123">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4124">正則運算式會 `Regex_hungary_eu_driver's_license_number` 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4124">The regular expression  `Regex_hungary_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4125">找到來自的關鍵字 `Keywords_hungary_eu_driver's_license_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4125">A keyword from  `Keywords_hungary_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Driver's License Number -->
<Entity id="b8fe86d1-c056-453b-bfaa-9fe698699ecc" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_hungary_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_hungary_eu_driver's_license_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```
