## <a name="hungary-national-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4141">匈牙利國身分識別號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4141">Hungary national identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="93909-4142">這個敏感資訊類型實體僅可用於歐盟國身分識別號碼的敏感資訊類型。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4142">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU National Identification Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4143">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4143">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-4144">11位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4144">11 digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4145">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4145">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-4146">11位數：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4146">11 digits:</span></span>
  
-  <span data-ttu-id="93909-4147">對應于性別（1-男，2-女，其他號碼）的一種數位，也可能是公民之前出生的公民，具有雙公民的1900或公民。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4147">One digit that corresponds to gender (1-male, 2-female, other numbers are also possible for citizens born before 1900 or citizens with double citizenship)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4148">對應至出生日期的六位數（YYMMDD）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4148">Six digits that correspond to birth date (YYMMDD)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4149">對應至序列值的三位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4149">Three digits that correspond to a serial number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4150">一個檢查碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4150">One check digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4151">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4151">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-4152">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4152">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4153">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4153">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-4154">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是85%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4154">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4155">函數 `Func_hungary_eu_national_id_card` 會找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4155">The function  `Func_hungary_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4156">找到來自的關鍵字 `Keywords_hungary_eu_national_id_card` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4156">A keyword from  `Keywords_hungary_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="93909-4157">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4157">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4158">函數 `Func_hungary_eu_national_id_card` 會找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4158">The function  `Func_hungary_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
<Entity id="419f449f-6d9d-4be1-a154-b531f7a91b41" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_hungary_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_hungary_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
<Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_hungary_eu_national_id_card" />
</Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="hungary-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4169">匈牙利護照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4169">Hungary passport number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="93909-4170">這個敏感資訊類型實體只適用于歐盟護照號碼機密資訊類型。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4170">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4171">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4171">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-4172">兩個字母后接六個或7位數，不含空格或分隔符號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4172">Two letters followed by six or seven digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4173">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4173">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-4174">兩個字母后接六位數或七位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4174">Two letters followed by six or seven digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4175">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4175">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-4176">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4176">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4177">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4177">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-4178">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4178">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4179">正則運算式會 `Regex_hungary_eu_passport_number` 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4179">The regular expression  `Regex_hungary_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4180">找到來自的關鍵字 `Keywords_hungary_eu_passport_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4180">A keyword from  `Keywords_hungary_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Passport Number -->
<Entity id="21883626-6245-4f3d-9b61-5cbb43e625ee" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_hungary_eu_passport_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_hungary_eu_passport_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4191">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4191">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-4192">九位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4192">Nine digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4193">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4193">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-4194">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4194">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4195">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4195">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-4196">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是85%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4196">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4197">函數 `Func_hungary_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` 會找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4197">The function  `Func_hungary_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4198">找到來自的關鍵字 `Keywords_hungary_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4198">A keyword from  `Keywords_hungary_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="93909-4199">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4199">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4200">函數 `Func_hungary_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` 會找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4200">The function  `Func_hungary_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU SSN or Equivalent Number -->
<Entity id="d24e32a4-c0bb-4ba8-899d-6303b95742d9" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_hungary_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_hungary_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
        </Pattern> 
       <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_hungary_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
        </Pattern>      
</Entity>
```

## <a name="hungary-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4220">匈牙利納稅識別號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4220">Hungary tax identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="93909-4221">此機密資訊類型實體僅可用於歐盟納稅識別碼的敏感資訊類型。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4221">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Tax Identification Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4222">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4222">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-4223">沒有空格或分隔符號的10位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4223">Ten digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4224">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4224">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-4225">10位數：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4225">Ten digits:</span></span>
  
-  <span data-ttu-id="93909-4226">一個位數，必須是 "8"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4226">One digit that must be "8"</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4227">代表日期01/01/1867 和個人出生日期之間的天數所對應的5位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4227">Five digits that correspond to the number of days between the date 01/01/1867 and the date of the birth of the individual</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4228">三位數的值，對應于因有機會讓個別人出生于同一天所產生的數目</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4228">Three digits that correspond to the number generated by chance to differentiate individuals born on the same day</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4229">一個檢查碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4229">One check digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4230">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4230">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-4231">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4231">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4232">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4232">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-4233">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是85%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4233">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4234">函數 `Func_hungary_eu_tax_file_number` 會找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4234">The function  `Func_hungary_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4235">找到來自的關鍵字 `Keywords_hungary_eu_tax_file_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4235">A keyword from  `Keywords_hungary_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="93909-4236">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4236">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4237">函數 `Func_hungary_eu_tax_file_number` 會找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4237">The function  `Func_hungary_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Tax File Number -->
<Entity id="e09c07d3-66e5-4783-989d-49ac62748f5f" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_hungary_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_hungary_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
<Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_hungary_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="india-permanent-account-number-pan"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4263">印度永久帳戶號碼（PAN）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4263">India permanent account number (PAN)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4264">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4264">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-4265">10個字母或數位</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4265">10 letters or digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4266">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4266">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-4267">10個字母或數位：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4267">10 letters or digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4268">五個字母（不區分大小寫）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4268">Five letters (not case sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4269">四位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4269">Four digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4270">以字母檢查碼表示的字母</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4270">A letter which is an alphabetic check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4271">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4271">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-4272">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4272">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4273">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4273">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-4274">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是85%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4274">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4275">正則運算式 Regex_india_permanent_account_number 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4275">The regular expression Regex_india_permanent_account_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4276">會找到來自 Keyword_india_permanent_account_number 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4276">A keyword from Keyword_india_permanent_account_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4277">校驗和通過。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4277">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- India Permanent Account Number -->
<Entity id="2602bfee-9bb0-47a5-a7a6-2bf3053e2804" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Regex_india_permanent_account_number"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_india_permanent_account_number"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="india-unique-identification-aadhaar-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4282">印度唯一識別碼（Aadhaar）號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4282">India unique identification (Aadhaar) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4283">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4283">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-4284">12位數包含選擇性空格或短杠</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4284">12 digits containing optional spaces or dashes</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4285">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4285">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-4286">12位數：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4286">12 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4287">四位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4287">Four digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4288">選擇性的空格或破折號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4288">An optional space or dash</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4289">四位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4289">Four digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4290">選擇性的空格或破折號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4290">An optional space or dash</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4291">最後一位數的檢查碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4291">The final digit which is the check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4292">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4292">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-4293">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4293">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4294">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4294">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-4295">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是85%：函數 Func_india_aadhaar 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4295">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters: The function Func_india_aadhaar finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="93909-4296">會找到來自 Keyword_india_aadhar 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4296">A keyword from Keyword_india_aadhar is found.</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="93909-4297">校驗和通過。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4297">The checksum passes.</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="93909-4298">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：函數 Func_india_aadhaar 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4298">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters: The function Func_india_aadhaar finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="93909-4299">校驗和通過。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4299">The checksum passes.</span></span>
```xml
<!-- India Unique Identification (Aadhaar) number -->
<Entity id="1ca46b29-76f5-4f46-9383-cfa15e91048f" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_india_aadhaar"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_india_aadhar"/>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_india_aadhaar"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```
### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4300">關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4300">Keywords</span></span>
   
#### <a name="keyword_india_aadhar"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4301">Keyword_india_aadhar</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4301">Keyword_india_aadhar</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4302">Aadhar</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4302">Aadhar</span></span>

## <a name="indonesia-identity-card-ktp-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4306">印尼身分識別卡（KTP）號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4306">Indonesia identity card (KTP) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4307">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4307">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-4308">包含選用句點的16位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4308">16 digits containing optional periods</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4309">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4309">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-4310">16位數：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4310">16 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4311">兩位數的省碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4311">Two-digit province code</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4312">一個句點（選用）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4312">A period (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4313">兩位數攝政或城市碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4313">Two-digit regency or city code</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4314">兩位數的 subdistrict 程式碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4314">Two-digit subdistrict code</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4315">一個句點（選用）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4315">A period (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4316">DDMMYY 之日期格式的六位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4316">Six digits in the format DDMMYY which are the date of birth</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4317">一個句點（選用）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4317">A period (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4318">四位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4318">Four digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4319">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4319">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-4320">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4320">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4321">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4321">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-4322">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4322">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4323">正則運算式 Regex_indonesia_id_card 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4323">The regular expression Regex_indonesia_id_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4324">會找到來自 Keyword_indonesia_id_card 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4324">A keyword from Keyword_indonesia_id_card is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-4325">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4325">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4326">正則運算式 Regex_indonesia_id_card 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4326">The regular expression Regex_indonesia_id_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Indonesia Identity Card (KTP) Number -->
<Entity id="da68fdb0-f383-4981-8c86-82689d3b7d55" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Regex_indonesia_id_card"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_indonesia_id_card"/>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Regex_indonesia_id_card"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4327">關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4327">Keywords</span></span>
   
#### <a name="keyword_indonesia_id_card"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4328">Keyword_indonesia_id_card</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4328">Keyword_indonesia_id_card</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4329">Ktp</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4329">KTP</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4331">Nomor Induk Kependudukan</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4331">Nomor Induk Kependudukan</span></span> 
   
## <a name="international-banking-account-number-iban"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4332">國際銀行帳戶號碼（IBAN）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4332">International banking account number (IBAN)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4333">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4333">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-4334">國家/地區代碼（兩個字母）加上檢查碼（兩位數）加上 bban 號碼（最多30個字元）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4334">Country code (two letters) plus check digits (two digits) plus bban number (up to 30 characters)</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4335">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4335">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-4336">模式必須包含下列各項：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4336">Pattern must include all of the following:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4337">兩個字母的國家/地區碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4337">Two-letter country code</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4338">兩個檢查碼位數（後面接著選擇性的空格）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4338">Two check digits (followed by an optional space)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4339">1-7 四個字母或數位的群組（可以以空格隔開）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4339">1-7 groups of four letters or digits (can be separated by spaces)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4340">1-3 個字母或數位</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4340">1-3 letters or digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-4341">每個國家/地區的格式稍有不同。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4341">The format for each country is slightly different.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="93909-4342">IBAN 敏感資訊類型涵蓋下列60個國家/地區：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4342">The IBAN sensitive information type covers these 60 countries:</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-4343">ad，ae，al，at，az，ba，a，bg，bh，ch，cr，cy，cz，de，深色，do，ee，es，es，fo，fr，gb，ge，gi，gl，gr，hr，hu，ie，il，為，it，kw，kz，lb，li，lt，lu，lv，mt，mu，nl-nl，no，pl，mt，ro，rs-232c，tn，tr，vg</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4343">ad, ae, al, at, az, ba, be, bg, bh, ch, cr, cy, cz, de, dk, do, ee, es, fi, fo, fr, gb, ge, gi, gl, gr, hr, hu, ie, il, is, it, kw, kz, lb, li, lt, lu, lv, mc, md, me, mk, mr, mt, mu, nl, no, pl, pt, ro, rs, sa, se, si, sk, sm, tn, tr, vg</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4344">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4344">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-4345">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4345">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4346">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4346">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-4347">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是85%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4347">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4348">函數 Func_iban 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4348">The function Func_iban finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4349">校驗和通過。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4349">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<Entity id="e7dc4711-11b7-4cb0-b88b-2c394a771f0e" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_iban" />
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4350">關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4350">Keywords</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-4351">無</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4351">None</span></span>

   

   
## <a name="international-classification-of-diseases-icd-10-cm"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4352">國際分類的疾病（ICD-10-釐米）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4352">International classification of diseases (ICD-10-CM)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4353">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4353">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-4354">Dictionary</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4354">Dictionary</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4355">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4355">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-4356">關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4356">Keyword</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4357">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4357">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-4358">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4358">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4359">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4359">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-4360">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是85%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4360">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4361">會找到來自 Dictionary_icd_10_updated 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4361">A keyword from Dictionary_icd_10_updated is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4362">會找到來自 Dictionary_icd_10_codes 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4362">A keyword from Dictionary_icd_10_codes is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-4363">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4363">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4364">會找到 Dictionary_icd_10_ 更新的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4364">A keyword from Dictionary_icd_10_ updated is found.</span></span>

```xml
      <!-- ICD-10 CM -->
      <Entity id="3356946c-6bb7-449b-b253-6ffa419c0ce7" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Dictionary_icd_10_updated" />
          <Match idRef="Dictionary_icd_10_codes" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Dictionary_icd_10_updated" />
        </Pattern>

```

<span data-ttu-id="93909-4365">關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4365">Keywords</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-4366">Dictionary_icd_10_updated 關鍵字字典中的任何字詞，其基礎是以[疾病的國際分類，第十個修訂版本、臨床修改（icd-10 釐米）](https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?linkid=852604)為基礎。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4366">Any term from the Dictionary_icd_10_updated keyword dictionary, which is based on the [International Classification of Diseases, Tenth Revision, Clinical Modification (ICD-10-CM)](https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?linkid=852604).</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="93909-4367">這種類型只會尋找字詞，而不是保險碼。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4367">This type looks only for the term, not the insurance codes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-4368">Dictionary_icd_10_codes 關鍵字字典中的任何字詞，其基礎是以[疾病的國際分類，第十個修訂版本、臨床修改（icd-10 釐米）](https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?linkid=852604)為基礎。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4368">Any term from the Dictionary_icd_10_codes keyword dictionary, which is based on the [International Classification of Diseases, Tenth Revision, Clinical Modification (ICD-10-CM)](https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?linkid=852604).</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="93909-4369">這種類型只會查看保險業代碼，而不是描述。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4369">This type looks only for insurance codes, not the description.</span></span>

## <a name="international-classification-of-diseases-icd-9-cm"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4370">國際疾病（ICD-9 CM）分類</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4370">International classification of diseases (ICD-9-CM)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4371">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4371">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-4372">Dictionary</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4372">Dictionary</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4373">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4373">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-4374">關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4374">Keyword</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4375">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4375">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-4376">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4376">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4377">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4377">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-4378">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是85%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4378">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4379">會找到來自 Dictionary_icd_9_updated 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4379">A keyword from Dictionary_icd_9_updated is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4380">會找到來自 Dictionary_icd_9_codes 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4380">A keyword from Dictionary_icd_9_codes is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-4381">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4381">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4382">會找到來自 Dictionary_icd_9_updated 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4382">A keyword from Dictionary_icd_9_updated is found.</span></span>

```xml
    <Entity id="fa3f9c74-ee07-4c52-b5f2-085d6b2c0ec4" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Dictionary_icd_9_updated" />
          <Match idRef="Dictionary_icd_9_codes" />
        </Pattern>
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Dictionary_icd_9_updated" />
        </Pattern>
      </Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4383">關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4383">Keywords</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-4384">Dictionary_icd_9_updated 關鍵字字典中的任何字詞，其基礎是根據[疾病的國際分類，第九個修訂版本，臨床修改（icd-9 CM）](https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?linkid=852605)。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4384">Any term from the Dictionary_icd_9_updated keyword dictionary, which is based on the [International Classification of Diseases,Ninth Revision, Clinical Modification (ICD-9-CM)](https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?linkid=852605).</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="93909-4385">這種類型只會尋找字詞，而不是保險碼。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4385">This type looks only for the term, not the insurance codes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-4386">Dictionary_icd_9_codes 關鍵字字典中的任何字詞，其基礎是根據[疾病的國際分類，第九個修訂版本，臨床修改（icd-9 CM）](https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?linkid=852605)。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4386">Any term from the Dictionary_icd_9_codes keyword dictionary, which is based on the [International Classification of Diseases,Ninth Revision, Clinical Modification (ICD-9-CM)](https://go.microsoft.com/fwlink/?linkid=852605).</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="93909-4387">這種類型只會查看保險業代碼，而不是描述。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4387">This type looks only for insurance codes, not the description.</span></span>

## <a name="ip-address"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4388">IP 位址</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4388">IP address</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4389">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4389">Format</span></span>

#### <a name="ipv4"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4390">IPv4：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4390">IPv4:</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="93909-4391">用於格式化（句點）及未格式化（無期間）的 IPv4 位址版本的複雜模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4391">Complex pattern which accounts for formatted (periods) and unformatted (no periods) versions of the IPv4 addresses</span></span>

#### <a name="ipv6"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4392">IPv6：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4392">IPv6:</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="93909-4393">IPv6 數位格式（包含冒號）的複雜模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4393">Complex pattern which accounts for formatted IPv6 numbers (which include colons)</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4394">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4394">Pattern</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4395">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4395">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-4396">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4396">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4397">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4397">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-4398">針對 IPv6，如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是85%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4398">For IPv6, a DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4399">正則運算式 Regex_ipv6_address 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4399">The regular expression Regex_ipv6_address finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4400">找不到 Keyword_ipaddress 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4400">No keyword from Keyword_ipaddress is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-4401">針對 IPv4，如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是95%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4401">For IPv4, a DLP policy is 95% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4402">正則運算式 Regex_ipv4_address 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4402">The regular expression Regex_ipv4_address finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4403">會找到來自 Keyword_ipaddress 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4403">A keyword from Keyword_ipaddress is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-4404">針對 IPv6，如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是95%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4404">For IPv6, a DLP policy is 95% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4405">正則運算式 Regex_ipv6_address 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4405">The regular expression Regex_ipv6_address finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4406">找不到 Keyword_ipaddress 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4406">No keyword from Keyword_ipaddress is found.</span></span>

```xml
    <!-- IP Address -->
    <Entity id="1daa4ad5-e2dd-4ca4-a788-54722c09efb2" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_ipv6_address" />
        <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_ipaddress" />
        </Any>
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="95">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_ipv4_address" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_ipaddress" />
        </Any>
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="95">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_ipv6_address" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_ipaddress" />
        </Any>
      </Pattern>
    </Entity>
```

## <a name="ireland-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4414">愛爾蘭駕照編號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4414">Ireland driver's license number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="93909-4415">這個敏感資訊類型實體只有歐盟駕駛執照號碼機密資訊類型提供。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4415">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4416">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4416">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-4417">六位數後接四個字母</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4417">Six digits followed by four letters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4418">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4418">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-4419">六位數和四個字母：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4419">Six digits and four letters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4420">六位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4420">Six digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4421">四個字母（不區分大小寫）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4421">Four letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4422">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4422">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-4423">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4423">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4424">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4424">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-4425">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4425">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4426">正則運算式會 `Regex_ireland_eu_driver's_license_number` 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4426">The regular expression  `Regex_ireland_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4427">找到來自的關鍵字 `Keywords_ireland_eu_driver's_license_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4427">A keyword from  `Keywords_ireland_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Driver's License Number -->
<Entity id="b8fe86d1-c056-453b-bfaa-9fe698699ecc" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_ireland_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_ireland_eu_driver's_license_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="ireland-national-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4443">愛爾蘭國身分識別號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4443">Ireland national identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="93909-4444">這個敏感資訊類型實體只包含在歐盟國身分識別號碼的敏感資訊類型中。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4444">This sensitive information type entity is only included in the EU National Identification Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4445">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4445">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-4446">在指定的模式中，字母、數位及空格的九個字元組合</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4446">A nine-character combination of letters, digits, and a space in the specified pattern</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4447">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4447">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-4448">在指定的模式中，字母、數位及空格的九個字元組合</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4448">A nine-character combination of letters, digits, and a space in the specified pattern</span></span>
  
<span data-ttu-id="93909-4449">從01年1月2013至現在：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4449">From 01 January 2013 to now:</span></span>
  
-  <span data-ttu-id="93909-4450">七位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4450">Seven digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4451">一個檢查碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4451">One check digit</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4452">一個空格或大寫字母 "W" （區分大小寫）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4452">One space or the uppercase letter "W" (Case sensitive)</span></span>
    
<span data-ttu-id="93909-4453">在2013年1月1日之前：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4453">Prior to 01 January 2013:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4454">七位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4454">Seven digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4455">一個檢查碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4455">One check digit</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4456">一個空格或大寫字母（區分大小寫）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4456">One space or an uppercase letter (Case sensitive)</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4457">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4457">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-4458">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4458">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4459">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4459">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-4460">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是85%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4460">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4461">函數會找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4461">The function finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4462">找到來自的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4462">A keyword from is found.</span></span>
    
<span data-ttu-id="93909-4463">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4463">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4464">函數會找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4464">The function finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
    
```xml
 <!--Ireland national identification number  -->
<Entity id="419f449f-6d9d-4be1-a154-b531f7a91b41" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_ireland_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_ireland_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
<Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_ireland_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="ireland-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4493">愛爾蘭護照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4493">Ireland passport number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="93909-4494">這個敏感資訊類型實體只適用于歐盟護照號碼機密資訊類型。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4494">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4495">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4495">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-4496">兩個字母或數位後接7位數，不含空格或分隔符號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4496">Two letters or digits followed by seven digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4497">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4497">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-4498">兩個字母或數位後接7位數：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4498">Two letters or digits followed by seven digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4499">兩位數或字母（不區分大小寫）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4499">Two digits or letters (not case sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4500">七位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4500">Seven digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4501">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4501">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-4502">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4502">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4503">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4503">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-4504">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4504">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4505">正則運算式會 `Regex_ireland_eu_passport_number` 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4505">The regular expression  `Regex_ireland_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4506">找到來自的關鍵字 `Keywords_ireland_eu_passport_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4506">A keyword from  `Keywords_ireland_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Passport Number -->
<Entity id="21883626-6245-4f3d-9b61-5cbb43e625ee" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_ireland_eu_passport_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_ireland_eu_passport_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="ireland-personal-public-service-pps-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4516">愛爾蘭個人公開服務（PPS）號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4516">Ireland personal public service (PPS) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4517">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4517">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-4518">舊格式（直到12月2012日）：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4518">Old format (until 31 Dec 2012):</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4519">七位數後接1-2 個字母</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4519">Seven digits followed by 1-2 letters</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="93909-4520">新格式（1月2013日和之後）：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4520">New format (1 Jan 2013 and after):</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4521">七位數後接兩個字母</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4521">Seven digits followed by two letters</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4522">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4522">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-4523">舊格式（直到12月2012日）：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4523">Old format (until 31 Dec 2012):</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4524">七位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4524">Seven digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4525">1-2 個字母（不區分大小寫）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4525">1-2 letters (not case sensitive)</span></span> 

<span data-ttu-id="93909-4526">新格式（1月2013日和之後）：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4526">New format (1 Jan 2013 and after):</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4527">七位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4527">Seven digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4528">字母（不區分大小寫）是字母檢查碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4528">A letter (not case sensitive) which is an alphabetic check digit</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4529">字母 "A" 或 "H" （不區分大小寫）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4529">The letter "A" or "H" (not case sensitive)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4530">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4530">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-4531">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4531">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4532">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4532">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-4533">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是85%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4533">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4534">函數 Func_ireland_pps 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4534">The function Func_ireland_pps finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4535">下列其中一項為真：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4535">One of the following is true:</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="93909-4536">會找到來自 Keyword_ireland_pps 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4536">A keyword from Keyword_ireland_pps is found.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="93909-4537">函數 Func_eu_date 會找到正確日期格式的日期。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4537">The function Func_eu_date finds a date in the right date format.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4538">校驗和通過。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4538">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-4539">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是65%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4539">A DLP policy is 65% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4540">函數 Func_ireland_pps 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4540">The function Func_ireland_pps finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4541">校驗和通過。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4541">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Ireland Personal Public Service (PPS) Number -->
<Entity id="1cdb674d-c19a-4fcf-9f4b-7f56cc87345a" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_ireland_pps"/>
     <Any minMatches="1">
  <Match idRef="Keyword_ireland_pps"/>
  <Match idRef="Func_eu_date"/>
     </Any>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_ireland_pps"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4542">關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4542">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_ireland_pps"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4543">Keyword_ireland_pps</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4543">Keyword_ireland_pps</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4546">PPS 數位</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4546">PPS Num</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4547">PPS No。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4547">PPS No.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4548">Pps#</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4548">PPS #</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4550">PPSN</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4550">PPSN</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4551">公用服務卡片</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4551">Public Services Card</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4553">Uimh.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4553">Uimh.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="93909-4554">Psp</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4554">PSP</span></span>

## <a name="ireland-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4556">愛爾蘭納稅識別號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4556">Ireland tax identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="93909-4557">此機密資訊類型實體僅可用於歐盟納稅識別碼的敏感資訊類型。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4557">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Tax Identification Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4558">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4558">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-4559">七位數後接字母，不含空格或分隔符號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4559">Seven digits followed by a letter with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4560">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4560">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-4561">七位數後接字母：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4561">Seven digits followed by a letter:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4562">七位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4562">Seven digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4563">一個字母（不區分大小寫）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4563">One letter (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4564">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4564">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-4565">不適用</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4565">Not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4566">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4566">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-4567">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是85%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4567">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4568">函數 `Func_ireland_eu_tax_file_number` 會找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4568">The function  `Func_ireland_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4569">找到來自的關鍵字 `Keywords_ireland_eu_tax_file_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4569">A keyword from  `Keywords_ireland_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="93909-4570">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4570">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4571">函數 `Func_ireland_eu_tax_file_number` 會找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4571">The function  `Func_ireland_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Tax File Number -->
<Entity id="e09c07d3-66e5-4783-989d-49ac62748f5f" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_ireland_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_ireland_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
<Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_ireland_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="israel-bank-account-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4600">以色列銀行帳戶號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4600">Israel bank account number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4601">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4601">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-4602">13位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4602">13 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4603">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4603">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-4604">格式 化：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4604">Formatted:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4605">兩位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4605">Two digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4606">虛線</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4606">A dash</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4607">三位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4607">Three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4608">虛線</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4608">A dash</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4609">八位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4609">Eight digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-4610">非</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4610">Unformatted:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4611">13個連續數位</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4611">13 consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4612">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4612">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-4613">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4613">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4614">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4614">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-4615">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4615">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4616">正則運算式 Regex_israel_bank_account_number 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4616">The regular expression Regex_israel_bank_account_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4617">會找到來自 Keyword_israel_bank_account_number 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4617">A keyword from Keyword_israel_bank_account_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Israel Bank Account Number -->
<Entity id="7d08b2ff-a0b9-437f-957c-aeddbf9b2b25" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_israel_bank_account_number" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_israel_bank_account_number" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4618">關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4618">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_israel_bank_account_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4619">Keyword_israel_bank_account_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4619">Keyword_israel_bank_account_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4620">銀行帳戶號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4620">Bank Account Number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4621">銀行帳戶</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4621">Bank Account</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4622">帳戶號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4622">Account Number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4623">מספר חשבון בנק</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4623">מספר חשבון בנק</span></span> 
   
## <a name="israel-national-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4624">以色列國身分識別號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4624">Israel national identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4625">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4625">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-4626">九位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4626">Nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4627">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4627">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-4628">九個連續數位</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4628">Nine consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4629">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4629">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-4630">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4630">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4631">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4631">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-4632">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4632">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4633">函數 Func_israeli_national_id_number 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4633">The function Func_israeli_national_id_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4634">會找到來自 Keyword_Israel_National_ID 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4634">A keyword from Keyword_Israel_National_ID is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4635">校驗和通過。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4635">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Israel National ID Number -->
<Entity id="e05881f5-1db1-418c-89aa-a3ac5c5277ee" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_israeli_national_id_number" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_Israel_National_ID" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4636">關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4636">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_israel_national_id"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4637">Keyword_Israel_National_ID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4637">Keyword_Israel_National_ID</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4638">מספר זהות</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4638">מספר זהות</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4639">本國識別碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4639">National ID Number</span></span>
   
## <a name="italy-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4640">義大利駕照編號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4640">Italy driver's license number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="93909-4641">這種敏感資訊類型的實體包含在歐盟駕駛執照號碼的敏感資訊類型中，可作為獨立的敏感資訊類型實體。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4641">This sensitive information type entity is included in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type and is available as a stand alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4642">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4642">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-4643">10個字母和數位的組合</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4643">A combination of 10 letters and digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4644">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4644">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4645">10個字母和數位的組合：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4645">A combination of 10 letters and digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4646">一個字母（不區分大小寫）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4646">One letter (not case sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4647">字母 "A" 或 "V" （不區分大小寫）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4647">The letter "A" or "V" (not case sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4648">七個字母（不區分大小寫）、數位或底線字元</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4648">Seven letters (not case sensitive), digits, or the underscore character</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4649">一個字母（不區分大小寫）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4649">One letter (not case sensitive)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4650">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4650">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-4651">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4651">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4652">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4652">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-4653">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4653">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4654">正則運算式 Regex_italy_drivers_license_number 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4654">The regular expression Regex_italy_drivers_license_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4655">會找到來自 Keyword_italy_drivers_license_number 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4655">A keyword from Keyword_italy_drivers_license_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Italy Driver's license Number -->
<Entity id="97d6244f-9157-41bd-8e0c-9d669a5c4d71" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_italy_drivers_license_number" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_italy_drivers_license_number" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4656">關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4656">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_italy_drivers_license_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4657">Keyword_italy_drivers_license_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4657">Keyword_italy_drivers_license_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4658">numero di patente di guida</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4658">numero di patente di guida</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4659">patente di guida</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4659">patente di guida</span></span> 

## <a name="italy-national-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4660">義大利國身分識別號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4660">Italy national identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="93909-4661">這個敏感資訊類型實體僅可用於歐盟國身分識別號碼的敏感資訊類型。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4661">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU National Identification Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4662">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4662">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-4663">指定之模式中字母和數位的16個字元組合</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4663">A 16-character combination of letters and digits in the specified pattern</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4664">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4664">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-4665">字母和數位的16個字元的組合：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4665">A 16-character combination of letters and digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4666">與系列名稱中的前三個雙子音相對應的三個字母</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4666">Three letters that correspond to the first three consonants in the family name</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4667">與名字中的第一個、第三個和第四個雙子音相對應的三個字母</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4667">Three letters that correspond to the first, third, and fourth consonants in the first name</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4668">與出生年份的最後一個數位相對應的兩位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4668">Two digits that correspond to the last digits of the birth year</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4669">對應至出生月份之字母的一個字母，在字母順序中使用字母，但是只會使用字母 A 到 E、H、L、M、P、P、R 到 T （即，一月份是 A，10月是 R）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4669">One letter that corresponds to the letter for the month of birth—letters are used in alphabetical order, but only the letters A to E, H, L, M, P, R to T are used (thus, January is A and October is R)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4670">兩位數的出生月份天數，為了區別 genders，40會新增到女士的出生日。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4670">Two digits that correspond to the day of the month of birth—in order to differentiate between genders, 40 is added to the day of birth for women</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4671">相對於 municipality 人員專屬之地區代碼的四位數（國家/地區的碼用於外國國家）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4671">Four digits that corresponds to the area code specific to the municipality where the person was born (country-wide codes are used for foreign countries)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4672">一個同位數位</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4672">One parity digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4673">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4673">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-4674">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4674">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4675">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4675">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-4676">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是85%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4676">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4677">函數 `Func_italy_eu_national_id_card` 會找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4677">The function  `Func_italy_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4678">找到來自的關鍵字 `Keywords_italy_eu_national_id_card` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4678">A keyword from  `Keywords_italy_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="93909-4679">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4679">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4680">函數 `Func_italy_eu_national_id_card` 會找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4680">The function  `Func_italy_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
<!-- Italy national identification number -->
<Entity id="419f449f-6d9d-4be1-a154-b531f7a91b41" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_italy_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_italy_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
<Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_italy_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4691">numero personale</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4691">numero personale</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4692">個人憑證號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4692">personal certificate number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4693">個人程式碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4693">personal code</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4694">個人識別碼代碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4694">personal id code</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4695">個人號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4695">personal id number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4696">personalcodeno#</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4696">personalcodeno#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4697">稅碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4697">tax code</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4699">納稅識別碼否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4699">tax identification no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4700">納稅識別號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4700">tax identification number</span></span>
