## <a name="italy-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4715">義大利護照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4715">Italy passport number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="93909-4716">這個敏感資訊類型實體只適用于歐盟護照號碼機密資訊類型。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4716">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4717">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4717">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-4718">兩個字母或數位後接7位數，不含空格或分隔符號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4718">Two letters or digits followed by seven digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4719">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4719">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-4720">兩個字母或數位後接7位數：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4720">Two letters or digits followed by seven digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4721">兩位數或字母（不區分大小寫）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4721">Two digits or letters (not case sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4722">七位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4722">Seven digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4723">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4723">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-4724">不適用</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4724">Not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4725">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4725">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-4726">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4726">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4727">正則運算式會 `Regex_italy_eu_passport_number` 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4727">The regular expression  `Regex_italy_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4728">找到來自的關鍵字 `Keywords_italy_eu_passport_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4728">A keyword from  `Keywords_italy_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Passport Number -->
<Entity id="21883626-6245-4f3d-9b61-5cbb43e625ee" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_italy_eu_passport_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_italy_eu_passport_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4729">關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4729">Keywords</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-4730">**Keywords_italy_eu_passport_number**</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4730">**Keywords_italy_eu_passport_number**</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4731">義大利護照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4731">italian passport number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4732">repubblica italiana passaporto</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4732">repubblica italiana passaporto</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4733">passaporto</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4733">passaporto</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4734">passaporto italiana</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4734">passaporto italiana</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4735">護照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4735">passport number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4736">italiana passaporto numero</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4736">italiana passaporto numero</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4737">passaporto numero</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4737">passaporto numero</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4738">numéro passeport italien</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4738">numéro passeport italien</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4739">numéro passeport</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4739">numéro passeport</span></span>

## <a name="italy-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4740">義大利納稅識別號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4740">Italy tax identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="93909-4741">此機密資訊類型實體僅可用於歐盟納稅識別碼的敏感資訊類型。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4741">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Tax Identification Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4742">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4742">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-4743">在指定的模式中有16個字母和數位</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4743">16 letters and digits in the specified pattern</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4744">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4744">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-4745">16個字母和數位：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4745">16 letters and digits:</span></span>
  
-  <span data-ttu-id="93909-4746">與系列名稱中的前三個雙子音相對應的三個字母</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4746">Three letters that correspond to the first three consonants in the family name</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4747">與名字中的第一個、第三個和第四個雙子音相對應的三個字母</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4747">Three letters that correspond to the first, third, and fourth consonants in the first name</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4748">與出生年份的最後一個數位相對應的兩位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4748">Two digits that correspond to the last digits of the birth year</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4749">對應至出生月份的一個數位（字母的使用字母順序），但是只會使用字母 A 到 E、H、L、M、P、P、R to T （即，一月份為 A，10月是 R）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4749">One digit that corresponds to the month of birth—letters are used in alphabetical order, but only the letters A to E, H, L, M, P, R to T are used (thus, January is A and October is R)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4750">兩位數，對應至出生的出生一天，40會新增至女生中，以區別于男生</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4750">Two digits that correspond to the day of the month of birth where 40 is added to the day of birth for females to differentiate from males</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4751">對應至某人出生之 municipality 之特定區功能變數代碼的四位數（國家/地區的碼是用於國外國家/地區）。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4751">Four digits that correspond to an area code specific to the municipality where the person was born—country-wide codes are used for foreign countries</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4752">一個檢查碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4752">One check digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4753">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4753">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-4754">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4754">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4755">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4755">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-4756">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是85%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4756">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4757">函數 `Func_italy_eu_tax_file_number` 會找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4757">The function  `Func_italy_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4758">找到來自的關鍵字 `Keywords_italy_eu_tax_file_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4758">A keyword from  `Keywords_italy_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="93909-4759">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4759">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4760">函數 `Func_italy_eu_tax_file_number` 會找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4760">The function  `Func_italy_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Tax File Number -->
<Entity id="e09c07d3-66e5-4783-989d-49ac62748f5f" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_italy_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_italy_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
<Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_italy_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="japan-bank-account-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4795">日本銀行帳戶號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4795">Japan bank account number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4796">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4796">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-4797">7或8位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4797">Seven or eight digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4798">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4798">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-4799">銀行帳戶號碼：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4799">Bank account number:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4800">7或8位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4800">Seven or eight digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4801">銀行帳戶分支程式碼：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4801">Bank account branch code:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4802">四位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4802">Four digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4803">一個空格或破折號（選用）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4803">A space or dash (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4804">三位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4804">Three digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-4805">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4805">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-4806">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4806">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4807">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4807">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-4808">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是85%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4808">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4809">函數 Func_jp_bank_account 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4809">The function Func_jp_bank_account finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4810">會找到來自 Keyword_jp_bank_account 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4810">A keyword from Keyword_jp_bank_account is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4811">下列其中一項為真：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4811">One of the following is true:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4812">函數 Func_jp_bank_account_branch_code 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4812">The function Func_jp_bank_account_branch_code finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4813">會找到來自 Keyword_jp_bank_branch_code 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4813">A keyword from Keyword_jp_bank_branch_code is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-4814">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4814">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4815">函數 Func_jp_bank_account 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4815">The function Func_jp_bank_account finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4816">會找到來自 Keyword_jp_bank_account 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4816">A keyword from Keyword_jp_bank_account is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Japan Bank Account Number -->
<Entity id="d354f95b-96ee-4b80-80bc-4377312b55bc" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
  <Version minEngineVersion="15.01.0131.000">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_jp_bank_account" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_jp_bank_account" />
          <Any minMatches="1">
            <Match idRef="Func_jp_bank_account_branch_code" />
            <Match idRef="Keyword_jp_bank_branch_code" />
          </Any>
      </Pattern>
  </Version>    
     <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_jp_bank_account" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_jp_bank_account" />
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="japan-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4875">日本駕照編號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4875">Japan driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4876">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4876">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-4877">12位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4877">12 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4878">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4878">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-4879">12個連續數位</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4879">12 consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4880">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4880">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-4881">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4881">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4882">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4882">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-4883">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4883">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4884">函數 Func_jp_drivers_license_number 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4884">The function Func_jp_drivers_license_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4885">會找到來自 Keyword_jp_drivers_license_number 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4885">A keyword from Keyword_jp_drivers_license_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Japan Driver's License Number -->
<Entity id="c6011143-d087-451c-8313-7f6d4aed2270" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_jp_drivers_license_number" />
        <Match idRef ="Keyword_jp_drivers_license_number" />
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="japan-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4913">日本護照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4913">Japan passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4914">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4914">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-4915">兩個字母后接7位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4915">Two letters followed by seven digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4916">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4916">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-4917">兩個字母（不區分大小寫）後接7位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4917">Two letters (not case sensitive) followed by seven digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4918">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4918">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-4919">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4919">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4920">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4920">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-4921">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4921">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4922">函數 Func_jp_passport 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4922">The function Func_jp_passport finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4923">會找到來自 Keyword_jp_passport 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4923">A keyword from Keyword_jp_passport is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Japan Passport Number -->
<Entity id="75177310-1a09-4613-bf6d-833aae3743f8" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_jp_passport" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_jp_passport" />
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="japan-residence-card-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4930">日本住家電話卡號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4930">Japan residence card number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4931">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4931">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-4932">12個字母和數位</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4932">12 letters and digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4933">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4933">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-4934">12個字母和數位：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4934">12 letters and digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4935">兩個字母（不區分大小寫）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4935">Two letters (not case sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4936">八位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4936">Eight digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4937">兩個字母（不區分大小寫）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4937">Two letters (not case sensitive)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4938">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4938">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-4939">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4939">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4940">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4940">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-4941">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4941">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4942">正則運算式 Regex_jp_residence_card_number 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4942">The regular expression Regex_jp_residence_card_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4943">會找到來自 Keyword_jp_residence_card_number 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4943">A keyword from Keyword_jp_residence_card_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!--Japan Residence Card Number-->
-<Entity id="ac36fef2-a289-4e2c-bb48-b02366e89fc0" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
   -<Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
      <IdMatch idRef="Regex_jp_residence_card_number"/>
      <Match idRef="Keyword_jp_residence_card_number"/>
   </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4947">不含住宅卡片</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4947">Residence card no</span></span>

## <a name="japan-resident-registration-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4950">日本居民登記號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4950">Japan resident registration number</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4955">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4955">Checksum</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4957">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4957">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-4958">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4958">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4959">函數 Func_jp_resident_registration_number 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4959">The function Func_jp_resident_registration_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4960">會找到來自 Keyword_jp_resident_registration_number 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4960">A keyword from Keyword_jp_resident_registration_number is found.</span></span>

```xml

<Entity id="01c1209b-6389-4faf-a5f8-3f7e13899652" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_jp_resident_registration_number" />
        <Match idRef ="Keyword_jp_resident_registration_number" />
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="japan-social-insurance-number-sin"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4974">日本社交保險號碼（SIN）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4974">Japan social insurance number (SIN)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4975">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4975">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-4976">7-12 位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4976">7-12 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4977">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4977">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-4978">7-12 位數：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4978">7-12 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4979">四位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4979">Four digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4980">連字號（選用）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4980">A hyphen (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4981">六位數或</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4981">Six digits OR</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4982">7-12 連續位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4982">7-12 consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4983">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4983">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-4984">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4984">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4985">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4985">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-4986">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是85%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4986">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4987">函數 Func_jp_sin 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4987">The function Func_jp_sin finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4988">會找到來自 Keyword_jp_sin 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4988">A keyword from Keyword_jp_sin is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-4989">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4989">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4990">函數 Func_jp_sin_pre_1997 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4990">The function Func_jp_sin_pre_1997 finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4991">會找到來自 Keyword_jp_sin 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4991">A keyword from Keyword_jp_sin is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Japan Social Insurance Number -->
<Entity id="c840e719-0896-45bb-84fd-1ed5c95e45ff" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_jp_sin" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_jp_sin" />
    </Pattern>
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_jp_sin_pre_1997" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_jp_sin" />
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4992">關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4992">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_jp_sin"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4993">Keyword_jp_sin</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4993">Keyword_jp_sin</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4994">社交保險保險編號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4994">Social Insurance No.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4995">社交保險編號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4995">Social Insurance Num</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4996">社交保險號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4996">Social Insurance Number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4997">社會保険のテンキー</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4997">社会保険のテンキー</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-4998">社會保険番號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4998">社会保険番号</span></span> 

## <a name="latvia-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-4999">拉脫維亞駕駛執照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-4999">Latvia driver's license number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="93909-5000">這個敏感資訊類型實體只有歐盟駕駛執照號碼機密資訊類型提供。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5000">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5001">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5001">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-5002">三個字母后接六位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5002">Three letters followed by six digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5003">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5003">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-5004">三個字母和六位數：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5004">Three letters and six digits:</span></span>
  
-  <span data-ttu-id="93909-5005">三個字母（不區分大小寫）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5005">Three letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5006">六位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5006">Six digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5007">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5007">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-5008">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5008">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5009">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5009">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-5010">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5010">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5011">正則運算式會 `Regex_latvia_eu_driver's_license_number` 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5011">The regular expression  `Regex_latvia_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5012">找到來自的關鍵字 `Keywords_latvia_eu_driver's_license_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5012">A keyword from  `Keywords_latvia_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Driver's License Number -->
<Entity id="b8fe86d1-c056-453b-bfaa-9fe698699ecc" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_latvia_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_driver's_license_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5013">關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5013">Keywords</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-5014">**Keywords_latvia_eu_driver ' s_license_number**</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5014">**Keywords_latvia_eu_driver's_license_number**</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5015">Dl#</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5015">dl#</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5016">駕照</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5016">driver license</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5017">駕駛執照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5017">driver license number</span></span>

## <a name="latvia-national-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5028">拉脫維亞國身分識別號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5028">Latvia national identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="93909-5029">這個敏感資訊類型實體僅可用於歐盟國身分識別號碼的敏感資訊類型。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5029">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU National Identification Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5030">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5030">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-5031">11位數和指定格式的連字號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5031">11 digits and a hyphen in the specified format</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5032">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5032">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-5033">11位數和連字號：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5033">11 digits and a hyphen:</span></span>
  
-  <span data-ttu-id="93909-5034">與出生日期對應的六位數（DDMMYY）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5034">Six digits that correspond to the birth date (DDMMYY)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5035">連字號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5035">A hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5036">一個數位，對應至出生世紀（"0" 代表19世紀，"1" 代表20世紀，而 "2" 代表21世紀）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5036">One digit that corresponds to the century of birth ("0" for 19th century, "1" for 20th century, and "2" for 21st century)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5037">四位數（隨機產生）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5037">Four digits, randomly generated</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5038">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5038">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-5039">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5039">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5040">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5040">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-5041">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是85%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5041">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5042">函數 `Func_latvia_eu_national_id_card` 會找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5042">The function  `Func_latvia_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5043">找到來自的關鍵字 `Keywords_latvia_eu_national_id_card` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5043">A keyword from  `Keywords_latvia_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="93909-5044">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5044">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5045">函數 `Func_latvia_eu_national_id_card` 會找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5045">The function  `Func_latvia_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
<!-- Latvia national identification number -->
<Entity id="419f449f-6d9d-4be1-a154-b531f7a91b41" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_latvia_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
 <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_latvia_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="latvia-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5108">拉脫維亞護照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5108">Latvia passport number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="93909-5109">這個敏感資訊類型實體只適用于歐盟護照號碼機密資訊類型。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5109">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5110">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5110">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-5111">兩個字母或數位後接7位數，不含空格或分隔符號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5111">Two letters or digits followed by seven digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5112">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5112">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-5113">兩個字母或數位後接7位數：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5113">Two letters or digits followed by seven digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5114">兩位數或字母（不區分大小寫）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5114">Two digits or letters (not case sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5115">七位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5115">Seven digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5116">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5116">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-5117">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5117">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5118">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5118">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-5119">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5119">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5120">正則運算式會 `Regex_latvia_eu_passport_number` 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5120">The regular expression  `Regex_latvia_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5121">找到來自的關鍵字 `Keywords_latvia_eu_passport_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5121">A keyword from  `Keywords_latvia_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Passport Number -->
<Entity id="21883626-6245-4f3d-9b61-5cbb43e625ee" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_latvia_eu_passport_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_passport_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5122">關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5122">Keywords</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-5123">**Keywords_latvia_eu_passport_number**</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5123">**Keywords_latvia_eu_passport_number**</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5124">護照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5124">passport number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5125">拉脫維亞文護照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5125">latvian passport number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5126">護照否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5126">passport no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5127">pase numurs</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5127">pase numurs</span></span>    

## <a name="latvia-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5128">拉脫維亞納稅識別號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5128">Latvia tax identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="93909-5129">此機密資訊類型實體僅可用於歐盟納稅識別碼的敏感資訊類型。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5129">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Tax Identification Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5130">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5130">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-5131">11位數，不含空格或分隔符號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5131">11 digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5132">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5132">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-5133">指定的模式中的11位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5133">11 digits in the specified pattern</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5134">與出生日期相對應的六位數（DDMMYY）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5134">Six digits that correspond to the date of birth (DDMMYY)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5135">對應至出生世紀的一個數位，其中 "0" 對應于19世紀，"1" 對應于20世紀，"2" 對應于21世紀。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5135">One digit that corresponds to the century of birth where "0" corresponds to 19th century, "1" corresponds to 20th century, and "2"corresponds to 21st century</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5136">四位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5136">Four digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5137">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5137">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-5138">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5138">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5139">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5139">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-5140">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是85%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5140">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5141">函數 `Func_latvia_eu_tax_file_number` 會找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5141">The function  `Func_latvia_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5142">找到來自的關鍵字 `Keywords_latvia_eu_tax_file_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5142">A keyword from  `Keywords_latvia_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="93909-5143">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5143">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5144">函數 `Func_latvia_eu_tax_file_number` 會找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5144">The function  `Func_latvia_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Tax File Number -->
<Entity id="e09c07d3-66e5-4783-989d-49ac62748f5f" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_latvia_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_latvia_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
<Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_latvia_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="lithuania-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5207">立陶宛駕照編號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5207">Lithuania driver's license number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="93909-5208">這個敏感資訊類型實體只有歐盟駕駛執照號碼機密資訊類型提供。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5208">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5209">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5209">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-5210">不含空格及分隔符號的八位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5210">Eight digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5211">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5211">Pattern</span></span>

 <span data-ttu-id="93909-5212">八位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5212">Eight digits</span></span> 
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5213">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5213">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-5214">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5214">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5215">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5215">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-5216">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5216">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5217">正則運算式會 `Regex_lithuania_eu_driver's_license_number` 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5217">The regular expression  `Regex_lithuania_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5218">找到來自的關鍵字 `Keywords_lithuania_eu_driver's_license_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5218">A keyword from  `Keywords_lithuania_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Driver's License Number -->
<Entity id="b8fe86d1-c056-453b-bfaa-9fe698699ecc" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_lithuania_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_lithuania_eu_driver's_license_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="lithuania-national-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5234">立陶宛國身分識別號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5234">Lithuania national identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="93909-5235">這個敏感資訊類型實體僅可用於歐盟國身分識別號碼的敏感資訊類型。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5235">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU National Identification Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5236">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5236">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-5237">11位數，不含空格及分隔符號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5237">11 digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5238">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5238">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-5239">11位數，不含空格及分隔符號：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5239">11 digits without spaces and delimiters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5240">對應至人員性別和出生世紀的一個數位</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5240">One digit that corresponds to the person's gender and century of birth</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5241">對應至出生日期的六位數（YYMMDD）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5241">Six digits that correspond to birth date (YYMMDD)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5242">對應至出生日期之序號的三位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5242">Three digits that correspond to the serial number of the date of birth</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5243">一個檢查碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5243">One check digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5244">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5244">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-5245">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5245">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5246">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5246">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-5247">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是85%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5247">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5248">函數 `Func_lithuania_eu_national_id_card` 會找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5248">The function  `Func_lithuania_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5249">找到來自的關鍵字 `Keywords_lithuania_eu_national_id_card` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5249">A keyword from  `Keywords_lithuania_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="93909-5250">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5250">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5251">函數 `Func_lithuania_eu_national_id_card` 會找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5251">The function  `Func_lithuania_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
<!-- Lithuania national identification number -->
<Entity id="419f449f-6d9d-4be1-a154-b531f7a91b41" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_lithuania_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_lithuania_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern> 
<Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_lithuania_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="lithuania-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5286">立陶宛護照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5286">Lithuania passport number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="93909-5287">這個敏感資訊類型實體只適用于歐盟護照號碼機密資訊類型。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5287">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5288">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5288">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-5289">八位數的數位或字母，不含空格或分隔符號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5289">Eight digits or letters with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5290">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5290">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-5291">八位數或字母（不區分大小寫）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5291">Eight digits or letters (not case sensitive)</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5292">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5292">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-5293">不適用</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5293">Not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5294">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5294">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-5295">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5295">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5296">正則運算式會 `Regex_lithuania_eu_passport_number` 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5296">The regular expression  `Regex_lithuania_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5297">找到來自的關鍵字 `Keywords_lithuania_eu_passport_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5297">A keyword from  `Keywords_lithuania_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Passport Number -->
<Entity id="21883626-6245-4f3d-9b61-5cbb43e625ee" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_lithuania_eu_passport_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_lithuania_eu_passport_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5298">關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5298">Keywords</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-5299">**Keywords_lithuania_eu_passport_number**</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5299">**Keywords_lithuania_eu_passport_number**</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-5300">護照號碼 lithunian 護照號碼護照 no paso numeris</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5300">passport number lithunian passport number passport no paso numeris</span></span>

## <a name="lithuania-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5301">立陶宛納稅識別號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5301">Lithuania tax identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="93909-5302">此機密資訊類型實體僅可用於歐盟納稅識別碼的敏感資訊類型。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5302">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Tax Identification Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5303">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5303">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-5304">11位數，不含空格或分隔符號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5304">11 digits without spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5305">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5305">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-5306">11位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5306">11 digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5307">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5307">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-5308">不適用</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5308">Not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5309">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5309">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-5310">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是85%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5310">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5311">函數 `Func_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number` 會找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5311">The function  `Func_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5312">找到來自的關鍵字 `Keywords_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5312">A keyword from  `Keywords_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="93909-5313">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5313">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5314">函數 `Func_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number` 會找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5314">The function  `Func_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Tax File Number -->
<Entity id="e09c07d3-66e5-4783-989d-49ac62748f5f" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
<Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_lithuania_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="luxemburg-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5348">Luxemburg 駕駛執照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5348">Luxemburg driver's license number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="93909-5349">他的敏感資訊類型實體只有歐盟駕駛執照號碼機密資訊類型提供。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5349">his sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5350">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5350">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-5351">六位數，不含空格及分隔符號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5351">Six digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5352">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5352">Pattern</span></span>

 <span data-ttu-id="93909-5353">六位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5353">Six digits</span></span> 
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5354">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5354">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-5355">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5355">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5356">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5356">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-5357">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5357">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5358">正則運算式會 `Regex_luxemburg_eu_driver's_license_number` 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5358">The regular expression  `Regex_luxemburg_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5359">找到來自的關鍵字 `Keywords_luxemburg_eu_driver's_license_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5359">A keyword from  `Keywords_luxemburg_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Driver's License Number -->
<Entity id="b8fe86d1-c056-453b-bfaa-9fe698699ecc" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_luxemburg_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_luxemburg_eu_driver's_license_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="luxemburg-national-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5375">Luxemburg 國身分識別號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5375">Luxemburg national identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="93909-5376">這個敏感資訊類型實體僅可用於歐盟國身分識別號碼的敏感資訊類型。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5376">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU National Identification Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5377">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5377">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-5378">11位數，不含空格及分隔符號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5378">11 digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5379">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5379">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-5380">11位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5380">11 digits</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5381">對應至人員性別和出生世紀的一個數位</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5381">One digit that corresponds to the person's gender and century of birth</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5382">對應至出生日期的六位數（YYMMDD）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5382">Six digits that correspond to birth date (YYMMDD)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5383">對應至出生日期之序號的三位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5383">Three digits that correspond to the serial number of the date of birth</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5384">一個檢查碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5384">One check digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5385">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5385">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-5386">不適用</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5386">Not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5387">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5387">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-5388">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5388">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5389">正則運算式會 `Regex_luxemburg_eu_national_id_card` 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5389">The regular expression  `Regex_luxemburg_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5390">找到來自的關鍵字 `Keywords_luxemburg_eu_national_id_card` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5390">A keyword from  `Keywords_luxemburg_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
<Entity id="419f449f-6d9d-4be1-a154-b531f7a91b41" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_luxemburg_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_luxemburg_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="luxemburg-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5413">Luxemburg 護照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5413">Luxemburg passport number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="93909-5414">這個敏感資訊類型實體只適用于歐盟護照號碼機密資訊類型。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5414">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5415">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5415">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-5416">八位數的數位或字母，不含空格或分隔符號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5416">Eight digits or letters with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5417">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5417">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-5418">八位數或字母（不區分大小寫）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5418">Eight digits or letters (not case sensitive)</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5419">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5419">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-5420">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5420">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5421">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5421">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-5422">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5422">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5423">正則運算式會 `Regex_nation_eu_passport_number` 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5423">The regular expression  `Regex_nation_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5424">找到來自的關鍵字 `Keywords_nation_eu_passport_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5424">A keyword from  `Keywords_nation_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Passport Number -->
<Entity id="21883626-6245-4f3d-9b61-5cbb43e625ee" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_nation_eu_passport_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_nation_eu_passport_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5425">關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5425">Keywords</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-5426">**Keywords_nation_eu_passport_number**</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5426">**Keywords_nation_eu_passport_number**</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-5427">護照號碼拉脫維亞文號碼護照 no passnummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5427">passport number latvian passport number passport no passnummer</span></span>

## <a name="luxemburg-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5428">Luxemburg 納稅識別號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5428">Luxemburg tax identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="93909-5429">此機密資訊類型實體僅可用於歐盟納稅識別碼的敏感資訊類型。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5429">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Tax Identification Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5430">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5430">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-5431">13位數沒有空格或分隔符號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5431">13 digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5432">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5432">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-5433">13位數：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5433">13 digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5434">11位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5434">11 digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5435">兩個檢查碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5435">Two check digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5436">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5436">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-5437">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5437">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5438">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5438">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-5439">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是85%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5439">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5440">函數 `Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number` 會找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5440">The function  `Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5441">找到來自的關鍵字 `Keywords_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5441">A keyword from  `Keywords_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="93909-5442">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5442">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5443">函數 `Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number` 會找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5443">The function  `Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Tax File Number -->
<Entity id="e09c07d3-66e5-4783-989d-49ac62748f5f" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
<Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_luxemburg_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="malaysia-identification-card-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5483">馬來西亞身分識別卡號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5483">Malaysia identification card number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5484">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5484">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-5485">12位數包含選擇性連字號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5485">12 digits containing optional hyphens</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5486">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5486">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-5487">12位數：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5487">12 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5488">YYMMDD 之日期格式的六位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5488">Six digits in the format YYMMDD which are the date of birth</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5489">破折號（選用）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5489">A dash (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5490">兩個字母的出生代碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5490">Two-letter place-of-birth code</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5491">破折號（選用）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5491">A dash (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5492">三個亂數字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5492">Three random digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5493">一位數的性別碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5493">One-digit gender code</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5494">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5494">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-5495">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5495">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5496">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5496">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-5497">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是85%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5497">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5498">正則運算式 Regex_malaysia_id_card_number 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5498">The regular expression Regex_malaysia_id_card_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5499">會找到來自 Keyword_malaysia_id_card_number 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5499">A keyword from Keyword_malaysia_id_card_number is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Malaysia ID Card Number -->
</Entity>
      <Entity id="7f0e921c-9677-435b-aba2-bb8f1013c749" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
            <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malaysia_id_card_number" />
            <Match idRef="Keyword_malaysia_id_card_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="malta-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5526">馬爾他駕照編號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5526">Malta driver's license number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="93909-5527">這個敏感資訊類型實體只有歐盟駕駛執照號碼機密資訊類型提供。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5527">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5528">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5528">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-5529">兩個字元的組合，並在指定的模式中包含六位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5529">Combination of two characters and six digits in the specified pattern</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5530">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5530">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-5531">兩個字元和六位數的組合：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5531">Combination of two characters and six digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5532">兩個字元（數位或字母，不區分大小寫）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5532">Two characters (digits or letters, not case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5533">一個空格（選用）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5533">A space (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5534">三位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5534">Three digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5535">一個空格（選用）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5535">A space (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5536">三位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5536">Three digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5537">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5537">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-5538">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5538">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5539">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5539">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-5540">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5540">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5541">正則運算式會 `Regex_malta_eu_driver's_license_number` 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5541">The regular expression  `Regex_malta_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5542">找到來自的關鍵字 `Keywords_malta_eu_driver's_license_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5542">A keyword from  `Keywords_malta_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
<!-- EU Driver's License Number -->
 <Entity id="b8fe86d1-c056-453b-bfaa-9fe698699ecc" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malta_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_malta_eu_driver's_license_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="malta-national-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5558">馬爾他國身分識別號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5558">Malta national identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="93909-5559">這個敏感資訊類型實體僅可用於歐盟國身分識別號碼的敏感資訊類型。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5559">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU National Identification Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5560">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5560">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-5561">七位數後接一個字母</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5561">Seven digits followed by one letter</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5562">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5562">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-5563">七位數後接一個字母：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5563">Seven digits followed by one letter:</span></span>
  
-  <span data-ttu-id="93909-5564">七位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5564">Seven digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5565">單一大寫字母（區分大小寫）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5565">One uppercase letter (case sensitive)</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5566">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5566">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-5567">不適用</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5567">Not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5568">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5568">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-5569">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5569">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5570">正則運算式會 `Regex_malta_eu_national_id_card` 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5570">The regular expression  `Regex_malta_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5571">找到來自的關鍵字 `Keywords_malta_eu_national_id_card` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5571">A keyword from  `Keywords_malta_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="93909-5572">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是65%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5572">A DLP policy is 65% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5573">正則運算式會 `Regex_malta_eu_national_id_card` 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5573">The regular expression  `Regex_malta_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!--Malta national identification number  -->
<Entity id="419f449f-6d9d-4be1-a154-b531f7a91b41" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malta_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_malta_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
<Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malta_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5584">numru tas-servizz taċ-ċittadin</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5584">numru tas-servizz taċ-ċittadin</span></span>
