## <a name="malta-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5590">馬爾他護照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5590">Malta passport number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="93909-5591">這個敏感資訊類型實體只適用于歐盟護照號碼機密資訊類型。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5591">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5592">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5592">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-5593">七位數，不含空格或分隔符號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5593">Seven digits without spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5594">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5594">Pattern</span></span>

 <span data-ttu-id="93909-5595">七位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5595">Seven digits</span></span> 
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5596">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5596">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-5597">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5597">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5598">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5598">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-5599">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5599">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5600">正則運算式會 `Regex_malta_eu_passport_number` 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5600">The regular expression  `Regex_malta_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5601">找到來自的關鍵字 `Keywords_malta_eu_passport_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5601">A keyword from  `Keywords_malta_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Passport Number -->
<Entity id="21883626-6245-4f3d-9b61-5cbb43e625ee" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malta_eu_passport_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_malta_eu_passport_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5602">關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5602">Keywords</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-5603">**Keywords_malta_eu_passport_number**</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5603">**Keywords_malta_eu_passport_number**</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5604">護照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5604">passport number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5605">馬爾他護照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5605">maltese passport number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5606">護照否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5606">passport no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5607">numru tal-passaport</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5607">numru tal-passaport</span></span>

## <a name="malta-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5608">馬爾他納稅識別號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5608">Malta tax identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="93909-5609">此機密資訊類型實體僅可用於歐盟納稅識別碼的敏感資訊類型。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5609">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Tax Identification Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5610">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5610">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-5611">在馬爾他 nationals 中：7位數和指定的模式中的一個字母</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5611">For Maltese nationals: 7 digits and one letter in the specified pattern</span></span>
  
<span data-ttu-id="93909-5612">非馬爾他 nationals 及馬爾他式實體：9位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5612">Non-Maltese nationals and Maltese entities: 9 digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5613">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5613">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-5614">馬爾他 nationals：7位數和一個字母</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5614">Maltese nationals: 7 digits and one letter</span></span>
  
-  <span data-ttu-id="93909-5615">七位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5615">Seven digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5616">一個字母（不區分大小寫）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5616">One letter (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
    
<span data-ttu-id="93909-5617">非馬爾他 nationals 及馬爾他式實體：9位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5617">Non-Maltese nationals and Maltese entities: 9 digits</span></span>
  
-  <span data-ttu-id="93909-5618">九位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5618">Nine digits</span></span> 
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5619">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5619">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-5620">不適用</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5620">Not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5621">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5621">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-5622">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5622">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5623">函數 `Func_malta_eu_tax_file_number` 會找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5623">The function  `Func_malta_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5624">找到來自的關鍵字 `Keywords_malta_eu_tax_file_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5624">A keyword from  `Keywords_malta_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="93909-5625">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是65%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5625">A DLP policy is 65% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5626">函數 `Func_malta_eu_tax_file_number` 會找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5626">The function  `Func_malta_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Tax File Number -->
<Entity id="e09c07d3-66e5-4783-989d-49ac62748f5f" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_malta_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_malta_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
<Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_malta_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="netherlands-citizens-service-bsn-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5659">荷蘭公民服務（BSN）號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5659">Netherlands citizen's service (BSN) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5660">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5660">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-5661">8-9 位數包含選擇性空格</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5661">8-9 digits containing optional spaces</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5662">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5662">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-5663">8-9 位數：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5663">8-9 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5664">三位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5664">Three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5665">一個空格（選用）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5665">A space (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5666">三位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5666">Three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5667">一個空格（選用）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5667">A space (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5668">2-3 位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5668">2-3 digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5669">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5669">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-5670">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5670">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5671">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5671">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-5672">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是85%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5672">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5673">函數 Func_netherlands_bsn 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5673">The function Func_netherlands_bsn finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5674">會找到來自 Keyword_netherlands_bsn 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5674">A keyword from Keyword_netherlands_bsn is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5675">函數 Func_eu_date2 會找到正確日期格式的日期。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5675">The function Func_eu_date2 finds a date in the right date format.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5676">校驗和通過。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5676">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Netherlands Citizen's Service (BSN) Number -->
<Entity id="c5f54253-ef7e-44f6-a578-440ed67e946d" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
       <IdMatch idRef="Func_netherlands_bsn" /> 
       <Match idRef="Keyword_netherlands_bsn" /> 
       <Match idRef="Func_eu_date2" /> 
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="netherlands-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5700">荷蘭駕駛執照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5700">Netherlands driver's license number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="93909-5701">這個敏感資訊類型實體只有歐盟駕駛執照號碼機密資訊類型提供。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5701">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5702">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5702">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-5703">10位數，不含空格及分隔符號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5703">10 digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5704">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5704">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-5705">10位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5705">10 digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5706">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5706">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-5707">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5707">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5708">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5708">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-5709">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5709">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5710">正則運算式會 `Regex_netherlands_eu_driver's_license_number` 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5710">The regular expression  `Regex_netherlands_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5711">找到來自的關鍵字 `Keywords_netherlands_eu_driver's_license_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5711">A keyword from  `Keywords_netherlands_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Driver's License Number -->
<Entity id="b8fe86d1-c056-453b-bfaa-9fe698699ecc" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_netherlands_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_netherlands_eu_driver's_license_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="netherlands-national-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5729">荷蘭國身分識別號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5729">Netherlands national identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="93909-5730">這個敏感資訊類型實體僅可用於歐盟國身分識別號碼的敏感資訊類型。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5730">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU National Identification Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5731">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5731">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-5732">九位數，不含空格或分隔符號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5732">Nine digits without spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5733">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5733">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-5734">九位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5734">Nine digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5735">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5735">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-5736">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5736">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5737">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5737">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-5738">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是85%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5738">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5739">函數 `Func_netherlands_eu_national_id_card` 會找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5739">The function  `Func_netherlands_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5740">找到來自的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5740">A keyword from is found.</span></span>
    
<span data-ttu-id="93909-5741">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5741">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5742">函數 `Func_netherlands_eu_national_id_card` 會找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5742">The function  `Func_netherlands_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!--Netherland national identification number  -->
<Entity id="419f449f-6d9d-4be1-a154-b531f7a91b41" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_netherlands_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_netherlands_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
<Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_netherlands_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="netherlands-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5766">荷蘭護照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5766">Netherlands passport number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="93909-5767">這個敏感資訊類型實體只適用于歐盟護照號碼機密資訊類型。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5767">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5768">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5768">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-5769">不含空格或分隔符號的九個字母或數位</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5769">Nine letters or digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5770">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5770">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-5771">九個字母或數位</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5771">Nine letters or digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5772">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5772">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-5773">不適用</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5773">Not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5774">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5774">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-5775">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5775">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5776">正則運算式會 `Regex_netherlands_eu_passport_number` 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5776">The regular expression  `Regex_netherlands_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5777">找到來自的關鍵字 `Keywords_netherlands_eu_passport_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5777">A keyword from  `Keywords_netherlands_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Passport Number -->
<Entity id="21883626-6245-4f3d-9b61-5cbb43e625ee" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_netherlands_eu_passport_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_netherlands_eu_passport_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5778">關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5778">Keywords</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-5779">**Keywords_netherlands_eu_passport_number**</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5779">**Keywords_netherlands_eu_passport_number**</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5780">荷蘭護照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5780">dutch passport number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5781">護照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5781">passport number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5782">荷蘭護照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5782">netherlands passport number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5783">nederlanden paspoort nummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5783">nederlanden paspoort nummer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5784">paspoort</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5784">paspoort</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5785">nederlanden paspoortnummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5785">nederlanden paspoortnummer</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5786">paspoortnummer</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5786">paspoortnummer</span></span>

## <a name="netherlands-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5787">荷蘭稅務識別號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5787">Netherlands tax identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="93909-5788">此機密資訊類型實體僅可用於歐盟納稅識別碼的敏感資訊類型。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5788">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Tax Identification Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5789">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5789">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-5790">九位數，不含空格或分隔符號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5790">Nine digits without spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5791">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5791">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-5792">九位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5792">Nine digits</span></span> 
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5793">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5793">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-5794">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5794">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5795">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5795">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-5796">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是85%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5796">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5797">函數 `Func_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number` 會找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5797">The function  `Func_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5798">找到來自的關鍵字 `Keywords_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5798">A keyword from  `Keywords_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="93909-5799">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5799">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5800">函數 `Func_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number` 會找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5800">The function  `Func_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Tax File Number -->
<Entity id="e09c07d3-66e5-4783-989d-49ac62748f5f" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
<Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_netherlands_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="new-zealand-ministry-of-health-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5838">紐西蘭健康情況號碼的部</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5838">New Zealand ministry of health number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5839">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5839">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-5840">三個字母、一個空格（選用）及四位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5840">Three letters, a space (optional), and four digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5841">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5841">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-5842">三個字母（不區分大小寫）一個空格（選用）四位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5842">Three letters (not case sensitive) a space (optional) four digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5843">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5843">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-5844">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5844">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5845">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5845">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-5846">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是85%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5846">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5847">函數 Func_new_zealand_ministry_of_health_number 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5847">The function Func_new_zealand_ministry_of_health_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5848">會找到來自 Keyword_nz_terms 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5848">A keyword from Keyword_nz_terms is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5849">校驗和通過。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5849">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- New Zealand Health Number -->
<Entity id="2b71c1c8-d14e-4430-82dc-fd1ed6bf05c7" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_new_zealand_ministry_of_health_number" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_nz_terms" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

<span data-ttu-id="93909-5850">關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5850">Keywords</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-5851">Keyword_nz_terms</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5851">Keyword_nz_terms</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5852">NHI</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5852">NHI</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5853">紐西蘭</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5853">New Zealand</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5854">健康情況</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5854">Health</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5855">治療</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5855">treatment</span></span> 
   
## <a name="norway-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5856">挪威身分識別號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5856">Norway identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5857">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5857">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-5858">11位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5858">11 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5859">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5859">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-5860">11位數：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5860">11 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5861">DDMMYY 之日期格式的六位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5861">Six digits in the format DDMMYY which are the date of birth</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5862">三位數個人號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5862">Three-digit individual number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5863">兩個檢查碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5863">Two check digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5864">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5864">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-5865">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5865">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5866">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5866">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-5867">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是85%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5867">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5868">函數 Func_norway_id_number 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5868">The function Func_norway_id_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5869">會找到來自 Keyword_norway_id_number 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5869">A keyword from Keyword_norway_id_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5870">校驗和通過。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5870">The checksum passes.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5871">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5871">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5872">函數 Func_norway_id_numbe 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5872">The function Func_norway_id_numbe finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5873">校驗和通過。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5873">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Norway Identification Number -->
<Entity id="d4c8a798-e9f2-4bd3-9652-500d24080fc3" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_norway_id_number"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_norway_id_number"/>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_norway_id_number"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="philippines-unified-multi-purpose-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5882">菲律賓統一多用途識別號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5882">Philippines unified multi-purpose identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5883">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5883">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-5884">以連字號隔開的12位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5884">12 digits separated by hyphens</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5885">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5885">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-5886">12位數：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5886">12 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5887">四位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5887">Four digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5888">連字號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5888">A hyphen</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5889">七位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5889">Seven digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5890">連字號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5890">A hyphen</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5891">一個數位</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5891">One digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5892">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5892">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-5893">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5893">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5894">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5894">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-5895">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5895">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5896">正則運算式 Regex_philippines_unified_id 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5896">The regular expression Regex_philippines_unified_id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5897">會找到來自 Keyword_philippines_id 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5897">A keyword from Keyword_philippines_id is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Philippines Unified Multi-Purpose ID number -->
<Entity id="019b39dd-8c25-4765-91a3-d9c6baf3c3b3" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Regex_philippines_unified_id"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_philippines_id"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5898">關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5898">Keywords</span></span>
   
#### <a name="keyword_philippines_id"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5899">Keyword_philippines_id</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5899">Keyword_philippines_id</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5900">統一的多重用途識別碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5900">Unified Multi-Purpose ID</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5901">UMID</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5901">UMID</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5902">身份證</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5902">Identity Card</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5903">Pinag-isang 多 Layunin 識別碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5903">Pinag-isang Multi-Layunin ID</span></span>

## <a name="poland-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5904">波蘭駕照編號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5904">Poland driver's license number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="93909-5905">這個敏感資訊類型實體只有歐盟駕駛執照號碼機密資訊類型提供。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5905">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5906">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5906">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-5907">14位數包含2個正斜杠</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5907">14 digits containing 2 forward slashes</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5908">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5908">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-5909">14位數和2轉寄斜線：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5909">14 digits and 2 forward slashes:</span></span>
  
-  <span data-ttu-id="93909-5910">五位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5910">Five digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5911">一個正斜線</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5911">A forward slash</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5912">兩位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5912">Two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5913">一個正斜線</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5913">A forward slash</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5914">七位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5914">Seven digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5915">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5915">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-5916">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5916">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5917">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5917">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-5918">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5918">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5919">正則運算式會 `Regex_poland_eu_driver's_license_number` 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5919">The regular expression  `Regex_poland_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5920">找到來自的關鍵字 `Keywords_poland_eu_driver's_license_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5920">A keyword from  `Keywords_poland_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Driver's License Number -->
<Entity id="b8fe86d1-c056-453b-bfaa-9fe698699ecc" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_poland_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_poland_eu_driver's_license_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

<span data-ttu-id="93909-5922">**Keywords_poland_eu_driver ' s_license_number**</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5922">**Keywords_poland_eu_driver's_license_number**</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5923">Dl#</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5923">dl#</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5926">驅動程式許可證</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5926">driver licence</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5927">驅動程式 .lic。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5927">drivers lic.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5928">驅動程式授權</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5928">drivers license</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5929">驅動程式許可證</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5929">drivers licence</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5930">駕駛執照</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5930">driver's license</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5931">駕駛執照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5931">driver's license number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5932">駕駛執照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5932">driver's licence number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5933">駕駛執照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5933">driving license number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5935">prawo jazdy</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5935">prawo jazdy</span></span>

## <a name="poland-identity-card"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5936">波蘭身分識別卡片</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5936">Poland identity card</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5937">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5937">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-5938">三個字母和六位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5938">Three letters and six digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5939">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5939">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-5940">三個字母（不區分大小寫）後接六位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5940">Three letters (not case sensitive) followed by six digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5941">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5941">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-5942">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5942">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5943">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5943">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-5944">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：函數 Func_polish_national_id 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5944">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters: The function Func_polish_national_id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="93909-5945">會找到來自 Keyword_polish_national_id_passport_number 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5945">A keyword from Keyword_polish_national_id_passport_number is found.</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="93909-5946">校驗和通過。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5946">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Poland Identity Card-->
<Entity id="25E64989-ED5D-40CA-A939-6C14183BB7BF" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_polish_national_id" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_polish_national_id_passport_number" />
      </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5947">關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5947">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_polish_national_id_passport_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5948">Keyword_polish_national_id_passport_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5948">Keyword_polish_national_id_passport_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5949">Dowód osobisty</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5949">Dowód osobisty</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5950">轉寄 dowodu osobistego</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5950">Numer dowodu osobistego</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5951">Nazwa i 轉寄 dowodu osobistego</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5951">Nazwa i numer dowodu osobistego</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5952">Nazwa i nr dowodu osobistego</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5952">Nazwa i nr dowodu osobistego</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5953">Nazwa i nr dowodu tożsamości</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5953">Nazwa i nr dowodu tożsamości</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5954">Dowód Tożsamości</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5954">Dowód Tożsamości</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5955">道鐘斯指數。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5955">dow.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="93909-5956">作業系統。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5956">os.</span></span>

   
## <a name="poland-national-id-pesel"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5957">波蘭國民身分證 (PESEL)</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5957">Poland National ID (PESEL)</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="93909-5958">這種敏感資訊類型的實體包含在歐盟國身分識別號碼機密資訊類型中，並可作為獨立的機密資訊類型實體。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5958">This sensitive information type entity is included in the EU National Identification Number sensitive information type and is available as a stand alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5959">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5959">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-5960">11位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5960">11 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5961">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5961">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-5962">11個連續數位</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5962">11 consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5963">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5963">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-5964">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5964">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5965">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5965">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-5966">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是85%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5966">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5967">函數 Func_pesel_identification_number 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5967">The function Func_pesel_identification_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5968">會找到來自 Keyword_pesel_identification_number 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5968">A keyword from Keyword_pesel_identification_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5969">校驗和通過。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5969">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Poland National ID (PESEL) -->      
<Entity id="E3AAF206-4297-412F-9E06-BA8487E22456" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_pesel_identification_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_pesel_identification_number" />
      </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5970">關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5970">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_pesel_identification_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5971">Keyword_pesel_identification_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5971">Keyword_pesel_identification_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5972">dowód osobisty</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5972">dowód osobisty</span></span>

## <a name="poland-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5981">波蘭護照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5981">Poland passport number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="93909-5982">這個敏感資訊類型實體包含在歐盟護照號碼機密資訊類型中，並可作為獨立的敏感資訊類型實體。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5982">This sensitive information type entity is included in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type and is available as a stand alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5983">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5983">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-5984">兩個字母和七位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5984">Two letters and seven digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5985">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5985">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-5986">兩個字母（不區分大小寫）後接7位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5986">Two letters (not case sensitive) followed by seven digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5987">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5987">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-5988">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5988">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5989">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5989">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-5990">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是85%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5990">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5991">函數 Func_polish_passport_number 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5991">The function Func_polish_passport_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5992">會找到來自 Keyword_polish_national_id_passport_number 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5992">A keyword from Keyword_polish_national_id_passport_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5993">校驗和通過。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5993">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Poland Passport Number -->
<Entity id="03937FB5-D2B6-4487-B61F-0F8BFF7C3517" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_polish_passport_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_polish_national_id_passport_number" />
      </Pattern>
</Entity>
</Version>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5994">關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5994">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_polish_national_id_passport_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-5995">Keyword_polish_national_id_passport_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5995">Keyword_polish_national_id_passport_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5996">轉寄 paszportu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5996">Numer paszportu</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5997">星期日。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5997">Nr.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="93909-5998">Paszportu</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5998">Paszportu</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-5999">Paszport</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-5999">Paszport</span></span>

## <a name="poland-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-6000">波蘭納稅識別號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6000">Poland tax identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="93909-6001">此機密資訊類型實體僅可用於歐盟納稅識別碼的敏感資訊類型。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6001">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Tax Identification Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-6002">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6002">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-6003">不含空格或分隔符號的11位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6003">Eleven digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-6004">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6004">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-6005">11位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6005">Eleven digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-6006">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6006">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-6007">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6007">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-6008">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6008">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-6009">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是85%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6009">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6010">函數 `Func_poland_eu_tax_file_number` 會找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6010">The function  `Func_poland_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6011">找到來自的關鍵字 `Keywords_poland_eu_tax_file_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6011">A keyword from  `Keywords_poland_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="93909-6012">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6012">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6013">函數 `Func_poland_eu_tax_file_number` 會找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6013">The function  `Func_poland_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Tax File Number -->
<Entity id="e09c07d3-66e5-4783-989d-49ac62748f5f" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_poland_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_poland_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
<Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_poland_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="portugal-citizen-card-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-6043">葡萄牙公民卡片號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6043">Portugal citizen card number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6044">這種敏感資訊類型的實體包含在歐盟國身分識別號碼機密資訊類型中，並可作為獨立的機密資訊類型實體。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6044">This sensitive information type entity is included in the EU National Identification Number sensitive information type and is available as a stand alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6045">這種敏感資訊類型實體包含在歐盟社會保險號碼或同等識別碼的敏感資訊類型中。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6045">This sensitive information type entity is included in the EU Social Security Number or Equivalent ID sensitive information type.</span></span>


### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-6046">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6046">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-6047">八位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6047">Eight digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-6048">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6048">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-6049">八位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6049">Eight digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-6050">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6050">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-6051">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6051">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-6052">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6052">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-6053">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是85%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6053">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6054">正則運算式 Regex_portugal_citizen_card 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6054">The regular expression Regex_portugal_citizen_card finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6055">會找到來自 Keyword_portugal_citizen_card 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6055">A keyword from Keyword_portugal_citizen_card is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Portugal Citizen Card Number -->
<Entity id="91a7ece2-add4-4986-9a15-c84544d81ecd" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Regex_portugal_citizen_card"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_portugal_citizen_card"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="portugal-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-6075">葡萄牙駕駛執照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6075">Portugal driver's license number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="93909-6076">這個敏感資訊類型實體只有歐盟駕駛執照號碼機密資訊類型提供。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6076">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-6077">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6077">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-6078">兩個字母后接指定的模式中的七個數字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6078">Two letters followed by a seven numbers in the specified pattern</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-6079">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6079">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-6080">兩個字母后接7個含特殊字元的數位：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6080">Two letters followed by seven numbers with special characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6081">兩個字母（不區分大小寫）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6081">Two letters (not case-sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6082">連字號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6082">A hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6083">六位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6083">Six digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6084">一個空格</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6084">A space</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6085">一個數位</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6085">One digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-6086">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6086">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-6087">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6087">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-6088">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6088">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-6089">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6089">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6090">正則運算式會 `Regex_portugal_eu_driver's_license_number` 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6090">The regular expression  `Regex_portugal_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6091">找到來自的關鍵字 `Keywords_portugal_eu_driver's_license_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6091">A keyword from  `Keywords_portugal_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Driver's License Number -->
<Entity id="b8fe86d1-c056-453b-bfaa-9fe698699ecc" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_portugal_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_portugal_eu_driver's_license_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="portugal-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-6107">葡萄牙護照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6107">Portugal passport number</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-6111">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6111">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-6112">一個字母后接六位數：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6112">One letter followed by six digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6113">一個字母（不區分大小寫）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6113">One letter (not case sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6114">六位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6114">Six digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-6115">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6115">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-6116">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6116">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-6117">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6117">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-6118">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6118">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6119">正則運算式會 `Regex_portugal_eu_passport_number` 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6119">The regular expression  `Regex_portugal_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6120">找到來自的關鍵字 `Keywords_portugal_eu_passport_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6120">A keyword from  `Keywords_portugal_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Passport Number -->
<Entity id="21883626-6245-4f3d-9b61-5cbb43e625ee" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_portugal_eu_passport_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_portugal_eu_passport_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

<span data-ttu-id="93909-6129">九位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6129">Nine digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-6131">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6131">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-6132">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6132">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-6133">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是85%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6133">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6134">函數 `Func_portugal_eu_tax_file_number` 會找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6134">The function  `Func_portugal_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6135">找到來自的關鍵字 `Keywords_portugal_eu_tax_file_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6135">A keyword from  `Keywords_portugal_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="93909-6136">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6136">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6137">函數 `Func_portugal_eu_tax_file_number` 會找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6137">The function  `Func_portugal_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Tax File Number -->
<Entity id="e09c07d3-66e5-4783-989d-49ac62748f5f" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_portugal_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_portugal_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
<Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_portugal_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="romania-national-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-6191">羅馬尼亞國身分識別號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6191">Romania national identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="93909-6192">這個敏感資訊類型實體僅可用於歐盟國身分識別號碼的敏感資訊類型。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6192">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU National Identification Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-6193">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6193">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-6194">13位數，不含空格及分隔符號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6194">13 digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-6195">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6195">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-6196">13位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6196">13 digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-6197">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6197">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-6198">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6198">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-6199">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6199">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-6200">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是85%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6200">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6201">函數 `Func_romania_eu_national_id_card` 會找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6201">The function  `Func_romania_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6202">找到來自的關鍵字 `Keywords_romania_eu_national_id_card` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6202">A keyword from  `Keywords_romania_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="93909-6203">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6203">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6204">函數 `Func_romania_eu_national_id_card` 會找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6204">The function  `Func_romania_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!--Romania national identification number  -->
<Entity id="419f449f-6d9d-4be1-a154-b531f7a91b41" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_romania_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_romania_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
<Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_romania_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="romania-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-6255">羅馬尼亞護照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6255">Romania passport number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="93909-6256">這個敏感資訊類型實體只適用于歐盟護照號碼機密資訊類型。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6256">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-6257">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6257">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-6258">8或9位數，不含空格及分隔符號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6258">Eight or nine digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-6259">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6259">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-6260">8或9位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6260">Eight or nine digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-6261">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6261">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-6262">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6262">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-6263">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6263">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-6264">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6264">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6265">正則運算式會 `Regex_romania_eu_passport_number` 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6265">The regular expression  `Regex_romania_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6266">找到來自的關鍵字 `Keywords_romania_eu_passport_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6266">A keyword from  `Keywords_romania_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Passport Number -->
<Entity id="21883626-6245-4f3d-9b61-5cbb43e625ee" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_romania_eu_passport_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_romania_eu_passport_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-6267">關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6267">Keywords</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-6268">**Keywords_romania_eu_passport_number**</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6268">**Keywords_romania_eu_passport_number**</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6269">護照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6269">passport number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6271">護照否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6271">passport no</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6272">numărul pașaportului</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6272">numărul pașaportului</span></span>

## <a name="romania-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-6273">羅馬尼亞納稅識別號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6273">Romania tax identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="93909-6274">此機密資訊類型實體僅可用於歐盟納稅識別碼的敏感資訊類型。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6274">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Tax Identification Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-6275">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6275">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-6276">13位數沒有空格或分隔符號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6276">13 digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-6277">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6277">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-6278">13位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6278">13 digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-6279">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6279">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-6280">不適用</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6280">Not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-6281">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6281">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-6282">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6282">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6283">正則運算式會 `Regex_romania_eu_tax_file_number` 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6283">The regular expression  `Regex_romania_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6284">找到來自的關鍵字 `Keywords_romania_eu_tax_file_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6284">A keyword from  `Keywords_romania_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Tax File Number -->
<Entity id="e09c07d3-66e5-4783-989d-49ac62748f5f" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_romania_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_romania_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-6285">關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6285">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keywords_romania_eu_tax_file_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-6286">Keywords_romania_eu_tax_file_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6286">Keywords_romania_eu_tax_file_number</span></span>
