## <a name="saudi-arabia-national-id"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-6335">沙烏地阿拉伯國際身分識別</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6335">Saudi Arabia National ID</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-6336">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6336">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-6337">10位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6337">10 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-6338">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6338">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-6339">10個連續數位</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6339">10 consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-6340">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6340">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-6341">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6341">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-6342">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6342">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-6343">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6343">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6344">正則運算式 Regex_saudi_arabia_national_id 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6344">The regular expression Regex_saudi_arabia_national_id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6345">會找到來自 Keyword_saudi_arabia_national_id 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6345">A keyword from Keyword_saudi_arabia_national_id is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Saudi Arabia National ID -->
<Entity id="8c5a0ba8-404a-41a3-8871-746aa21ee6c0" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_saudi_arabia_national_id" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_saudi_arabia_national_id" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-6346">關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6346">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_saudi_arabia_national_id"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-6347">Keyword_saudi_arabia_national_id</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6347">Keyword_saudi_arabia_national_id</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6348">身分識別卡</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6348">Identification Card</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6349">我的卡片編號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6349">I card number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6350">識別碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6350">ID number</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6351">الوطنية الهوية بطاقة رقم</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6351">الوطنية الهوية بطاقة رقم</span></span> 

   
## <a name="singapore-national-registration-identity-card-nric-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-6352">新加坡國家註冊身分識別卡片（NRIC）號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6352">Singapore national registration identity card (NRIC) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-6353">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6353">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-6354">九個字母和數位</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6354">Nine letters and digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-6355">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6355">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6356">九個字母和數位：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6356">Nine letters and digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6357">字母 "F"、"G"、"S" 或 "T" （不區分大小寫）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6357">The letter "F", "G", "S", or "T" (not case sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6358">七位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6358">Seven digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6359">字母檢查碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6359">An alphabetic check digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-6360">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6360">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-6361">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6361">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-6362">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6362">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-6363">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是85%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6363">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6364">正則運算式 Regex_singapore_nric 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6364">The regular expression Regex_singapore_nric finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6365">會找到來自 Keyword_singapore_nric 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6365">A keyword from Keyword_singapore_nric is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6366">校驗和通過。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6366">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-6367">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6367">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6368">正則運算式 Regex_singapore_nric 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6368">The regular expression Regex_singapore_nric finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6369">校驗和通過。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6369">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Singapore National Registration Identity Card (NRIC) Number -->
<Entity id="cead390a-dd83-4856-9751-fb6dc98c34da" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Regex_singapore_nric"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_singapore_nric"/>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Regex_singapore_nric"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-6370">關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6370">Keywords</span></span>

## <a name="slovakia-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-6380">斯洛伐克駕照編號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6380">Slovakia driver's license number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="93909-6381">這個敏感資訊類型實體只有歐盟駕駛執照號碼機密資訊類型提供。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6381">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-6382">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6382">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-6383">一個字元後接7位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6383">One character followed by seven digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-6384">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6384">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-6385">一個字元後接7位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6385">One character followed by seven digits</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6386">一個字母（不區分大小寫）或數位</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6386">One letter (not case-sensitive) or digit</span></span>
-  <span data-ttu-id="93909-6387">七位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6387">Seven digits</span></span> 
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-6388">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6388">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-6389">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6389">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-6390">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6390">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-6391">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6391">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6392">正則運算式會 `Regex_slovakia_eu_driver's_license_number` 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6392">The regular expression  `Regex_slovakia_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6393">找到來自的關鍵字 `Keywords_slovakia_eu_driver's_license_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6393">A keyword from  `Keywords_slovakia_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Driver's License Number -->
<Entity id="b8fe86d1-c056-453b-bfaa-9fe698699ecc" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_slovaknia_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_slovakia_eu_driver's_license_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-6394">關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6394">Keywords</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-6395">**Keywords_slovakia_eu_driver ' s_license_number**</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6395">**Keywords_slovakia_eu_driver's_license_number**</span></span>

## <a name="slovakia-national-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-6398">斯洛伐克國身分識別號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6398">Slovakia national identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="93909-6399">這個敏感資訊類型實體僅可用於歐盟國身分識別號碼的敏感資訊類型。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6399">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU National Identification Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-6400">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6400">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-6401">10位數包含一個反斜線</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6401">Ten digits containing one backslash</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-6402">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6402">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-6403">10位數包含一個反斜線：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6403">Ten digits containing one backslash:</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-6404">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6404">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-6405">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6405">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-6406">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6406">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-6407">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是85%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6407">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6408">函數 `Func_slovakia_eu_national_id_card` 會找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6408">The function  `Func_slovakia_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6409">找到來自的關鍵字 `Keywords_slovakia_eu_national_id_card` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6409">A keyword from  `Keywords_slovakia_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="93909-6410">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6410">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6411">函數 `Func_slovakia_eu_national_id_card` 會找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6411">The function  `Func_slovakia_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- Slovakia national identification number -->
<Entity id="419f449f-6d9d-4be1-a154-b531f7a91b41" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_slovakia_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_slovakia_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
<Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_slovakia_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="slovakia-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-6458">斯洛伐克護照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6458">Slovakia passport number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="93909-6459">這個敏感資訊類型實體只適用于歐盟護照號碼機密資訊類型。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6459">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-6460">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6460">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-6461">一個數位或字母后接7位數，不含空格或分隔符號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6461">One digit or letter followed by seven digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-6462">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6462">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-6463">一個數位或字母（不區分大小寫）後接7位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6463">One digit or letter (not case sensitive) followed by seven digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-6464">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6464">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-6465">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6465">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-6466">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6466">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-6467">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6467">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6468">正則運算式會 `Regex_slovakia_eu_passport_number` 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6468">The regular expression  `Regex_slovakia_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6469">找到來自的關鍵字 `Keywords_slovakia_eu_passport_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6469">A keyword from  `Keywords_slovakia_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Passport Number -->
<Entity id="21883626-6245-4f3d-9b61-5cbb43e625ee" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_slovakia_eu_passport_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_slovakia_eu_passport_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-6470">關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6470">Keywords</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-6471">**Keywords_slovakia_eu_passport_number**</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6471">**Keywords_slovakia_eu_passport_number**</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-6477">此機密資訊類型實體僅可用於歐盟納稅識別碼的敏感資訊類型。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6477">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Tax Identification Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-6479">10位數，不含空格或分隔符號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6479">10 digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-6480">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6480">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-6481">10位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6481">10 digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-6482">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6482">Checksum</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-6484">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6484">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-6485">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6485">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6486">正則運算式會 `Regex_slovakia_eu_tax_file_number` 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6486">The regular expression  `Regex_slovakia_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6487">找到來自的關鍵字 `Keywords_slovakia_eu_tax_file_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6487">A keyword from  `Keywords_slovakia_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Tax File Number -->
<Entity id="e09c07d3-66e5-4783-989d-49ac62748f5f" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_slovakia_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_slovakia_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="slovenia-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-6534">斯洛維尼亞駕照編號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6534">Slovenia driver's license number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="93909-6535">這個敏感資訊類型實體只有歐盟駕駛執照號碼機密資訊類型提供。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6535">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-6536">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6536">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-6537">九位數，不含空格及分隔符號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6537">Nine digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-6538">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6538">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-6539">九位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6539">Nine digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-6540">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6540">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-6541">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6541">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-6542">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6542">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-6543">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6543">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6544">正則運算式會 `Regex_slovenia_eu_driver's_license_number` 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6544">The regular expression  `Regex_slovenia_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6545">找到來自的關鍵字 `Keywords_slovenia_eu_driver's_license_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6545">A keyword from  `Keywords_slovenia_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Driver's License Number -->
<Entity id="b8fe86d1-c056-453b-bfaa-9fe698699ecc" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_slovenia_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_slovenia_eu_driver's_license_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="slovenia-national-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-6561">斯洛維尼亞國身分識別號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6561">Slovenia national identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="93909-6562">這個敏感資訊類型實體僅可用於歐盟國身分識別號碼的敏感資訊類型。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6562">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU National Identification Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-6563">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6563">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-6564">13位數，不含空格或分隔符號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6564">13 digits without spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-6565">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6565">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-6566">指定的模式中的13位數：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6566">13 digits in the specified pattern:</span></span>
  
-  <span data-ttu-id="93909-6567">對應至出生日期（DDMMLLL）的7位數，其中 "LLL" 會對應至出生年份的後三位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6567">Seven digits that correspond to the birth date (DDMMLLL) where "LLL" corresponds to the last three digits of the birth year</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6568">對應至出生區域的兩位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6568">Two digits that correspond to the area of birth</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6569">三個數字，對應于一天出生的性別和序號碼組合（000-499 的插頭和500-999 的女）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6569">Three digits that correspond to a combination of gender and serial number for persons born on the same day (000-499 for male and 500-999 for female)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6570">一個檢查碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6570">One check digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-6571">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6571">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-6572">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6572">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-6573">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6573">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-6574">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是85%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6574">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6575">函數 `Func_slovenia_eu_national_id_card` 會找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6575">The function  `Func_slovenia_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6576">找到來自的關鍵字 `Keywords_slovenia_eu_national_id_card` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6576">A keyword from  `Keywords_slovenia_eu_national_id_card` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="93909-6577">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6577">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6578">函數 `Func_slovenia_eu_national_id_card` 會找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6578">The function  `Func_slovenia_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- Slovenia national identification number -->
<Entity id="419f449f-6d9d-4be1-a154-b531f7a91b41" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_slovenia_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_slovenia_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
<Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_slovenia_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="slovenia-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-6606">斯洛維尼亞護照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6606">Slovenia passport number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="93909-6607">這個敏感資訊類型實體只適用于歐盟護照號碼機密資訊類型。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6607">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-6608">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6608">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-6609">兩個字母后接7位數，不含空格或分隔符號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6609">Two letters followed by seven digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-6610">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6610">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-6611">兩個字母后接7位數：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6611">Two letters followed by seven digits:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6612">字母 "P"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6612">The letter "P"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6613">單一大寫字母</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6613">One uppercase letter</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6614">七位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6614">Seven digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-6615">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6615">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-6616">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6616">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-6617">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6617">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-6618">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6618">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6619">正則運算式會 `Regex_slovenia_eu_passport_number` 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6619">The regular expression  `Regex_slovenia_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6620">找到來自的關鍵字 `Keywords_slovenia_eu_passport_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6620">A keyword from  `Keywords_slovenia_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Passport Number -->
<Entity id="21883626-6245-4f3d-9b61-5cbb43e625ee" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_slovenia_eu_passport_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_slovenia_eu_passport_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-6621">關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6621">Keywords</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-6622">**Keywords_slovenia_eu_passport_number**</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6622">**Keywords_slovenia_eu_passport_number**</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-6623">護照號碼斯洛維尼亞護照號碼護照 no številka potnega lista</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6623">passport number slovenian passport number passport no številka potnega lista</span></span>

## <a name="slovenia-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-6624">斯洛維尼亞納稅識別號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6624">Slovenia tax identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="93909-6625">此機密資訊類型實體僅可用於歐盟納稅識別碼的敏感資訊類型。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6625">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Tax Identification Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-6626">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6626">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-6627">八位數沒有空格或分隔符號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6627">Eight digits with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-6628">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6628">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-6629">八位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6629">Eight digits</span></span>
  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-6630">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6630">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-6631">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6631">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-6632">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6632">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-6633">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是85%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6633">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6634">函數 `Func_slovenia_eu_tax_file_number` 會找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6634">The function  `Func_slovenia_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6635">找到來自的關鍵字 `Keywords_slovenia_eu_tax_file_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6635">A keyword from  `Keywords_slovenia_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="93909-6636">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6636">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6637">函數 `Func_slovenia_eu_tax_file_number` 會找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6637">The function  `Func_slovenia_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Tax File Number -->
<Entity id="e09c07d3-66e5-4783-989d-49ac62748f5f" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_nation_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_nation_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
<Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_slovenia_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="south-africa-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-6661">南非識別號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6661">South Africa identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-6662">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6662">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-6663">可以包含空格的13位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6663">13 digits that may contain spaces</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-6664">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6664">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-6665">13位數：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6665">13 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6666">YYMMDD 之日期格式的六位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6666">Six digits in the format YYMMDD which are the date of birth</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6667">四位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6667">Four digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6668">單一數位的公民指示器</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6668">A single-digit citizenship indicator</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6669">數位 "8" 或 "9"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6669">The digit "8" or "9"</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6670">一個數位的校驗和位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6670">One digit which is a checksum digit</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-6671">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6671">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-6672">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6672">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-6673">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6673">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-6674">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是85%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6674">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6675">函數 Func_south_africa_identification_number 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6675">The function Func_south_africa_identification_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6676">會找到來自 Keyword_south_africa_identification_number 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6676">A keyword from Keyword_south_africa_identification_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6677">校驗和通過。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6677">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- South Africa Identification Number -->
<Entity id="e2adf7cb-8ea6-4048-a2ed-d89eb65f2780" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_south_africa_identification_number"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_south_africa_identification_number"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-6678">關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6678">Keywords</span></span>

## <a name="south-korea-resident-registration-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-6683">韓國居民登記號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6683">South Korea resident registration number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-6684">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6684">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-6685">13位數包含連字號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6685">13 digits containing a hyphen</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-6686">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6686">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-6687">13位數：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6687">13 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6688">YYMMDD 之日期格式的六位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6688">Six digits in the format YYMMDD which are the date of birth</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6689">連字號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6689">A hyphen</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6690">一個數位是由世紀和性別決定</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6690">One digit determined by the century and gender</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6691">四位數的出生區功能變數代碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6691">Four-digit region-of-birth code</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6692">一種用來區分先前號碼相同之人員的數位</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6692">One digit used to differentiate people for whom the preceding numbers are identical</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6693">檢查碼。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6693">A check digit.</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-6694">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6694">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-6695">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6695">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-6696">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6696">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-6697">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是85%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6697">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6698">函數 Func_south_korea_resident_number 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6698">The function Func_south_korea_resident_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6699">會找到來自 Keyword_south_korea_resident_number 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6699">A keyword from Keyword_south_korea_resident_number is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6700">校驗和通過。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6700">The checksum passes.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-6701">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6701">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6702">函數 Func_south_korea_resident_number 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6702">The function Func_south_korea_resident_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6703">校驗和通過。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6703">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- South Korea Resident Registration Number -->
<Entity id="5b802e18-ba80-44c4-bc83-bf2ad36ae36a" recommendedConfidence="85" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_south_korea_resident_number"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_south_korea_resident_number"/>
  </Pattern>
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Func_south_korea_resident_number"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-6704">關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6704">Keywords</span></span>
   
#### <a name="keyword_south_korea_resident_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-6705">Keyword_south_korea_resident_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6705">Keyword_south_korea_resident_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6706">國民身分證</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6706">National ID card</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6707">公民註冊號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6707">Citizen's Registration Number</span></span>

## <a name="spain-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-6711">西班牙駕照編號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6711">Spain driver's license number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="93909-6712">這個敏感資訊類型實體只有歐盟駕駛執照號碼機密資訊類型提供。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6712">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-6713">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6713">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-6714">八位數後接一個字元</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6714">Eight digits followed by one character</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-6715">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6715">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-6716">八位數後接一個字元：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6716">Eight digits followed by one character:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6717">八位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6717">Eight digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6718">一個數位或字母（不區分大小寫）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6718">One digit or letter (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-6719">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6719">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-6720">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6720">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-6721">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6721">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-6722">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6722">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6723">函數 `Func_spain_eu_driver's_license_number` 會找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6723">The function  `Func_spain_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6724">找到來自的關鍵字 `Keywords_spain_eu_driver's_license_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6724">A keyword from  `Keywords_spain_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Driver's License Number -->
<Entity id="b8fe86d1-c056-453b-bfaa-9fe698699ecc" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spain_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_spain_eu_driver's_license_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="spain-national-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-6761">西班牙國身分識別號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6761">Spain national identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="93909-6762">這個敏感資訊類型實體僅可用於歐盟國身分識別號碼的敏感資訊類型。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6762">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU National Identification Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-6763">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6763">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-6764">七位數後接一個字元</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6764">Seven digits followed by one character</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-6765">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6765">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-6766">七位數後接一個字元</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6766">Seven digits followed by one character</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6767">七位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6767">Seven digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6768">一個數位或字母（不區分大小寫）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6768">One digit or letter (not case-sensitive)</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-6769">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6769">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-6770">不適用</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6770">Not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-6771">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6771">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-6772">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6772">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6773">正則運算式會 `Regex_spain_eu_national_id_card` 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6773">The regular expression  `Regex_spain_eu_national_id_card` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6774">找到來自的關鍵字 `Keywords_spain_eu_national_id_card"` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6774">A keyword from  `Keywords_spain_eu_national_id_card"` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
<!-- Spain national identification number -->
 
<Entity id="419f449f-6d9d-4be1-a154-b531f7a91b41" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_spain_eu_national_id_card" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_spain_eu_national_id_card" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="spain-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-6798">西班牙護照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6798">Spain passport number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="93909-6799">這個敏感資訊類型實體只適用于歐盟護照號碼機密資訊類型。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6799">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-6800">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6800">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-6801">8或9個字元組合的字母和數位，不含空格或分隔符號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6801">An eight- or nine-character combination of letters and numbers with no spaces or delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-6802">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6802">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-6803">字母和數位的8或9個字元組合：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6803">An eight- or nine-character combination of letters and numbers:</span></span>
  
-  <span data-ttu-id="93909-6804">兩位數或字母</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6804">Two digits or letters</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6805">一個數位或字母（選用）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6805">One digit or letter (optional)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6806">六位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6806">Six digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-6807">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6807">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-6808">不適用</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6808">Not applicable</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-6809">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6809">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-6810">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6810">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6811">正則運算式會 `Regex_spain_eu_passport_number` 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6811">The regular expression  `Regex_spain_eu_passport_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6812">找到來自的關鍵字 `Keywords_spain_eu_passport_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6812">A keyword from  `Keywords_spain_eu_passport_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Passport Number -->
<Entity id="21883626-6245-4f3d-9b61-5cbb43e625ee" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_spain_eu_passport_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_spain_eu_passport_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-6813">關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6813">Keywords</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-6814">**Keywords_spain_eu_passport_number**</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6814">**Keywords_spain_eu_passport_number**</span></span>

## <a name="spain-social-security-number-ssn"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-6824">西班牙社會安全號碼（SSN）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6824">Spain social security number (SSN)</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="93909-6825">此機密資訊類型的實體包含在歐盟社會保險號碼或同等識別碼的敏感資訊類型中，並可作為獨立的敏感資訊類型實體。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6825">This sensitive information type entity is included in the EU Social Security Number or Equivalent ID sensitive information type and is available as a stand alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-6826">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6826">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-6827">11-12 位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6827">11-12 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-6828">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6828">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-6829">11-12 位數：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6829">11-12 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6830">兩位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6830">Two digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6831">一個正斜線（選用）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6831">A forward slash (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6832">7-8 位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6832">7-8 digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6833">一個正斜線（選用）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6833">A forward slash (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6834">兩位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6834">Two digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-6835">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6835">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-6836">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6836">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-6837">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6837">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-6838">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是85%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6838">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6839">函數 Func_spanish_social_security_number 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6839">The function Func_spanish_social_security_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6840">校驗和通過。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6840">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Spain SSN -->
<Entity id="5df987c0-8eae-4bce-ace7-b316347f3070" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_spanish_social_security_number" />
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-6841">關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6841">Keywords</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-6842">無</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6842">None</span></span>

## <a name="spain-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-6843">西班牙納稅識別號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6843">Spain tax identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="93909-6844">此機密資訊類型實體僅可用於歐盟納稅識別碼的敏感資訊類型。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6844">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Tax Identification Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-6845">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6845">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-6846">指定的模式中的7或8位數，以及一或兩個字母</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6846">Seven or eight digits and one or two letters in the specified pattern</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-6847">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6847">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-6848">具有西班牙國身分識別卡的西班牙文自然人員：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6848">Spanish Natural Persons with a Spain National Identity Card:</span></span>
  
-  <span data-ttu-id="93909-6849">八位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6849">Eight digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6850">單一大寫字母（區分大小寫）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6850">One uppercase letter (case-sensitive)</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="93909-6851">沒有西班牙國身分身分身分識別卡的非居民 Spaniards</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6851">Non-resident Spaniards without a Spain National Identity Card</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6852">一個大寫字母 "L" （區分大小寫）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6852">One uppercase letter "L" (case-sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6853">七位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6853">Seven digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6854">單一大寫字母（區分大小寫）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6854">One uppercase letter (case-sensitive)</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="93909-6855">在沒有西班牙國身分識別卡的14年年齡底下的居民 Spaniards：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6855">Resident Spaniards under the age of 14 years without a Spain National Identity Card :</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6856">一個大寫字母 "K" （區分大小寫）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6856">One uppercase letter"K" (case-sensitive)</span></span>
-  <span data-ttu-id="93909-6857">七位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6857">Seven digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6858">單一大寫字母（區分大小寫）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6858">One uppercase letter (case-sensitive)</span></span>
    
<span data-ttu-id="93909-6859">Foreigners 與 Foreigner 的識別號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6859">Foreigners with a Foreigner's Identification Number</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6860">一個大寫的字母，為 "X"、"Y" 或 "Z" （區分大小寫）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6860">One uppercase letter that is "X", "Y", or "Z" (case-sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6861">七位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6861">Seven digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6862">單一大寫字母（區分大小寫）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6862">One uppercase letter (case-sensitive)</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="93909-6863">沒有 Foreigner 識別碼的 Foreigners</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6863">Foreigners without a Foreigner's Identification Number</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6864">一個大寫的字母 "M" （區分大小寫）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6864">One uppercase letter that is "M" (case-sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6865">七位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6865">Seven digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6866">單一大寫字母（區分大小寫）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6866">One uppercase letter (case-sensitive)</span></span> 
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-6867">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6867">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-6868">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6868">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-6869">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6869">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-6870">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是85%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6870">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6871">函數 `Func_spain_eu_tax_file_number` 會找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6871">The function  `Func_spain_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6872">找到來自的關鍵字 `Keywords_spain_eu_tax_file_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6872">A keyword from  `Keywords_spain_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="93909-6873">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6873">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6874">函數 `Func_spain_eu_tax_file_number` 會找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6874">The function  `Func_spain_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Tax File Number -->
<Entity id="e09c07d3-66e5-4783-989d-49ac62748f5f" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spain_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_spain_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
<Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_spain_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="sql-server-connection-string"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-6905">SQL Server 連接字串</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6905">SQL Server connection string</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-6906">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6906">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-6907">字串 "User Id"、"User ID"、"uid" 或 "UserId"，後面加上下列模式中所述的字元及字串。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6907">The string "User Id", "User ID", "uid", or "UserId" followed by the characters and strings outlined in the pattern below.</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-6908">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6908">Pattern</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6909">字串 "User Id"、"User ID"、"uid" 或 "UserId"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6909">The string "User Id", "User ID", "uid", or "UserId"</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6910">介於1-200 小寫或大寫字母、數位、符號、特殊字元或空格之間的任何組合</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6910">Any combination of between 1-200 lower- or uppercase letters, digits, symbols, special characters, or spaces</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6911">字串 "Password" 或 "pwd"，其中 "pwd" 前面不是小寫字母</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6911">The string "Password" or "pwd" where "pwd" is not preceded by a lowercase letter</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6912">等號（=）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6912">An equal sign (=)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6913">不是貨幣符號（$）的任何字元、百分比符號（%）、大於符號（>）、符號（@）、引號（"）、分號（;)、左大括弧（[）或左中括弧（{）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6913">Any character that is not a dollar sign ($), percent symbol (%), greater than symbol (>), at symbol (@), quotation mark ("), semicolon (;), left brace([), or left bracket ({)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6914">任何7-128 個字元的組合，不是分號（;)、正斜線（/）或引號（"）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6914">Any combination of 7-128 characters that are not a semicolon (;), forward slash (/), or quotation mark (")</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6915">一個分號（;)或引號（"）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6915">A semicolon (;) or quotation mark (")</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-6916">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6916">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-6917">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6917">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-6918">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6918">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-6919">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是85%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6919">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6920">正則運算式 CEP_Regex_SQLServerConnectionString 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6920">The regular expression CEP_Regex_SQLServerConnectionString finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6921">找**不**到來自 CEP_GlobalFilter 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6921">A keyword from CEP_GlobalFilter is **not** found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6922">正則運算式**CEP_PasswordPlaceHolder 不會找到符合**模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6922">The regular expression CEP_PasswordPlaceHolder does **not** find content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6923">正則運算式**CEP_CommonExampleKeywords 不會找到符合**模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6923">The regular expression CEP_CommonExampleKeywords does **not** find content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```sql
<!---SQL Server Connection String>
<Entity id="e76b6205-d3cb-46f2-bd63-c90153f2f97d" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="CEP_Regex_SQLServerConnectionString" />
        <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
            <Match idRef="CEP_GlobalFilter" />
            <Match idRef="CEP_PasswordPlaceHolder" />
            <Match idRef="CEP_CommonExampleKeywords" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-6924">關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6924">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="cep_globalfilter"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-6925">CEP_GlobalFilter</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6925">CEP_GlobalFilter</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6926">部分密碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6926">some-password</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6927">somepassword</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6927">somepassword</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6928">secretPassword</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6928">secretPassword</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6929">樣品</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6929">sample</span></span>

#### <a name="cep_passwordplaceholder"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-6930">CEP_PasswordPlaceHolder</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6930">CEP_PasswordPlaceHolder</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-6931">（請注意，在技術上而言，這個敏感資訊類型是使用正則運算式來識別這些關鍵字，而不是關鍵字清單。）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6931">(Note that technically, this sensitive information type identifies these keywords by using a regular expression, not a keyword list.)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6932">密碼或密碼後接0-2 個空格、等號（=）、0-2 空間及星號（\*）-OR------------------</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6932">Password or pwd followed by 0-2 spaces, an equal sign (=), 0-2 spaces, and an asterisk (\*) --OR--</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6933">密碼或密碼，接著：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6933">Password or pwd followed by:</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="93909-6934">等號（=）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6934">Equal sign (=)</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="93909-6935">小於符號（<）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6935">Less than symbol (<)</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="93909-6936">1-200 個字元的任何組合，其大小大寫或小寫字母、數位、星號（\*）、連字號（-）、底線（_）或空白字元</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6936">Any combination of 1-200 characters that are upper- or lowercase letters, digits, an asterisk (\*), hyphen (-), underline (_), or whitespace character</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="93909-6937">大於符號（>）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6937">Greater than symbol (>)</span></span>

#### <a name="cep_commonexamplekeywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-6938">CEP_CommonExampleKeywords</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6938">CEP_CommonExampleKeywords</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-6939">（請注意，在技術上而言，這個敏感資訊類型是使用正則運算式來識別這些關鍵字，而不是關鍵字清單。）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6939">(Note that technically, this sensitive information type identifies these keywords by using a regular expression, not a keyword list.)</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6940">尚未</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6940">contoso</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6941">送交</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6941">fabrikam</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6942">資料庫</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6942">northwind</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6943">沙 箱</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6943">sandbox</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6944">onebox</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6944">onebox</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6945">本地 主機</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6945">localhost</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6946">127.0.0.1</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6946">127.0.0.1</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6947">testacs.</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6947">testacs.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="93909-6948">Com</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6948">com</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6949">s-int。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6949">s-int.</span></span><!--no-hyperlink--><span data-ttu-id="93909-6950">網</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6950">net</span></span>

## <a name="sweden-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-6951">瑞典駕駛執照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6951">Sweden driver's license number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="93909-6952">這個敏感資訊類型實體只有歐盟駕駛執照號碼機密資訊類型提供。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6952">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-6953">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6953">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-6954">10位數包含連字號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6954">Ten digits containing a hyphen</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-6955">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6955">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-6956">10位數包含連字號：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6956">Ten digits containing a hyphen:</span></span>
  
-  <span data-ttu-id="93909-6957">六位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6957">Six digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6958">連字號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6958">A hyphen</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6959">四位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6959">Four digits</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-6960">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6960">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-6961">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6961">No</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-6962">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6962">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-6963">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6963">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6964">正則運算式會 `Regex_sweden_eu_driver's_license_number` 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6964">The regular expression  `Regex_sweden_eu_driver's_license_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6965">找到來自的關鍵字 `Keywords_sweden_eu_driver's_license_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6965">A keyword from  `Keywords_sweden_eu_driver's_license_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Driver's License Number -->
<Entity id="b8fe86d1-c056-453b-bfaa-9fe698699ecc" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Regex_sweden_eu_driver's_license_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_sweden_eu_driver's_license_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity> 
```

<span data-ttu-id="93909-6967">**Keywords_sweden_eu_driver ' s_license_number**</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6967">**Keywords_sweden_eu_driver's_license_number**</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6970">駕駛執照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6970">driver license number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6971">驅動程式許可證</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6971">driver licence</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6973">驅動程式授權</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6973">drivers license</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6974">驅動程式許可證</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6974">drivers licence</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6975">駕駛執照</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6975">driver's license</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6976">駕駛執照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6976">driver's license number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6977">駕駛執照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6977">driver's licence number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6978">駕駛執照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6978">driving license number</span></span>

## <a name="sweden-national-id"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-6981">瑞典國民身分證號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6981">Sweden National ID</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="93909-6982">這種敏感資訊類型的實體包含在歐盟國身分識別號碼機密資訊類型中，並可作為獨立的機密資訊類型實體。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6982">This sensitive information type entity is included in the EU National Identification Number sensitive information type and is available as a stand alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-6983">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6983">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-6984">10或12位數和選擇性分隔符號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6984">10 or 12 digits and an optional delimiter</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-6985">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6985">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-6986">10或12位數和選用的分隔符號：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6986">10 or 12 digits and an optional delimiter:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6987">2-4 位數（選用）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6987">2-4 digits (optional)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6988">日期格式 YYMMDD 的六位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6988">Six digits in date format YYMMDD</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6989">分隔符號 "-" 或 "+" （選用），加上</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6989">Delimiter of "-" or "+" (optional), plus</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6990">四位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6990">Four digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-6991">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6991">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-6992">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6992">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-6993">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6993">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-6994">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是85%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6994">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6995">函數 Func_swedish_national_identifier 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6995">The function Func_swedish_national_identifier finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-6996">校驗和通過。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6996">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Sweden National ID -->
<Entity id="f69aaf40-79be-4fac-8f05-fd1910d272c8" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_swedish_national_identifier" />
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-6997">關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6997">Keywords</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-6998">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6998">No</span></span>
   
## <a name="sweden-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-6999">瑞典護照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-6999">Sweden passport number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="93909-7000">這個敏感資訊類型實體包含在歐盟護照號碼機密資訊類型中，並可作為獨立的敏感資訊類型實體。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7000">This sensitive information type entity is included in the EU Passport Number sensitive information type and is available as a stand alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-7001">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7001">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-7002">八位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7002">Eight digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-7003">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7003">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-7004">八個連續數位</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7004">Eight consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-7005">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7005">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-7006">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7006">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-7007">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7007">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-7008">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7008">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7009">正則運算式 Regex_sweden_passport_number 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7009">The regular expression Regex_sweden_passport_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7010">下列其中一項為真：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7010">One of the following is true:</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="93909-7011">會找到來自 Keyword_passport 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7011">A keyword from Keyword_passport is found.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="93909-7012">會找到來自 Keyword_sweden_passport 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7012">A keyword from Keyword_sweden_passport is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Sweden Passport Number -->
<Entity id="ba4e7456-55a9-4d89-9140-c33673553526" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_sweden_passport_number" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_passport" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_sweden_passport" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-7013">關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7013">Keywords</span></span>
   
#### <a name="keyword_sweden_passport"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-7014">Keyword_sweden_passport</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7014">Keyword_sweden_passport</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7015">簽證要求</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7015">visa requirements</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7016">外部註冊卡</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7016">Alien Registration Card</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7017">Schengen 簽證</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7017">Schengen visas</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7018">Schengen 簽證</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7018">Schengen visa</span></span>
