## <a name="sweden-social-security-number-or-equivalent-identification"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-7043">瑞典社會安全號碼或對等身分識別</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7043">Sweden social security number or equivalent identification</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="93909-7044">這個敏感資訊類型實體只有歐盟社會保險號碼或同等識別碼的敏感資訊類型提供。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7044">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Social Security Number or Equivalent ID sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-7045">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7045">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-7046">12位數，不含空格及分隔符號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7046">12 digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-7047">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7047">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-7048">12位數：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7048">12 digits:</span></span>
  
-  <span data-ttu-id="93909-7049">對應至出生日期的八位數（YYYYMMDD）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7049">Eight digits that correspond to the birth date (YYYYMMDD)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7050">對應至序數的三位數，其中：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7050">Three digits that correspond to a serial number where:</span></span> 
  - <span data-ttu-id="93909-7051">序數中的最後一個數位是由為男指派的奇數和偶數的女數位來表示性別</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7051">The last digit in the serial number indicates gender by the assignment of an odd number for male and an even number for female</span></span>
  - <span data-ttu-id="93909-7052">最多1990，corresponded 序數的指派給在該縣內，號碼的持有者是出生的，或（如果是在1947之前出生），在該縣中，根據稅收記錄，在年1月 1 1947 日，使用特殊的程式碼（通常是9，7位數）進行 immigrants</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7052">Up to 1990, the assignment of serial number corresponded to the county where the bearer of the number was born or (if born before 1947) where he/she had been living, according to tax records, on January 1, 1947, with a special code (usually 9 as the 7th digit) for immigrants</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7053">一個檢查碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7053">One check digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-7054">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7054">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-7055">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7055">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-7056">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7056">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-7057">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是85%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7057">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7058">函數 `Func_sweden_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` 會找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7058">The function  `Func_sweden_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7059">找到來自的關鍵字 `Keywords_sweden_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7059">A keyword from  `Keywords_sweden_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="93909-7060">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7060">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7061">函數 `Func_sweden_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` 會找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7061">The function  `Func_sweden_eu_ssn_or_equivalent` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU SSN or Equivalent Number -->
<Entity id="d24e32a4-c0bb-4ba8-899d-6303b95742d9" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_sweden_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_sweden_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
        </Pattern> 
       <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_sweden_eu_ssn_or_equivalent" />
        </Pattern>      
</Entity>
```

## <a name="sweden-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-7077">瑞典納稅識別號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7077">Sweden tax identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="93909-7078">此機密資訊類型實體僅可用於歐盟納稅識別碼的敏感資訊類型。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7078">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Tax Identification Number sensitive information type.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-7079">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7079">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-7080">指定之模式中的10位數和符號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7080">Ten digits and a symbol in the specified pattern</span></span>
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-7081">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7081">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-7082">10位數和符號：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7082">Ten digits and a symbol:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7083">與出生日期對應的六位數（YYMMDD）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7083">Six digits that correspond to the birth date (YYMMDD)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7084">正負號或反斜線</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7084">A plus sign, minus sign, or backslash</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7085">在下列情況下，識別號碼唯一的三位數：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7085">Three digits that make the identification number unique where:</span></span> 
  - <span data-ttu-id="93909-7086">若為1990之前所簽發的號碼，第七和第八位數識別出生的縣或對外出生的人員</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7086">For numbers issued before 1990, the seventh and eighth digit identify the county of birth or foreign-born people</span></span>
  - <span data-ttu-id="93909-7087">第九個位置中的位數會以奇數為單位表示，甚至是對女的性別</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7087">The digit in the ninth position indicates gender by either odd for male or even for female</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7088">一個檢查碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7088">One check digit</span></span>
    
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-7089">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7089">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-7090">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7090">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-7091">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7091">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-7092">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是85%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7092">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7093">函數 `Func_sweden_eu_tax_file_number` 會找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7093">The function  `Func_sweden_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7094">找到來自的關鍵字 `Keywords_sweden_eu_tax_file_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7094">A keyword from  `Keywords_sweden_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
<span data-ttu-id="93909-7095">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7095">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7096">函數 `Func_sweden_eu_tax_file_number` 會找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7096">The function  `Func_sweden_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
```xml
 <!-- EU Tax File Number -->
<Entity id="e09c07d3-66e5-4783-989d-49ac62748f5f" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_sweden_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_sweden_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
<Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_sweden_eu_tax_file_number" />
        </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="swift-code"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-7122">SWIFT 程式碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7122">SWIFT code</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-7123">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7123">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-7124">四個字母后接5-31 個字母或數位</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7124">Four letters followed by 5-31 letters or digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-7125">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7125">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-7126">四個字母后接5-31 個字母或數位：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7126">Four letters followed by 5-31 letters or digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7127">四個字母的銀行代碼（不區分大小寫）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7127">Four-letter bank code (not case sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7128">選擇性的空格</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7128">An optional space</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7129">4-28 個字母或數位（基本銀行帳戶號碼（BBAN））</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7129">4-28 letters or digits (the Basic Bank Account Number (BBAN))</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7130">選擇性的空格</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7130">An optional space</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7131">1-3 個字母或數位（BBAN 的其餘部分）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7131">1-3 letters or digits (remainder of the BBAN)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-7132">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7132">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-7133">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7133">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-7134">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7134">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-7135">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7135">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7136">正則運算式 Regex_swift 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7136">The regular expression Regex_swift finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7137">會找到來自 Keyword_swift 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7137">A keyword from Keyword_swift is found.</span></span>

```xml
<Entity id="cb2ab58c-9cb8-4c81-baf8-a4e106791df4" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
<Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_swift" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_swift" />
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="taiwan-national-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-7171">臺灣國身分識別號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7171">Taiwan national identification number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-7172">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7172">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-7173">一個字母（英文）後後的九位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7173">One letter (in English) followed by nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-7174">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7174">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-7175">一個字母（英文）後接9位數：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7175">One letter (in English) followed by nine digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7176">一個字母（英文、不區分大小寫）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7176">One letter (in English, not case sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7177">數位 "1" 或 "2"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7177">The digit "1" or "2"</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7178">八位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7178">Eight digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-7179">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7179">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-7180">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7180">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-7181">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7181">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-7182">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是85%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7182">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7183">函數 Func_taiwanese_national_id 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7183">The function Func_taiwanese_national_id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7184">會找到來自 Keyword_taiwanese_national_id 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7184">A keyword from Keyword_taiwanese_national_id is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7185">校驗和通過。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7185">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Taiwanese National ID -->
<Entity id="4C7BFC34-8DD1-421D-8FB7-6C6182C2AF03" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_taiwanese_national_id" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_taiwanese_national_id" />
      </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7194">身分證號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7194">身分證號碼</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7195">身份證號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7195">身份證號</span></span>

## <a name="taiwan-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-7202">臺灣護照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7202">Taiwan passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-7203">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7203">Format</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7204">生物識別護照號碼：9位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7204">Biometric passport number: Nine digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7205">非生物識別護照號碼：9位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7205">Non-biometric passport number: Nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-7206">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7206">Pattern</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="93909-7207">生物識別護照號碼：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7207">Biometric passport number:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7208">數位 "3"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7208">The digit "3"</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7209">八位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7209">Eight digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-7210">無生物識別護照號碼：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7210">Non-biometric passport number:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7211">九位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7211">Nine digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-7212">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7212">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-7213">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7213">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-7214">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7214">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-7215">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7215">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7216">正則運算式 Regex_taiwan_passport 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7216">The regular expression Regex_taiwan_passport finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7217">會找到來自 Keyword_taiwan_passport 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7217">A keyword from Keyword_taiwan_passport is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Taiwan Passport Number -->
<Entity id="e7251cb4-4c2c-41df-963e-924eb3dae04a" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Regex_taiwan_passport"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_taiwan_passport"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="taiwan-resident-certificate-arctarc-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-7228">臺灣居民憑證（ARC/TARC）號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7228">Taiwan resident certificate (ARC/TARC) number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-7229">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7229">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-7230">10個字母和數位</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7230">10 letters and digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-7231">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7231">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-7232">10個字母和數位：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7232">10 letters and digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7233">兩個字母（不區分大小寫）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7233">Two letters (not case sensitive)</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7234">八位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7234">Eight digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-7235">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7235">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-7236">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7236">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-7237">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7237">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-7238">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7238">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7239">正則運算式 Regex_taiwan_resident_certificate 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7239">The regular expression Regex_taiwan_resident_certificate finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7240">會找到來自 Keyword_taiwan_resident_certificate 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7240">A keyword from Keyword_taiwan_resident_certificate is found.</span></span>

```xml

  <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
     <IdMatch idRef="Regex_taiwan_resident_certificate"/>
     <Match idRef="Keyword_taiwan_resident_certificate"/>
  </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="thai-population-identification-code"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-7254">泰國人口識別碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7254">Thai population identification code</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-7255">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7255">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-7256">13位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7256">13 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-7257">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7257">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-7258">13位數：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7258">13 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7259">第一個數位不是0或9</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7259">First digit is not 0 or 9</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7260">12位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7260">12 digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-7261">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7261">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-7262">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7262">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-7263">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7263">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-7264">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是85%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7264">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7265">函數 Func_Thai_Citizen_Id 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7265">The function Func_Thai_Citizen_Id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7266">會找到來自 Keyword_Thai_Citizen_Id 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7266">A keyword from Keyword_Thai_Citizen_Id is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-7267">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7267">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7268">函數 Func_Thai_Citizen_Id 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7268">The function Func_Thai_Citizen_Id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Thai Citizen ID -->
-<Entity id="44ca9e86-ead7-4c5d-884a-e2eaa401515e" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">
   -<Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
      <IdMatch idRef="Func_Thai_Citizen_Id"/>
      <Match idRef="Keyword_Thai_Citizen_Id"/>
   </Pattern>
   -<Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
      <IdMatch idRef="Func_Thai_Citizen_Id"/>
   </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="turkish-national-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-7277">土耳其國身分識別號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7277">Turkish national identification number</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-7282">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7282">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-7283">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7283">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-7284">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7284">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-7285">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是85%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7285">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7286">函數 Func_Turkish_National_Id 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7286">The function Func_Turkish_National_Id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-7288">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7288">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7289">函數 Func_Turkish_National_Id 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7289">The function Func_Turkish_National_Id finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- Turkish National Identity -->
-<Entity id="fb621f20-3876-4cfc-acec-8c8e73ca32c7" recommendedConfidence="75" patternsProximity="300">

      <IdMatch idRef="Func_Turkish_National_Id"/>
      <Match idRef="Keyword_Turkish_National_Id"/>
   </Pattern>
   -<Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
      <IdMatch idRef="Func_Turkish_National_Id"/>
   </Pattern>
```

## <a name="uk-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-7296">英國。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7296">U.K.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="93909-7297">駕駛執照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7297">driver's license number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="93909-7298">這種敏感資訊類型的實體包含在歐盟駕駛執照號碼的敏感資訊類型中，可作為獨立的敏感資訊類型實體。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7298">This sensitive information type entity is included in the EU Driver's License Number sensitive information type and is available as a stand alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-7299">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7299">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-7300">以指定格式的18個字母和數位的組合</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7300">Combination of 18 letters and digits in the specified format</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-7301">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7301">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-7302">18個字母和數位：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7302">18 letters and digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7303">五個字母（不區分大小寫）或數位 "9" 取代字母</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7303">Five letters (not case sensitive) or the digit "9" in place of a letter</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7304">一個數位</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7304">One digit</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7305">MMDDY 日期格式中的5位數（如果驅動程式是女，則為第7個字元 62 51，而不是1到12，則增加50）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7305">Five digits in the date format MMDDY for date of birth (7th character is incremented by 50 if driver is female, i.e. 51 to 62 instead of 01 to 12)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7306">兩個字母（不區分大小寫）或數位 "9" 取代字母</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7306">Two letters (not case sensitive) or the digit "9" in place of a letter</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7307">五位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7307">Five digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-7308">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7308">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-7309">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7309">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-7310">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7310">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-7311">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7311">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7312">函數 Func_uk_drivers_license 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7312">The function Func_uk_drivers_license finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7313">會找到來自 Keyword_uk_drivers_license 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7313">A keyword from Keyword_uk_drivers_license is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7314">校驗和通過。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7314">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- U.K. Driver's License Number -->
<Entity id="f93de4be-d94c-40df-a8be-461738047551" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_uk_drivers_license" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_uk_drivers_license" />
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="uk-electoral-roll-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-7332">英國。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7332">U.K.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="93909-7333">electoral 編號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7333">electoral roll number</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-7336">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7336">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-7337">兩個字母（不區分大小寫）後接1-4 數目</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7337">Two letters (not case sensitive) followed by 1-4 numbers</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-7339">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7339">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-7340">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7340">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-7341">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7341">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7342">正則運算式 Regex_uk_electoral 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7342">The regular expression Regex_uk_electoral finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7343">會找到來自 Keyword_uk_electoral 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7343">A keyword from Keyword_uk_electoral is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- U.K. Electoral Number -->
<Entity id="a3eea206-dc0c-4f06-9e22-aa1be3059963" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_uk_electoral" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_uk_electoral" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-7344">關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7344">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_uk_electoral"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-7345">Keyword_uk_electoral</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7345">Keyword_uk_electoral</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7346">理事會提名</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7346">council nomination</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7347">提名表單</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7347">nomination form</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7348">electoral 寄存器</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7348">electoral register</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7349">electoral 輥</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7349">electoral roll</span></span>

   
## <a name="uk-national-health-service-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-7350">英國。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7350">U.K.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="93909-7351">本國健康情況服務號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7351">national health service number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-7352">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7352">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-7353">以空格分隔的10-17 位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7353">10-17 digits separated by spaces</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-7354">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7354">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-7355">10-17 位數：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7355">10-17 digits:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7356">3或10位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7356">Either 3 or 10 digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7357">一個空格</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7357">A space</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7358">三位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7358">Three digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7359">一個空格</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7359">A space</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7360">四位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7360">Four digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-7361">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7361">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-7362">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7362">Yes</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-7363">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7363">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-7364">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是85%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7364">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7365">函數 Func_uk_nhs_number 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7365">The function Func_uk_nhs_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7366">下列其中一項為真：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7366">One of the following is true:</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="93909-7367">會找到來自 Keyword_uk_nhs_number 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7367">A keyword from Keyword_uk_nhs_number is found.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="93909-7368">會找到來自 Keyword_uk_nhs_number1 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7368">A keyword from Keyword_uk_nhs_number1 is found.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="93909-7369">會找到來自 Keyword_uk_nhs_number_dob 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7369">A keyword from Keyword_uk_nhs_number_dob is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7370">校驗和通過。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7370">The checksum passes.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- U.K. NHS Number -->
<Entity id="3192014e-2a16-44e9-aa69-4b20375c9a78" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="85">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_uk_nhs_number" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_uk_nhs_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_uk_nhs_number1" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_uk_nhs_number_dob" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-7371">關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7371">Keywords</span></span>
   
#### <a name="keyword_uk_nhs_number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-7372">Keyword_uk_nhs_number</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7372">Keyword_uk_nhs_number</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7373">全國健康情況服務</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7373">national health service</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7374">Nhs</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7374">nhs</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7375">健康情況服務授權</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7375">health services authority</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7376">健康情況授權單位</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7376">health authority</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_uk_nhs_number1"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-7377">Keyword_uk_nhs_number1</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7377">Keyword_uk_nhs_number1</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7378">患者識別碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7378">patient id</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7379">患者識別</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7379">patient identification</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7380">患者否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7380">patient no</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7381">病人編號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7381">patient number</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_uk_nhs_number_dob"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-7382">Keyword_uk_nhs_number_dob</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7382">Keyword_uk_nhs_number_dob</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7383">Gp</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7383">GP</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7384">DOB</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7384">DOB</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7385">D. B</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7385">D.O.B</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7386">出生日期</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7386">Date of Birth</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7387">出生日期</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7387">Birth Date</span></span> 
   
## <a name="uk-national-insurance-number-nino"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-7388">英國。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7388">U.K.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="93909-7389">本國保險號碼（NINO）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7389">national insurance number (NINO)</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="93909-7390">此機密資訊類型的實體包含在歐盟國家 Identificaiton 號碼機密資訊類型中，也可作為獨立機密資訊類型實體使用。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7390">This sensitive information type entity is included in the EU National Identificaiton Number sensitive information type and is available as a stand alone sensitive information type entity.</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-7391">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7391">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-7392">以空格或破折號分隔的7個字元或9個字元</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7392">7 characters or 9 characters separated by spaces or dashes</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-7393">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7393">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-7394">兩種可能的模式：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7394">Two possible patterns:</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7395">兩個字母（有效的 NINOs 只會使用此前置詞中的特定字元，此模式會驗證; 不區分大小寫）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7395">Two letters (valid NINOs use only certain characters in this prefix, which this pattern validates; not case sensitive)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7396">六位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7396">Six digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7397">"A"、"B"、"C" 或 "d" （類似前置詞）只允許在尾碼中使用某些字元; 不區分大小寫）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7397">Either 'A', 'B', 'C', or 'D' (like the prefix, only certain characters are allowed in the suffix; not case sensitive)</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-7398">OR</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7398">OR</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7399">兩個字母</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7399">Two letters</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7400">一個空格或破折號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7400">A space or dash</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7401">兩位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7401">Two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7402">一個空格或破折號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7402">A space or dash</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7403">兩位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7403">Two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7404">一個空格或破折號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7404">A space or dash</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7405">兩位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7405">Two digits</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7406">一個空格或破折號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7406">A space or dash</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7407">' A '、' B '、' C ' 或 ' d ' 是 '</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7407">Either 'A', 'B', 'C', or 'D'</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-7408">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7408">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-7409">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7409">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-7410">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7410">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-7411">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是85%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7411">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7412">函數 Func_uk_nino 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7412">The function Func_uk_nino finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7413">會找到來自 Keyword_uk_nino 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7413">A keyword from Keyword_uk_nino is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-7414">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7414">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7415">函數 Func_uk_nino 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7415">The function Func_uk_nino finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7416">找不到 Keyword_uk_nino 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7416">No keyword from Keyword_uk_nino is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- U.K. NINO -->
<Entity id="16c07343-c26f-49d2-a987-3daf717e94cc" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_uk_nino" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_uk_nino" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>    
     <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_uk_nino" />
        <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_uk_nino" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

### <a name="keywords"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-7417">關鍵字</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7417">Keywords</span></span>

#### <a name="keyword_uk_nino"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-7418">Keyword_uk_nino</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7418">Keyword_uk_nino</span></span>

- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7419">本國保險號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7419">national insurance number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7420">全國保險貢獻</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7420">national insurance contributions</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7421">保護法案</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7421">protection act</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7422">保險</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7422">insurance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7423">社會安全號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7423">social security number</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7424">保險費應用程式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7424">insurance application</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7425">醫療應用程式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7425">medical application</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7426">社交保險</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7426">social insurance</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7427">醫療注意力</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7427">medical attention</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7428">社會保障</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7428">social security</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7429">英國</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7429">great britain</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7430">保險</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7430">insurance</span></span>
    
## <a name="uk-tax-identification-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-7431">英國。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7431">U.K.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="93909-7432">納稅識別號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7432">tax identification number</span></span>
<span data-ttu-id="93909-7433">此機密資訊類型實體僅可用於歐盟納稅識別碼的敏感資訊類型。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7433">This sensitive information type entity is only available in the EU Tax Identification Number sensitive information type.</span></span>


### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-7434">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7434">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-7435">唯一的納稅人參考（UTR）：10位數，不含空格及分隔符號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7435">Unique Taxpayer Reference (UTR): 10 digits without spaces and delimiters</span></span>
 
  
### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-7436">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7436">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-7437">唯一的納稅人參考（UTR）：10位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7437">Unique Taxpayer Reference (UTR): 10 digits</span></span>

  
### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-7438">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7438">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-7439">是</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7439">Yes</span></span>
  
### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-7440">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7440">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-7441">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7441">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
  
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7442">函數 `Func_uk_eu_tax_file_number` 會找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7442">The function  `Func_uk_eu_tax_file_number` finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span> 
    
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7443">找到來自的關鍵字 `Keywords_uk_eu_tax_file_number` 。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7443">A keyword from  `Keywords_uk_eu_tax_file_number` is found.</span></span> 
    
```
 <!-- EU Tax File Number -->
<Entity id="e09c07d3-66e5-4783-989d-49ac62748f5f" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
        <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
          <IdMatch idRef="Func_uk_eu_tax_file_number" />
          <Match idRef="Keywords_uk_eu_tax_file_number" />
```

## <a name="us-bank-account-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-7463">美國銀行帳戶號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7463">U.S. bank account number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-7464">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7464">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-7465">8-17 位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7465">8-17 digits</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-7466">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7466">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-7467">8-17 連續位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7467">8-17 consecutive digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-7468">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7468">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-7469">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7469">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-7470">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7470">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-7471">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7471">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7472">正則運算式 Regex_usa_bank_account_number 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7472">The regular expression Regex_usa_bank_account_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7473">會找到來自 Keyword_usa_Bank_Account 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7473">A keyword from Keyword_usa_Bank_Account is found.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- U.S. Bank Account Number -->
<Entity id="a2ce32a8-f935-4bb6-8e96-2a5157672e2c" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Regex_usa_bank_account_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_usa_Bank_Account" />
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="us-drivers-license-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-7503">美國駕駛執照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7503">U.S. driver's license number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-7504">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7504">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-7505">取決於狀態</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7505">Depends on the state</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-7506">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7506">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-7507">取決於狀態--例如紐約：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7507">Depends on the state -- for example, New York:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7508">已格式化的九位數，如 ddd ddd ddd 會相符。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7508">Nine digits formatted like ddd ddd ddd will match.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7509">九位數的 ddddddddd 不相符。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7509">Nine digits like ddddddddd will not match.</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-7510">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7510">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-7511">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7511">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-7512">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7512">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-7513">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7513">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7514">函數 Func_new_york_drivers_license_number 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7514">The function Func_new_york_drivers_license_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7515">找到來自 Keyword_ [state_name] _drivers_license_name 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7515">A keyword from Keyword_[state_name]_drivers_license_name is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7516">會找到來自 Keyword_us_drivers_license 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7516">A keyword from Keyword_us_drivers_license is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-7517">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是65%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7517">A DLP policy is 65% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7518">函數 Func_new_york_drivers_license_number 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7518">The function Func_new_york_drivers_license_number finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7519">找到來自 Keyword_ [state_name] _drivers_license_name 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7519">A keyword from Keyword_[state_name]_drivers_license_name is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7520">會找到來自 Keyword_us_drivers_license_abbreviations 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7520">A keyword from Keyword_us_drivers_license_abbreviations is found.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7521">找不到 Keyword_us_drivers_license 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7521">No keyword from Keyword_us_drivers_license is found.</span></span>

```xml
<Entity id="dfeb356f-61cd-459e-bf0f-7c6d28b458c6 patternsProximity="300">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_new_york_drivers_license_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_new_york_drivers_license_name" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_us_drivers_license" />
    </Pattern>
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_new_york_drivers_license_number" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_new_york_drivers_license_name" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_us_drivers_license_abbreviations" />
        <Any minMatches="0" maxMatches="0">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_us_drivers_license" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="us-individual-taxpayer-identification-number-itin"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-7619">美國個別的納稅人識別號碼（ITIN）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7619">U.S. individual taxpayer identification number (ITIN)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-7620">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7620">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-7621">以 "9" 開頭且包含 "7" 或 "8" 的九位數做為第四位數，可選擇性地使用空格或破折號格式化</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7621">Nine digits that start with a "9" and contain a "7" or "8" as the fourth digit, optionally formatted with spaces or dashes</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-7622">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7622">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-7623">格式 化：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7623">Formatted:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7624">數位 "9"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7624">The digit "9"</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7625">兩位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7625">Two digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7626">一個空格或破折號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7626">A space or dash</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7627">"7" 或 "8"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7627">A "7" or "8"</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7628">一個數位</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7628">A digit</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7629">一個空格或破折號</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7629">A space, or dash</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7630">四位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7630">Four digits</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-7631">非</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7631">Unformatted:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7632">數位 "9"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7632">The digit "9"</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7633">兩位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7633">Two digits</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7634">"7" 或 "8"</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7634">A "7" or "8"</span></span> 
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7635">五位數</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7635">Five digits</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-7636">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7636">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-7637">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7637">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-7638">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7638">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-7639">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是85%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7639">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7640">函數 Func_formatted_itin 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7640">The function Func_formatted_itin finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7641">下列專案中至少有一個為真：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7641">At least one of the following is true:</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="93909-7642">會找到來自 Keyword_itin 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7642">A keyword from Keyword_itin is found.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="93909-7643">函數 Func_us_address 會找到正確日期格式的位址。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7643">The function Func_us_address finds an address in the right date format.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="93909-7644">函數 Func_us_date 會找到正確日期格式的日期。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7644">The function Func_us_date finds a date in the right date format.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="93909-7645">會找到來自 Keyword_itin_collaborative 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7645">A keyword from Keyword_itin_collaborative is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-7646">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7646">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7647">函數 Func_unformatted_itin 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7647">The function Func_unformatted_itin finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7648">下列專案中至少有一個為真：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7648">At least one of the following is true:</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="93909-7649">會找到來自 Keyword_itin_collaborative 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7649">A keyword from Keyword_itin_collaborative is found.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="93909-7650">函數 Func_us_address 會找到正確日期格式的位址。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7650">The function Func_us_address finds an address in the right date format.</span></span>
    - <span data-ttu-id="93909-7651">函數 Func_us_date 會找到正確日期格式的日期。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7651">The function Func_us_date finds a date in the right date format.</span></span>

```xml
<!-- U.S. Individual Taxpayer Identification Number (ITIN) -->
<Entity id="e55e2a32-f92d-4985-a35d-a0b269eb687b" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_formatted_itin" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_itin" />
          <Match idRef="Func_us_address" />
          <Match idRef="Func_us_date" />
          <Match idRef="Keyword_itin_collaborative" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_unformatted_itin" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_itin" />
        <Any minMatches="1">
          <Match idRef="Keyword_itin_collaborative" />
          <Match idRef="Func_us_address" />
          <Match idRef="Func_us_date" />
        </Any>
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```

## <a name="us-social-security-number-ssn"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-7672">U.S. 社會安全號碼（SSN）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7672">U.S. social security number (SSN)</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-7673">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7673">Format</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-7674">9位數（可能是格式化或未格式化的模式）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7674">9 digits, which may be in a formatted or unformatted pattern</span></span>

> [!NOTE]
> <span data-ttu-id="93909-7675">如果在2011之前發出，則 SSN 具有強格式，其中的號碼的某些部分必須介於一定範圍內，才是有效的（但沒有任何 checksum）。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7675">If issued before mid-2011, an SSN has strong formatting where certain parts of the number must fall within certain ranges to be valid (but there's no checksum).</span></span>

### <a name="pattern"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-7676">模式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7676">Pattern</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-7677">四種功能會在四種不同的模式中尋找主旨 ssn：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7677">Four functions look for SSNs in four different patterns:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7678">Func_ssn 會2011以主旨 ssn 的強格式格式化，並以短劃線或空格格式化（ddd-dd-dddd 或 ddd dd dddd）來尋找</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7678">Func_ssn finds SSNs with pre-2011 strong formatting that are formatted with dashes or spaces (ddd-dd-dddd OR ddd dd dddd)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7679">Func_unformatted_ssn 會以預先2011的強格式格式化，以格式化為九個連續數位（ddddddddd）的主旨 ssn，來尋找</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7679">Func_unformatted_ssn finds SSNs with pre-2011 strong formatting that are unformatted as nine consecutive digits (ddddddddd)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7680">Func_randomized_formatted_ssn 會找到以短劃線或空格格式化的2011後主旨 ssn （ddd-dd-dddd 或 ddd dd dddd）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7680">Func_randomized_formatted_ssn finds post-2011 SSNs that are formatted with dashes or spaces (ddd-dd-dddd OR ddd dd dddd)</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7681">Func_randomized_unformatted_ssn 尋找未格式化為九個連續數位的2011後主旨 ssn （ddddddddd）</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7681">Func_randomized_unformatted_ssn finds post-2011 SSNs that are unformatted as nine consecutive digits (ddddddddd)</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-7682">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7682">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-7683">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7683">No</span></span>


### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-7684">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7684">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-7685">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是85%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7685">A DLP policy is 85% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7686">函數 Func_ssn 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7686">The function Func_ssn finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7687">會找到來自 Keyword_ssn 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7687">A keyword from Keyword_ssn is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-7688">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7688">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7689">函數 Func_unformatted_ssn 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7689">The function Func_unformatted_ssn finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7690">會找到來自 Keyword_ssn 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7690">A keyword from Keyword_ssn is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-7691">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是65%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7691">A DLP policy is 65% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7692">函數 Func_randomized_formatted_ssn 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7692">The function Func_randomized_formatted_ssn finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7693">會找到來自 Keyword_ssn 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7693">A keyword from Keyword_ssn is found.</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-7694">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是55%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7694">A DLP policy is 55% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7695">函數 Func_randomized_unformatted_ssn 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7695">The function Func_randomized_unformatted_ssn finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7696">會找到來自 Keyword_ssn 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7696">A keyword from Keyword_ssn is found.</span></span>


```xml
<!-- U.S. Social Security Number (SSN) -->
  <Entity id="a44669fe-0d48-453d-a9b1-2cc83f2cba77" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="85">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_ssn" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_ssn" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_unformatted_ssn" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_ssn" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="65">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_randomized_formatted_ssn" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_ssn" />
      </Pattern>
      <Pattern confidenceLevel="55">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_randomized_unformatted_ssn" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_ssn" />
      </Pattern>
  </Entity>
```

## <a name="us--uk-passport-number"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-7707">美國/英國</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7707">U.S. / U.K.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="93909-7708">護照號碼</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7708">passport number</span></span>

### <a name="format"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-7711">格式</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7711">Format</span></span>

### <a name="checksum"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-7715">校驗</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7715">Checksum</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-7716">否</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7716">No</span></span>

### <a name="definition"></a><span data-ttu-id="93909-7717">定義</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7717">Definition</span></span>

<span data-ttu-id="93909-7718">如果接近300個字元以內，則 DLP 原則偵測到此敏感資訊類型的置信量是75%：</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7718">A DLP policy is 75% confident that it's detected this type of sensitive information if, within a proximity of 300 characters:</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7719">函數 Func_usa_uk_passport 找到符合模式的內容。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7719">The function Func_usa_uk_passport finds content that matches the pattern.</span></span>
- <span data-ttu-id="93909-7720">會找到來自 Keyword_passport 的關鍵字。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="93909-7720">A keyword from Keyword_passport is found.</span></span>

```xml
<Entity id="178ec42a-18b4-47cc-85c7-d62c92fd67f8" patternsProximity="300" recommendedConfidence="75">
    <Pattern confidenceLevel="75">
        <IdMatch idRef="Func_usa_uk_passport" />
        <Match idRef="Keyword_passport" />
    </Pattern>
</Entity>
```
